        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK TANG CAIZI CHUAN ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Hui-Ting Chuang</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">书名: 唐才子傳\n辛文房著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Title: Tang Caizi Chuan (Biographies of T'ang Talents)\nAuthor: Xin Wen-fang</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">卷一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>        ○序</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    魏帝著《論》，稱“文章經國之大業，不朽之盛事，年壽有時而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>盡，未若文章之無窮”。詩，文而音者也。唐興尚文，衣冠兼化，無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>慮不可勝計。擅美于詩，當復千家。歲月苒苒，遷逝淪落，亦且多矣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。況乃浮沉畏途，黽勉卑宦，存沒相半，不亦難乎！崇事奕葉，苦思</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>積年，心神游穹厚之倪，耳目及晏曠之際，幸成著述，更或凋零，兵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>火相仍，名逮于此，談何容易哉！夫詩，所以動天地，感鬼神，厚人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>倫，移風俗也。發乎其情，止乎禮義，非苟尚辭而已。溯尋其來，國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風、雅、頌開其端，《離騷》、《招魂》放厥辭；蘇、李之高妙，足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以定律；建安之遒壯，粲爾成家；爛漫于江左，濫觴于齊、梁，皆襲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>祖沿流，坦然明白。鏗鏘愧金石，炳煥卻丹青，理窮必通，因時為變</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，勿訝于枳橘，非土所宜；誰別于渭、涇，投膠自定，蓋系乎得失之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>運也。唐几三百年，鼎鐘挾雅道，中間大體三變，故章句有焦心之人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，聲律至穿楊之妙，于法而能備，于言無所假。及其逸度高標，余波</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遺韻，臨高能賦，閑暇微吟，舊格近體、古風樂府之類，芳沃當代，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>響起陳人，淡寂無枯悴之嫌，繁藻無淫妖之忌，猶金碧助彩，宮商自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>協，端足以仰緒先塵，俯謝來世，清廟之瑟，薰風之琴，未或簡其沉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郁，兩晉風流，不相下于秋毫也。余遐想高情，身服斯道，究其梗概</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>行藏，散見錯出，使覽于述作，尚昧音容，洽彼姓名，未辨機軸，嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>切病之。頃以端居多暇，害事都捐，游目簡編，宅心史集，或求詳累</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帙，因備先傳，撰擬成篇，斑斑有據，以悉全時之盛，用成一家之言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，各冠以時，定為先后，遠陪公議，誰得而誣也。如方外高格，逃名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>散人，上漢仙侶，幽閨綺思，雖多微考實，故別總論之。天下英奇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所見略似，人心相去，苦亦不多。至若觸事興懷，隨附篇末。異方之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士，弱冠斐然，狃于見聞，豈所能盡。敢倡斯盟，尚賴同志相與廣焉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。庶乎作九京于長夢，詠一代之清風。后來奮飛可畏，相激百世之下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，猶期賞音也。傳成凡二百七十八篇，因而附錄不泯者又一百二十家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，厘為十卷，名以《唐才子傳》云。有元大德甲辰春引。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○六帝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    夫云漢昭回，仰彌高于宸極；洪鐘希叩，發至響于咸池。以太宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天縱，玄廟聰明，憲、德、文、僖，睿姿繼挺，俱以萬機之暇，特駐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吟情，奎璧騰輝，袞龍浮彩，寵延臣下，每錫贈酬。故上有好者，下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>必有甚焉者矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○王績</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    績，字無功，絳州龍門人，文中子通之弟也。年十五游長安，謁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>楊素，一坐服其英敏，目為神仙童子。隋大業末，舉孝廉高第，除秘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書正字。不樂在朝，辭疾，復授揚州六合縣丞。以嗜酒妨政，時天下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亦亂，遂托病風，輕舟夜遁。嘆曰：“網羅在天，吾將安之！”乃還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>故鄉。至唐武德中，詔征以前朝官待詔門下省，績弟靜謂績曰：“待</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詔可樂否“曰：“待詔俸薄，況蕭瑟，但良醞三升，差可戀耳。”（</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>待詔）江國公聞之曰：“三升良醞，未足以絆王先生。”特判日給一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>斗。時人呼為“斗酒學士”。貞觀初，以疾罷歸。河渚間有仲長子光</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者，亦隱士也，無妻子。績愛其真，遂相近結廬，日與對酌。君有奴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>婢數人，多種黍，春秋釀酒，養鳧雁、蒔藥草自供。以《周易》、《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>莊》、《老》置床頭，無他用心也。自號“東皋子”。雖刺史謁見，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>皆不答。終于家。性簡傲，好飲酒，能盡五斗，自著《五斗先生傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。彈琴、為詩、著文，高情勝氣，獨步當時。撰《酒經》一卷、《酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>譜》一卷。李淳風見之曰：“君酒家南、董也。”及詩賦等傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    論曰：唐興迨季葉，治日少而亂日多，雖草衣帶索，罕得安居。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>當其時，遠釣弋者，不走山而逃海，斯德而隱者矣。自王君以下，幽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人間出，皆遠騰長往之士，危行言遜，重撥禍機，糠核軒冕，挂冠引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>退，往往見之。躍身炎冷之途，標華黃、綺之列。雖或累聘丘園，勉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>加冠佩，適足以速深藏于藪澤耳。然猶有不能逃白刃、死非命焉。夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>跡晦名彰，風高塵絕，豈不以有翰墨之妙，騷雅之奇美哉！文章為不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朽之盛事也。恥不為堯、舜民，學者之所同志；致君于三、五，懦夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尚知勇為。今則舍聲利而向山棲，鹿冠舄几，使于錦繡之服；柴車茅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舍，安于丹雘之廈；藜羹不糝，甘于五鼎之味；素琴濁酒，和于醇飴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之奉；樵青山，漁白水，足于佩金魚而紆紫綬也。時有不同也，事有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不侔也。向子平曰：“吾故知富不如貧，貴不如賤，第未知死何如生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。“此達人之言也。《易》曰：“遯之時義大矣哉！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔信明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    信明，青州人。少英敏，及長，強記，美文章。高孝基語人曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“崔生才冠一時，但恨位不到耳。”隋大業中，為堯城令。竇建德僭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>號，信明弟仕賊，勸信明降節，當得美官。不肯從，遂逾城去，隱太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>行山中。唐貞觀六年，詔即家拜興勢丞，遷秦川令，卒。信明恃才蹇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亢，嘗自矜其文。時有揚州錄事參軍滎陽鄭世翼，亦驁倨忤物，遇信</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>明于江中，謂曰：“聞君有‘楓落呈江冷’之句，仍願見其余。”信</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>明欣然多出舊制。鄭覽未終，曰：“所見不逮所聞！”投卷于水中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>引舟而去。今其詩傳者數篇而已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○王勃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    勃，字子安，太原人，王通之諸孫也。六歲善辭章。麟德初，劉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>祥道表其材，對策高第。未及冠，授朝散郎。沛王召署府修撰。時諸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王斗雞，會勃戲為文檄英王雞，高宗聞之，怒，斥出府。勃既廢，客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>劍南，登山曠望，慨然思諸葛之功，賦詩見情。又嘗匿死罪官奴，恐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事泄，輒殺之，事覺當誅，會赦除名。父福畤坐是左遷交趾令。勃往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>省覲，途過南昌，時都督閻公新修滕王閣成，九月九日，大會賓客，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>將令其婿作記，以夸盛事。勃至入謁，帥知其才，因請為之。勃欣然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>對客操觚，頃刻而就，文不加點，滿座大驚。酒酣辭別，帥贈百縑，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>即舉帆去，至炎方，舟入洋海溺死，時年二十九。勃屬文綺麗，請者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甚多，金帛盈積，心織而衣，筆耕而食。然不甚精思，先磨墨數升，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>則酣飲，引被覆面臥，及寤，援筆成篇，不易一字，人謂之腹稿。嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>言人子不可不知醫，時長安曹元有秘方，勃盡得其術。又以虢州多藥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>草，求補參軍。倚才陵藉，僚吏疾之。有集三十卷，及《舟中纂序》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>五卷，今行于世。勃嘗遇異人，相之曰：“子神強骨弱，氣清體羸，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>腦骨虧陷，目睛不全。秀而不實，終無大貴矣。”故其才長而命短者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，豈非相乎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○楊炯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    炯，華陰人。顯慶六年舉神童，授校書郎。永隆二年，皇太子舍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奠，表豪俊，充崇文館學士。后為婺州盈川令。卒。炯恃才憑傲，每</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>恥朝士矯飾，呼為“麒麟楦”。或問之，曰：“今假弄麒麟戲者，必</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刻畫其形覆驢上，宛然異物，及去其皮，還是驢耳。”聞者甚不平，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>故為時所忌。初，張說以《箴》贈盈川之行，戒其苛刻，至官，果以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酷稱。炯博學善文，與王勃、盧照鄰、駱賓王以文辭齊名，海內稱四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才子，亦曰“四杰”，效之者風靡焉。炯嘗謂：“吾愧在盧前，恥居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王后。”張說曰：“盈川文如懸河，酌之不竭。恥王后，愧盧前，謙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。”有《盈川集》三十卷行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○盧照鄰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    照鄰，字昇之，范陽人。調鄧王府典簽，王愛重，謂人曰：“此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吾之相如也。”后遷新都尉，嬰病去官。居太白山草閣，得方士玄明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>膏餌之。會父喪，號慟，因嘔，丹輒出，疾愈甚。家貧苦，貴宦時時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>供衣藥，乃去具茨山下，買園數十畝，疏潁水周舍，復豫為墓，偃臥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其中。自以當高宗時尚吏，己獨儒；武后尚法，己獨黃老；后封嵩山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，屢聘賢士，己已廢；著《五悲文》以自明。手足攣緩，不起行已十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年，每春歸秋至，云壑煙郊，輒輿出戶庭，悠然一望。遂自傷，作《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>釋疾文》，有云：“覆燾雖廣，嗟不容乎此生；亭育雖繁，恩已絕乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>斯代。”與親屬訣，自沉潁水。有詩文二十卷及《幽懮子》三卷行于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○駱賓王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    賓王，義烏人。七歲能賦詩。武后時，數上疏言事，得罪貶臨海</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>丞，鞅鞅不得志，棄官去。文明中，徐敬業起兵欲反正，往投之，署</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為府屬。為敬業作檄傳天下，暴斥武后罪。后見讀之，矍然曰：“誰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為之“或以賓王對，后曰：“有如此才不用，宰相過也。”及敗亡命</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不知所之。后宋之問貶還，道出錢塘，游靈隱寺，夜月，行吟長廊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下，曰：“鷲嶺郁岧嶢，龍宮隱寂寥。”未得下聯。有老僧燃燈坐禪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，問曰：“少年不寐，而吟諷甚苦，何耶“之問曰：“欲題此寺，而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>思不屬。”僧笑曰：“何不道‘樓觀滄海日，門對浙江潮。’“之問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>終篇曰：“桂子月中落，天香云外飄。捫蘿登塔遠，刳木取泉遙。云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>薄霜初下，冰輕葉未凋。待入天台寺，看余渡石橋。”僧一聯，篇中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>警策也。遲明訪之，已不見。老僧即駱賓王也。傳聞桴海而去矣。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，中宗詔求其文，得百余篇及詩等十卷，命郗云卿次序之，及《百道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>判集》一卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○杜審言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    審言，字必簡，京兆人，預之遠裔。咸亨元年宋守節榜進士，為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>隰城尉。恃高才，傲世見疾。蘇味道為天官侍郎，審言集判，出謂人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“味道必死。”人驚問何故，曰：“彼見吾判，當羞死耳。”又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“吾文章當得屈、宋作衙官，吾筆當得王羲之北面。”其矜誕類</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此。坐事貶吉州司戶。乃武后召還，將用之，問曰：“卿喜否“審言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舞蹈謝。后令賦《歡喜詩》，稱旨，授著作郎，為修文館直學士。卒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初，審言病，宋之問、武平一往省候，曰：“甚為造化小兒相苦，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尚何言！然吾在，久壓公等。今且死，但恨不見替人也。”少與李嶠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、崔融、蘇味道為“文章四友”。有集十卷，今不存，但傳詩四十余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>篇而已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○沈佺期</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    佺期，字云卿，相州人。上元二年鄭益榜進士。工五言。由協律</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、考功郎受賕，長流驩州。后召拜起居郎，兼修文館直學士。常侍宮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，既侍宴，帝詔學士等為《回波》舞，佺期作弄辭悅帝，詔賜牙緋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。歷中書舍人。佺期嘗以詩贈張燕公，公曰：“沈三兄詩清麗，須讓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>居第一也。”詩名大振。自魏建安迄江左，詩律屢變。至沈約、鮑照</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、庾信、徐陵以音韻相婉附，屬對精致。及佺期、之問，又加靡麗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>回忌聲病，約句准篇，著定格律，遂成近體，如錦繡成文，學者宗尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。語曰：“蘇、李居前，沈、宋比肩。”謂唐詩變體，始自二公，猶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>始自蘇武、李陵也。有集十卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○宋之問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    之問，字延清，汾州人。上元二年進士。偉貌辯給。甫冠，武后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>召與楊炯分直習藝館，累轉尚方監丞。后游龍門，詔從臣賦詩，左史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>東方虯詩先成，后賜錦袍。之問俄頃獻，后覽之嗟賞，更奪袍以賜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后求北門學士，以有齒疾不許，遂作《明河篇》，有“明河可望不可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>親“之句，以見志。謅事張易之，坐貶瀧州。后逃歸，匿張仲之家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聞仲之謀殺武三思，乃告變，擢鴻臚簿，遷考功郎，復媚太平公主。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以知舉賄賂狼藉，下遷越州長史。窮歷剡溪山水，置酒賦詩，日游宴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，賓客雜遝。睿宗立，以無悛悟之心，流欽州，御史劾奏賜死。人言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>劉希夷之報也。徐堅嘗論其文，“如良金美玉，無施不可”。有集行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉希夷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    希夷，字廷芝，潁川人。上元二年鄭益榜進士，時年二十五，射</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>策有文名。苦篇詠，特善閨帷之作，詞情哀怨，多依古調，體勢與時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不合，遂不為所重。希夷美姿容，好談笑，善彈琵琶，飲酒至數斗不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>醉，落魄不拘常檢。嘗作《白頭吟》，一聯云：“今年花落顏色改，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>明年花開復誰在。”既而嘆曰：“此語讖也。石崇謂‘白首同所歸’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，復何以異。”乃除之。又吟曰：“年年歲歲花相似，歲歲年年人不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>同。”復嘆曰：“死生有命，豈由此虛言乎！”遂并存之。舅宋之問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>苦愛后一聯，知其未傳于人，懇求之，許而竟不與。之問怒其誑己，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>使奴以土囊壓殺于別舍，時未及三十，人悉憐之。有集十卷及詩集四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，今傳。希夷天賦俊爽，才情如此，想其事業勛名，何所不至，孰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謂奇蹇之運，遭逢惡人，寸祿不沾，長懷頓挫，斯才高而見忌者也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賈生悼長沙之屈，檷衡痛江夏之來，倏焉折首，無何殞命。以隋侯之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>珠，彈千仞之雀，所較者輕，所失者重，玉迸松摧，良可惜也。況于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>骨肉相殘者乎！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陳子昂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    子昂，字伯玉，梓州人。開耀二年許旦榜進士。初，年十八時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>未知書，以富家子，任俠尚氣弋博，后入鄉校感悔，即于州東南金華</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山觀讀書，痛自修飭，精窮墳典，耽愛黃、老、《易•象》。光宅元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年，詣闕上書，諫靈駕入京。武后召見，奇其才，遂拜麟台正字，令</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“地籍英華，文稱暐曄。”累遷拾遺。聖歷初，解官歸。會父喪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，廬塚次。縣令段簡貪殘，聞其富，造詐誣子昂，脅取賂二十萬緡，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>猶薄之，遂送獄。子昂自筮封，驚曰：“天命不祐，吾殆窮乎！”果</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>死獄中，年四十三。子昂貌柔雅，為性褊躁，輕財好施，篤朋友之義</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。與游英俊，多秉鈞衡。唐興，文章承徐、庾余風，天下祖尚，子昂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>始變雅正。初，為《感遇詩》三十章，王適見而驚曰：“此子必為海</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>內文宗。”由是知名，凡所著論，世以為法，詩調尤工。嘗勸后興明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>堂、太學，以調元氣。柳公權評曰：“能極著述，克備比興，唐興以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>來，子昂而已。”有集十卷，今傳。嗚呼！古來材大，或難為用。象</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以有齒，卒焚其身。信哉，子昂之謂歟！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李百藥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    百藥，字重規，定州人。幼多病，祖母以“百藥“名之。七歲能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文。襲父德林爵。會高祖招杜伏威，百藥勸朝京師，中道而悔，怒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>飲以石灰酒，因大利几死，既而宿病皆愈。貞觀中，拜中書舍人，遷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>太子庶子。嘗侍帝，同賦《帝京篇》，手詔褒美，曰：“卿何身老而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才之壯，齒宿而意之新乎！”百藥才行，天下推服。好獎荐后進。翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>藻沉郁，詩尤所長。有集傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李嶠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嶠，字巨山，趙州人。十五通五經，二十擢進士，累遷為監察御</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>史。武后時，同鳳閣鸞台平章事。后因罪貶廬州別駕，卒。嶠富才思</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，有所屬綴，人輒傳諷。明皇將幸蜀，登花萼樓，使樓前善《水調》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者奏歌，歌曰：“山川滿目淚沾衣，富貴榮華能几時不見只今汾水上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，惟有年年秋雁飛。”帝慘愴，移時，顧侍者曰：“誰為此“對曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“故宰相李嶠之詞也。”帝曰：“真才子！”不待終曲而去。嶠前與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王勃、楊炯接，中與崔融、蘇味道齊名，晚諸人沒，為文章宿老，學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者取法焉。今集五十卷，《雜詠詩》十二卷，《單題詩》一百二十首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，張方為注，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    說，字道濟，洛陽人。垂拱四年，舉學綜古今科，中第三等，考</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>策日封進，授太子校書。令曰：“張說文思清新，藝能優洽。金門對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>策，已居高科之首；銀榜效官，宜申一命之秩。”后累遷鳳閣舍人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>睿宗時，兵部侍郎、同平章事。開元十八年，終左丞相、燕國公。說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敦氣節，重然諾。為文精壯，長于碑志。朝廷大述作，多出其手。詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>法特妙，晚謫岳陽，詩益淒婉，人謂得江山之助。今有集三十卷，行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于世。子均，開元四年進士，亦以詩鳴。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    翰，字子羽，并州人。景云元年盧逸下進士及第。又舉直言極諫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，又舉超拔群類科。少豪蕩，怯才不羈，喜縱酒，櫪多名馬，家蓄妓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>樂。翰發言立意，自比王侯。日聚英杰，縱禽擊鼓為歡。張嘉貞為本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>州長史，厚遇之。翰酒間自歌，以舞屬嘉貞，神氣軒舉。張說尤加禮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>異，及輔政，召為正字，擢駕部員外郎。說罷，翰出為仙州別駕。以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>窮樂畋飲，貶嶺表，道卒。翰工詩，多壯麗之詞。文士祖詠、杜華等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，嘗與游從。華母崔氏云：“吾聞孟母三遷，吾今欲卜居，使汝與王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翰為鄰，足矣。”其才名如此。燕公論其文，如瓊杯玉斝，雖爛然可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>珍，而多玷缺云。有集今傳。太史公恨古布衣之俠，湮沒無聞，以其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>義出存亡死生之間，而不伐其德，千金駟馬，才啻草芥。信哉，名不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>虛立也。觀王翰之氣，其若人之儔乎！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○吳筠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    筠，字貞節，華陰人。通經義，美文辭。舉進士不中，隱居南陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>倚帝山為道士。天寶中，玄宗遣使召至京師，與語甚悅，敕待詔翰林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。獻《玄綱》三篇。帝問道，對曰：“深于道者，惟《老子》五千言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，其余徒費紙札耳。”復問神仙治煉之術，曰：“此野人之事，積歲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月求之，非人主所宜留意。”筠每陳設名教世務，帝重之。初，筠愛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>會稽山水，往來天台、剡中，與李白、孔巢父相遇酬唱，至是因荐于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朝，帝即遣使召之。筠性高鯁，其待詔翰林時，恃承恩顧。高力士素</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奉佛，嘗短筠于上前。筠故多著賦文，深詆釋氏，頗為通人所譏云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后知天下將亂，苦求還嵩山，詔為立道觀。大歷間卒。弟子謚為宗元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>先生。善為詩。有集十卷，權德輿序之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○張子容</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    子容，襄陽人。開元元年常無名榜進士。仕為樂城令。初與孟浩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然同隱鹿門山，為死生交，詩篇唱答頗多。后值亂離，流寓江表，嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>送內兄李錄事歸故里云：“十年多難與君同，几處移家逐轉蓬。白首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相逢征戰后，青春已過亂離中。行人杳杳看西日，歸馬蕭蕭向北風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>漢水楚云千萬里，天涯此別恨無窮。”后竟棄官歸舊業。有詩集，興</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>趣高遠，略去凡近。當時哲匠，咸稱道焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○李昂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    昂，開元二年王丘下狀元及第。天寶間仕為禮部侍郎，知貢舉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>獎拔寒素甚多。工詩，有《戚夫人楚舞歌》一篇，播傳人口，真佳作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○孫逖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    逖，博州人。幼而有文，屬思警敏，援筆成篇。開元二年，舉手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>筆俊拔、哲人奇士隱淪屠釣及文藻宏麗等科，第一人及第。玄宗引見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，擢左拾遺，集賢殿修撰。改考功員外郎，遷中書舍人。與顏真卿、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李華、蕭穎士皆同時，稱海內名士。仕終刑部侍郎。善詩，古調今格</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，悉其所長。集二十卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○盧鴻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鴻，字浩然，隱居嵩山。博學，善八分書，工詩，兼畫山水樹石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。開元初，玄宗備禮征再三，不至。詔曰：“鴻有泰一之道，中庸之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>德，鉤深詣微，確乎自高。詔書屢下，每輒辭托，使朕虛心引領，于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>今有年。雖有素履幽人之介，而失考父滋恭之誼。禮有大倫，君臣之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>義，不可廢也。有司其賚束帛之具，重宣茲旨，想其翻然易節，副朕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>意焉。”鴻遂至東都，謁見不拜，宰相問狀，答曰：“禮者，忠信所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>薄。臣敢以忠信見帝。”召升內殿，置酒。拜諫議大夫，固辭，復下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詔許還山。將行，賜隱居服，官營草堂。鴻到山中，廣精舍，從學者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>五百人。及卒，詔賜萬錢營葬。后皮日休為《七愛詩》謂：“傲大君</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者，必有真隱，盧征君是也。”工詩，今傳甚多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王泠然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    泠然，山東人。開元五年，裴耀卿下進士，授將仕郎，守太子校</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書郎。工文賦詩。氣質豪爽，當言無所回忌，乃卓犖奇才，濟世之器</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。惜其不大顯而終。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○劉慎虛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    慎虛，嵩山人。姿容秀拔。九歲屬文，上書，召見，拜童子郎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>開元十一年，徐征榜進士，調洛陽尉，遷夏縣令。性高古，脫略勢利</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，嘯傲風塵。后欲卜隱廬阜，不果。交游多山僧道侶。為詩情幽興遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，思雅詞奇，忽有所得，便驚眾聽。當時東南高唱者數十人，聲律婉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>態，無出其右，惟氣骨不逮諸公。永明已還，端可杰立江表。善為方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外之言。夫何不永，天碎國寶，有志不就，惜哉！集今傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王灣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    灣，開元元年常無名榜進士。與學士綦毋潛契切。詞翰早著，為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天下所稱。往來吳、楚間，多有著述。如《江南意》一聯云：“海日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生殘夜，江春入舊年。”詩人以來，罕有此作。張燕公手題于政事堂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，每示能文，令為楷式。曾奉使登終南山，有賦。志趣高遠，識者不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能棄焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔顥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    顥，汴州人。開元十一年源少良下及進士第。天寶中，為尚書司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>勛員外郎。少年為詩，意浮艷，多陷輕薄，晚節忽變常體，風骨凜然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。一窺塞垣，狀極戎旅，奇造往往并驅江、鮑。后游武昌，登黃鶴樓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，感慨賦詩。及李白來，曰：“眼前有景道不得，崔顥題詩在上頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”無作而去。為哲匠斂手云。然行履稍劣，好蒱博，嗜酒。娶妻擇美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者，稍不愜，即棄之，凡易三四。初，李邕聞其才名，虛舍邀之。顥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至獻詩，首章云：“十五嫁王昌。”邕叱曰：“小兒無禮！”不與接</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而入。顥苦吟詠，當病起清虛，友人戲之曰：“非子病如此，乃苦吟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩瘦耳。”遂為口實。天寶十三年卒。有詩一卷，今行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○祖詠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    詠，洛陽人。開元十二年杜綰榜進士。有文名，殷璠評其詩：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翦刻省靜，用思尤苦，氣雖不高，調頗凌俗，足稱為才子也。”少與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王維為吟侶，維在濟州，寓官舍，贈祖三詩，有云：“結交二十載，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不得一日展。貧病子既深，契闊余不淺。”蓋亦流落不偶，極可傷也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。后移家歸汝墳間別業，以漁樵自終。有詩一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○儲光羲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    光羲，兗州人。開元十四年嚴迪榜進士。有詔中書試文章。嘗為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>監察御史。值安祿山陷長安，輒受偽署。賊平后，自歸，貶死嶺南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工詩，格高調逸，趣遠情深，削盡常言，挾風雅之道，養浩然之氣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>覽者猶聆《韶》、《濩》音，先洗桑濮耳，庶几乎賞音也。有集七十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，《正論》十五卷，《九經分義疏》二十卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">卷二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○包融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    融，延陵人。開元間仕歷大理司直。與參軍殷遙、孟浩然交厚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工為詩。二子何、佶，縱聲雅道，齊名當時，號“三包”。有詩一卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，行世。夫人之于學，苦心難；既苦心，成業難；成業者獲名不朽，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>兼父子兄弟間尤難。歷觀唐人，父子如三包，六竇，張碧、張瀛，顧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>況、非熊，章孝標、章碣，溫庭筠、溫憲；公孫如杜審言、杜甫，錢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>起、錢珝；兄弟如皇甫冉、皇甫曾，李宣古、李宣遠，姚系、姚倫等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>；皆聯玉無瑕，清塵遠播。芝蘭繼芳，重難改于父道；騷雅接響，庶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不慊于祖風。四難之間，揮麈之際，亦可以為美談矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔國輔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>      國輔，山陰人。開元十四年嚴迪榜進士，與儲光羲、綦毋潛同時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。舉縣令，累遷集賢直學士、禮部郎中。天寶間，坐是王珙近親，貶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>竟陵司馬。有文及詩，婉孌清楚，深宜諷詠。樂府短章，古人有不能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>過也。初至竟陵，與處士陸鴻漸游，三歲，交情至厚，謔笑永日。又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相與較定茶水之品。臨別謂羽曰：“予有襄陽太守李瞪所遺白驢、烏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>犎牛各一頭，及盧黃門所遺文槐書函一枚，此物皆己之所惜者，宜野</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人乘蓄，故特以相贈。”雅意高情，一時所尚。有酬酢之歌詩，并集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○盧象</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    象，字緯卿，汶水人，鴻之侄也。攜家來居江東最久。仕為校書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎、左拾遺、膳部員外郎。受安祿山偽官，貶永州司戶參軍。后為主</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>客員外郎。有詩名，譽充秘閣，雅而不素，有大體，得國士之風。集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>二十卷，今傳。同仕有韋述，為桑泉尉。時詔求逸書，命述等編校于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朝元殿。后為翰林學士，有詩名，今亦傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○綦毋潛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    潛，字孝通，荊南人。開元十四年嚴迪榜進士及第。授宜壽尉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遷右拾遺，入集賢院待制，復授校書，終著作郎。與李端同時。詩調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>屹崒峭蒨足佳句，善寫方外之情，歷代未有。荊南分野，數百年來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>獨秀斯人。后見兵亂，官況日惡，挂冠歸隱江東別業。王維有詩送之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，曰：“明時久不達，棄置與君同。天命無怨色，人生有素風。”一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時文士咸賦詩祖餞，甚榮。有集一卷，行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王昌齡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    昌齡，字少伯，太原人。開元十五年李嶷榜進士，授汜水尉。又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中宏辭，遷校書郎。后以不護細行，貶龍標尉。以刀火之際，歸鄉里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，為刺史閭丘曉所忌而殺。后張鎬按軍河南，曉愆期，將戮之，辭以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>親老，乞恕，鎬曰：“王昌齡之親欲與誰養乎“曉大慚沮。昌齡工詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，縝密而思清，時稱“詩家夫子王江寧”，蓋嘗為江寧令。與文士王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之渙、辛漸交友至深，皆出模范，其名重如此。有詩集五卷，又述作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩格律、境思、體例，共十四篇，為《詩格》一卷，又，《詩中密旨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》一卷，及《古樂府解題》一卷，今并傳。自元嘉以還，四百年之內</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，曹、劉、陸、謝，風骨頓盡。逮儲光羲、王昌齡，頗從厥跡，兩賢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>氣同而體別也。王稍聲峻，奇句俊格，驚耳駭目。奈何晚途不矜小節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，謗議騰沸，兩竄遐荒，使知音者喟然長嘆，至歸全之道，不亦痛哉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">。\n    ○常建</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    建，長安人。開元十五年與王昌齡同榜登科。大歷中，授盱眙尉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。仕頗不如意，遂放浪琴酒，往來太白、紫閣諸峰，有肥遯之志。嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>采藥仙谷中，遇女子，遍體毛綠，自言是秦時宮人，亡入山來食松葉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，遂不飢寒，因授建微旨，所養非常。后寓鄂渚，招王昌齡、張僨同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>隱，獲大名當時。集一卷，今傳。古稱高才而無貴仕，誠哉是言。曩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>劉楨死于文學，鮑照卒于參軍，今建亦淪于一尉，悲夫！建屬思既精</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，詞亦警絕，似初發通莊，卻尋野徑，百里之外，方歸大道。旨遠興</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僻，能論意表，可謂一唱而三嘆矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    ○賀蘭進明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    進明，開元十六年虞咸榜進士及第。仕為御史大夫。肅宗時，出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為河南節度使。時祿山群黨未平，嘗帥師屯臨淮備賊，竟亦無功。進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>明好古博雅，經籍滿腹，其所著述一百余篇，頗究天人之際。又有古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩樂府等數十篇，大體符于阮公，皆今所傳者云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔署</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    署，宋州人。少孤貧，不應荐辟，志況疏爽，擇交于方外。苦讀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書，高棲少室山中。與薛據友善。工詩，言詞款要，情興悲涼，送別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、登樓，俱堪淚下。集傳于今也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陶翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    翰，潤州人。開元十八年崔明允下進士及第，次年中博學宏辭，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>與鄭昉同時，官至禮部員外郎。為詩詞筆雙美，既多興象，復備風骨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。三百年以前，方可論其裁制。大為當時所稱。今有集相傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王維</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    維，字摩詰，太原人。九歲知屬辭，工草隸，閑音律。岐王重之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。維將應舉，岐王謂曰：“子詩清越者，可錄數篇，琵琶新聲，能度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一曲，同詣九公主第。”維如其言。是日，諸伶擁維獨奏，主問何名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，曰：“《郁輪袍》。”因出詩卷。主曰：“皆我習諷，謂是古作，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乃子之佳制乎“延于上座曰：“京兆得此生為解頭，榮哉！“力荐之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。開元十九年狀元及第。擢右拾遺，遷給事中。賊陷兩京，駕出幸，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>維扈從不及，為所擒，服藥稱喑病。祿山愛其才，逼至洛陽供舊職，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>拘于普施寺。賊宴凝碧池，悉召梨園諸工合樂，維痛悼，賦詩曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>萬戶傷心生野煙，百官何日再朝天秋槐花落空宮里，凝碧池頭奏管弦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”時聞行在所。賊平后，授偽官者皆定罪，獨維得免。仕至尚書右</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>丞。維詩入妙品上上，畫思亦然。至山水平遠，云勢石色，皆天機所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>到，非學而能。自為詩云：“當代謬詞客，前身應畫師。”后人評維</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“詩中有畫，畫中有詩”，信哉！客有以《按樂圖》示維者，曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此《霓裳》第三疊最初拍也。”對曲果然。篤志奉佛，蔬食素衣。喪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>妻不再娶，孤居三十年。別墅在藍田縣南輞川，亭館相望。嘗自寫其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>景物奇勝，日與文士丘為、裴迪、崔興宗游覽賦詩，琴樽自樂。后表</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>請舍宅以為寺。臨終，作書辭親友，停筆而化。代宗訪維文章，弟縉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集賦詩第十卷上之，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○薛據</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    據，荊南人。開元十九年王維榜進士。天寶六年，又中風雅古調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>科第一人。于吏部參選，據自恃才名，請受萬年錄事。流外官訴宰執</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，以為赤縣是某等清要，據無媒，改涉縣令。后仕歷司議郎，終水部</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎中。據為人骨鯁，有氣魄，文章亦然。嘗自傷不得早達，造句往往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>追凌鮑、謝。初好棲遁，居高山煉藥。晚歲置別業終南山下老焉。有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉長卿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    長卿，字文房，河間人。少居嵩山讀書，后移家來鄱陽最久。開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元二十一年徐征榜及第。至德中，歷監察御史，以檢校祠部員外郎出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為轉運使判官，知淮西岳鄂轉運留后。觀察使吳仲孺誣奏，非罪系姑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蘇獄，久之，貶潘州南巴尉。會有為辯之者，量移睦州司馬。終隨州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刺史。長卿清才冠世，頗凌浮俗，性剛，多忤權門，故兩逢遷斥，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悉冤之。詩調雅暢，甚能煉飾。其自賦，傷而不怨，足以發揮風雅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>權德輿稱為“五言長城”。長卿嘗謂：“今人稱前有沈、宋、王、杜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，后有錢、郎、劉、李。李嘉祐、郎士元何得與余并驅“每題詩不言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>姓，但書“長卿”，以天下無不知其名者云。灞陵碧澗有別業。今集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩賦文等傳世。淮南李穆，有清才，公之婿也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李季蘭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    季蘭，名冶，以字行，峽中人，女道士也。美姿容，神情蕭散。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>專心翰墨，善彈琴，尤工格律。當時才子頗夸纖麗，殊少荒艷之態。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>始年六歲時，作《薔薇詩》云：“經時不架卻，心緒亂縱橫。”其父</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>見曰：“此女聰黠非常，恐為失行婦人。”后以交游文士，微泄風聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，皆出乎輕薄之口。夫士有百行，女唯四德。季蘭則不然，形氣既雄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，詩意亦蕩。自鮑昭以下，罕有其倫。時往來剡中，與山人陸羽、上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人皎然意甚相得。皎然嘗有詩云：“天女來相試，將花欲染衣。禪心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>竟不起，還捧舊花歸。“其謔浪至此。又嘗會諸賢于烏程開元寺，知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>河間劉長卿有陰重之疾，誚曰：“山氣日夕佳。”劉應聲曰：“眾鳥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>欣有托。”舉坐大笑，論者兩美之。天寶間，玄宗聞其詩才，詔赴闕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，留宮中月余，優賜甚厚，遣歸故山。評者謂上比班姬則不足，下比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>韓英則有余，不以遲暮，亦一俊媼。有集，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    論曰：《詩》云，“《關雎》，樂得淑女，以配君子，懮在進賢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不淫其色。哀窈窕，思賢才，而無傷苦之心焉。”故古詩之道，各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>存六義，然終歸于正，不離乎雅。是以昔賢婦人，散情文墨，斑斑簡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>牘。概而論之，后來班姬傷秋扇以暫恩，謝娥詠絮雪而同素；大家《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>七誡》，執者修者；蔡琰《胡笳》，聞而心折。率以明白之操，徽美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之誠，欲見于悠遠，寓文以宣情，含毫而見志，豈泛濫之故，使人擊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節沾洒，彈指追念，良有謂焉。噫！筆墨固非女子之事，亦在用之如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何耳。苟天之可逃，禮不必備，則詞為自獻之具，詩有妒情之作，衣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>服飲食，無閑淨之容，鉛華膏澤，多鮮飾之態，故不相宜矣。是播惡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于眾，何《關雎》之義哉歷觀唐以雅道獎士類，而閨閣英秀，亦能熏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>染，錦心繡口，蕙情蘭性，足可尚矣。中間如李季蘭、魚玄機，皆躍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出方外，修清淨之教，陶寫幽懷，留連光景，逍遙閑暇之功，無非云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>水之念，與名儒比隆，珠往瓊復。然浮艷委托之心，終不能盡，白璧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>微瑕，惟在此耳。薛濤流落歌舞，以靈慧獲名當時，此亦難矣。三者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>既不可略，如劉媛、劉云、鮑君徽、崔仲容、道士元淳、薛縕、崔公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>達、張窈窕、程長文、梁瓊、廉氏、姚月華、裴羽仙、劉瑤、常浩、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>葛鴉兒、崔鶯鶯、譚意哥、戶部侍郎吉中孚妻張夫人、鮑參軍妻文姬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、杜羔妻趙氏、張建封妾盼盼、南楚材妻薛媛等，皆能華藻，才色雙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>美者也。或望幸離宮，傷寵后掖；或以從軍萬里，斷絕音耗；或祗役</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>連年，迢遙風水；或為宕子妻，或為商人婦。花雨春夜，月露秋天，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>玄鳥將謝，賓鴻來屆；搗錦石之流黃，織回文于緗綺，魂夢飛遠，關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山到難。當此時也，濡毫命素，寫怨書懷，一語一聯，俱堪墮淚。至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>若間以丰麗，雜以纖穠，導淫奔之約，敘久曠之情，不假綠琴，但飛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>紅紙，中間不能免焉。尺有短而寸有長，故未欲椎埋之云爾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○閻防</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    防，河中人。開元二十二年李琚榜及第。顏真卿甚敬愛之，欲荐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于朝，不屈。為人好古博雅，詩語真素，魂清魄爽，放曠山水，高情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>獨詣。于終南山丰德寺結茅茨讀書，百丈溪是其隱處，題詩云：“浪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>跡棄人世，還山自幽獨。始傍巢由蹤，吾其獲心曲。”又云：“養閑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>度人事，達命知止足。不學魯國儒，俟時勞伐輻。”后信命，不務進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>取，以此自終。有詩集行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李頎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    頎，東川人。開元二十三年賈季鄰榜進士及第。調新鄉縣尉。性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>疏簡，厭薄世務。慕神仙，服餌丹砂，明輕舉之道，結好塵喧之外。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一時名輩，莫不重之。工詩，發調既清，修詞亦秀，雜歌咸善，玄理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>最長，多為放浪之語，足可震蕩心神。惜其偉材，只到黃綬。故其論</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>家，往往高于眾作。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張諲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    諲，永嘉人。初隱少室下，閉門修肄，志甚勤苦，不及聲利。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>應舉，官到刑部員外郎。明《易•象》，善草隸，兼畫山水，詩格高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>古。與李頎友善，事王維為兄，皆為詩酒丹青之契。維贈詩云：“屏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風誤點惑孫郎，團扇草書驚內史。”李頎贈曰：“小王破體閑支策，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>落月梨花照空壁。詩堪記室妒風流，畫與將軍作勍敵。”天寶中謝官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，歸故山偃仰，不復來人間矣。有詩傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○孟浩然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    浩然，襄陽人。少好節義，詩工五言。隱鹿門山，即漢龐公棲隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>處也。四十游京師，諸名士間嘗集秘省聯句，浩然曰：“微云淡河漢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，疏雨滴梧桐。”眾欽服。張九齡、王維極稱道之。維待詔金鑾，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><h5>旦私邀入，商較風雅，俄報玄宗臨幸，浩然錯笥K，伏匿床下，維不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敢隱，因奏聞。帝喜曰：“朕素聞其人，而未見也。”詔出，再拜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帝問曰：“卿將詩來耶“對曰：“偶不賚。”即命吟近作，誦至“不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才明主棄，多病故人疏“之句，帝慨然曰：“卿不求仕，朕何嘗棄卿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，奈何誣我！”因命放還南山。后張九齡署為從事。開元末，王昌齡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>游襄陽，時新病起，相見甚歡，浪情宴謔，食鮮疾動而終。古稱檷衡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不遇，趙壹無祿。觀浩然磬拆謙退，才名日高，竟淪明代，終身白衣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，良可悲夫！其詩文采丰茸，經緯綿密，半遵雅調，全削凡近。所著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三卷，今傳。王維畫浩然像于郢州，為浩然亭。咸通中，鄭諴謂賢者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名不可斥，更名曰“孟亭”，今存焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○丘為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    為，嘉興人。初累舉不第，歸山讀書數年。天寶初劉單榜進士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王維甚稱許之，嘗與唱和。初，事繼母孝，有靈芝生堂下。累官太子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>右庶子，時年八十余，母猶無恙，給俸祿之半。及居懮觀察使韓滉以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為致仕官給祿，所以惠養老臣，不可在喪為異，唯罷春秋羊酒。初還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄉，縣令謁之，為候門磬折，令坐，乃拜，里胥立庭下，既出，乃敢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>坐。經縣署，降馬而過，舉動有禮。卒年九十六。有集行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    白，字太白，山東人。母夢長庚星而誕，因以命之。十歲通五經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，自夢筆頭生花，后天才贍逸名聞天下。喜縱橫，擊劍為任俠。輕財</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>好施。更客任城，與孔巢父、韓准、裴政、張叔明、陶沔居徂徠山中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，日沉飲，號“竹溪六逸”。天寶初，自蜀至長安，道未振，以所業</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>投賀知章，讀至《蜀道難》，嘆曰：“子謫仙人也。”乃解金龜換酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，終日相樂。遂荐于玄宗，召見金鑾殿，論時事，因奏頌一篇，帝喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，賜食，親為調羹，詔供奉翰林。嘗大醉上前，草詔，使高力士脫靴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，力士恥之，摘其《清平調》中飛燕事，以激怒貴妃，帝每欲與官，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>妃輒沮之。白益傲放，與賀知章、李適之、汝陽王璡、崔宗之、蘇晉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、張旭、焦遂為“飲酒八仙人”。懇求還山，賜黃金，詔放歸。白浮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>游四方，欲登華山，乘醉跨驢經縣治，宰不知，怒，引至庭下曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>汝何人，敢無禮！”白供狀不書姓名，曰：“曾令龍巾拭吐，御手調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>羹，貴妃捧硯，力士脫靴。天子門前，尚容走馬；華陰縣里，不得騎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>驢“宰驚愧，拜謝曰：“不知翰林至此。”白長笑而去。嘗乘舟，與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>崔宗之自采石至金陵，著宮錦袍坐，傍若無人。祿山反，明皇在蜀，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>永王璘節度東南，白時臥廬山，辟為僚佐。璘起兵反，白逃還彭澤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>璘敗，累系潯陽獄。初，白游并州，見郭子儀，奇之，曾救其死罪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至是，郭子儀請官以贖，詔長流夜郎。白晚節好黃、老，度牛渚磯，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乘酒捉月，沉水中。初，悅謝家青山，今墓在焉。有文集二十卷，行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。或云：白，涼武昭王暠九世孫也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○杜甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    甫，字子美，京兆人。審言生閑，閑生甫。少貧不自振，客吳越</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、齊趙間。李邕奇其材，先往見之。舉進士不中第，困長安。天寶十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>載，玄宗朝獻太清宮、饗廟及郊，甫奏賦三篇，帝奇之，使待詔集賢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>院，命宰相試文章。擢河西尉，不拜，改右衛率府胄曹參軍。數上賦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>頌，高自稱道，且言：“先臣恕、預以來，承儒守官十一世，迨審言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以文章顯。臣賴緒業，自七歲屬辭，且四十年，然衣不蓋體，常寄食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于人，竊恐轉死溝壑，伏惟天子哀憐之。若令執先臣故事，拔泥涂久</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>辱，則臣之述作，雖不足鼓吹六經，先鳴數子，至沉郁頓挫，隨時敏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>給，揚雄、枚皋，可企及也。有臣如此，陛下其忍棄之！”會祿山亂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，天子入蜀，甫避走三川。肅宗立，自鄜州羸服欲奔行在，為賊所得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。至德二年，亡走鳳翔，上謁，拜左拾遺。與房琯為布衣交，琯時敗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>兵，又以琴客董廷蘭之故罷相，甫上疏言：“罪細，不宜免大臣。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帝怒，詔三司雜問。宰相張鎬曰：“甫若抵罪，絕言者路。”帝解，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不復問。時所在寇奪，甫家寓鄜，彌年艱窶，孺弱至餓死，因許甫自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>往省視。從還京師，出為華州司功參軍。關輔飢，輒棄官去。客秦州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，負薪拾橡栗自給。流落劍南，營草堂成都西郭浣花溪。召補京兆功</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曹參軍，不至。會嚴武節度劍南西川，往依焉。武再帥劍南，表為參</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謀，檢校工部員外郎。武以世舊，待甫甚善，親詣其家。甫見之，或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時不巾，而性褊躁傲誕，常醉登武床，瞪視曰：“嚴挺之乃有此兒！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”武中銜之。一日，欲殺甫，集吏于門，武將出，冠鉤于帘者三，左</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>右走報其母，力救得止。崔旰等亂，甫往來梓、夔間。大歷中，出瞿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>塘，溯沅、湘以登衡山。因客耒陽，游岳祠，大水暴至，涉旬不得食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，縣令具舟迎之，乃得還，為設牛炙白酒，大醉，一昔卒，年五十九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。甫放曠不自檢，好論天下大事，高而不切也。與李白齊名，時號“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李杜”。數嘗寇亂，挺節無所汙。為歌詩，傷時撓弱，情不忘君，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>皆憐之。墳在岳陽。有集六十卷，及潤州刺史樊晃纂《小集》，今傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。能言者未必能行，能行者未必能言。觀李、杜二公，踦掠洈忽漱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>際，語語王霸，褒貶得失，忠孝之心，驚動千古，騷雅之妙，雙振當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時，兼眾善于無今，集大成于往作，歷世之下，想見風塵。惜乎長轡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>未騁，奇才并屈，竹帛少色，徒列空言，嗚呼哀哉！昔謂杜之典重，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李之飄逸，神聖之際，二公造焉。觀于海者難為水，游李、杜之門者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>難為詩，斯言信哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鄭虔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    虔，鄭州人，高士也。蘇許公為宰相，申以忘年之契，荐為著作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎。嘗以當世事著書八十余篇。有告虔私撰國史者，虔蒼惶焚之，坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謫十年。玄宗愛其才，開元二十五年，為更置廣文館，虔為博士。廣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文博士自虔始。杜甫為交，有贈詩曰：“才名四十年，坐客寒無氈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>惟有蘇司業，時時與酒錢。”其窮飢轗軻，淡如也。好琴酒篇詠，善</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>圖山水。能書，苦無紙，于慈恩寺貯柿葉數屋，遂日就書殆遍。嘗自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寫其詩并畫，表獻之，玄宗大署其尾曰：“鄭虔三絕。”與李、杜為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>密友，多稱鄭廣文。祿山反，偽授水部員外郎，托以疾，不奪。賊平</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，張通、王維并囚系，三人皆善畫，崔圓使繪齋壁，因為祈解，得貶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>台州司戶，卒。有集行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○高適</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    適，字達夫，一字仲武，滄州人。少性拓落，不拘小節，恥預常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>科，隱跡博徒，才名便遠。后舉有道，授封丘尉。未几，哥舒翰表掌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書記。后擢諫議大夫。負氣敢言，權近側目。李輔國忌其才。蜀亂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出為蜀、彭二州刺史，遷西川節度使。還，為左散騎常侍。永泰初卒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。適尚氣節，語王霸，袞袞不厭。遭時多難，以功名自許。年五十，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>始學為詩，即工，以氣質自高，多胸臆間語。每一篇已，好事者輒傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>播吟玩。嘗過汴州，與李白、杜甫會，酒酣登吹台，慷慨悲歌，臨風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>懷古，人莫測也。中間唱和頗多。今有詩文等二十卷，及所選至德迄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大歷述作者二十六人詩，為《中興間氣集》二卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○沈千運</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    千運，吳興人。工舊體詩，氣格高古，當時士流，皆敬慕之，號</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為“沈四山人”。天寶中，數應舉不第，時年齒已邁，遨游襄、鄧間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，干謁名公。來濮上，感懷賦詩曰：“聖朝優賢良，草澤無遺族。人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生各有命，在余胡不淑。一生但區區，五十無寸祿。衰落當捐棄，貧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賤招謗讟。”其時多艱，自知屯蹇，遂浩然有歸歟之志，賦詩曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棲隱無別事，所願離風塵，不來城邑游，禮樂拘束人。”又曰：“如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何巢與由，天子不得臣。”遂釋志，還山中別業。嘗曰：“衡門之下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，可以棲遲。有薄田園，兒稼女織，偃仰今古，自足此生。誰能作小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吏，走風塵下乎“高適賦《還山吟》贈行曰：“還山吟，天高日暮寒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山深。送君還山識君心，人生老大須恣意。看君解作一生事，山間偃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>仰無不至。石泉淙淙若風雨，桂花松子常滿地。賣藥囊中應有錢，還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山服藥又長年。白云勸盡杯中物，明月相隨何處眠。眠時憶同醒時意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，夢魂可以相周旋。”肅宗議備禮征致，會卒而罷。有詩傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○孟云卿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    云卿，關西人。天寶間不第，氣頗難平，志亦高尚，懷嘉遯之節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。與薛據相友善。嘗流寓荊州，杜工部多有與云卿贈答之作，甚愛重</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之。工詩，其體祖述沈千運，漁獵陳拾遺，詞氣傷怨，雖然模效才得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>升堂，猶未入室，然當時古調，無出其右，一時之英也。如“虎豹不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相食，哀哉人食人“；又“朝亦常苦飢，暮亦常苦飢。飄飄萬里余，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貧賤多是非。少年莫遠游，遠游多不歸“；皆為當代推服。韋應物《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>過廣陵遇孟九贈詩》云：“高文激頹波，四海靡不傳。西施且一笑，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>眾女安得妍。”其才名于此可見矣。仕終校書郎。集今傳。云卿稟通</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>濟之才，淪吞噬之俗，棲棲南北，苦無所遇，何生之不辰也。身處江</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>湖，心存魏闕，猶杞國之人懮天墜，相率而逃者，匹夫之志，亦可念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○岑參</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    參，南陽人，文本之后。天寶三年趙岳榜第二人及第。累官左補</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>闕、起居郎，出為嘉州刺史。杜鴻漸表置安西幕府，拜職方郎中，兼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍御史，辭罷。別業在杜陵山中。后終于蜀。參累佐戎幕，往來鞍馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>烽塵間十余載，極征行離別之情，城障寨堡，無不經行。博覽史籍，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尤工綴文，屬詞清尚，用心良苦。詩調尤高，唐興罕見此作。放情山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>水，故常懷逸念，奇造幽致，所得往往超拔孤秀，度越常情。與高適</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風骨頗同，讀之令人慷慨懷感。每篇絕筆，人輒傳詠。至德中，裴休</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、杜甫等嘗荐其識度清遠，議論雅正，佳名早立，時輩所仰，可以備</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>獻替之官。未及大用而謝世，豈不傷哉！有集十卷行于世。杜確為之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>序云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王之渙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    之渙，薊門人。少有俠氣，所從游皆五陵少年，擊劍悲歌，從禽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>縱酒。中折節工文，十年名譽日振。恥困場屋，遂交謁名公。為詩情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>致雅暢，得齊、梁之風。每有作，樂工輒取以被聲律。與王昌齡、高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>適、暢當忘形爾汝。嘗共詣旗亭，有梨園名部繼至，昌齡等曰：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>輩擅詩名，未定甲乙。可觀諸伶謳詩，以多者為優。”一伶唱昌齡二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>絕句，一唱適一絕句。之渙曰：“樂人所唱皆下俚之詞。”須臾，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>佳妓唱曰：“黃河遠上白云間，一片孤城萬仞山。羌笛何須怨楊柳，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>春風不度玉門關。”復唱二絕，皆之渙詞。三子大笑。之渙曰：“田</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舍奴，吾豈妄哉！”諸伶竟不諭其故，拜曰：“肉眼不識神仙。”三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子從之酣醉終日。其狂放如此云。有詩傳于今。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○賀知章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    知章，字季真，會稽人。少以文詞知名，性曠夷，善談論笑謔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>證聖初，擢進士、超拔群類科。陸象先在中書，引為太常博士。象先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>與知章最親善，常曰：“季真清談風韻，吾一日不見，則鄙吝生矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”當時賢達，皆傾慕之。為太子賓客。開元十三年，遷禮部侍郎兼集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賢院學士。晚年尤加縱誕，無復禮度，自號“四明狂客”，又稱“秘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書外監”，遨游里巷。又善草隸，每醉輒屬詞，筆不停輟，咸有可觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，每紙不過數十字，好事者共傳寶之。天寶三年，因病，夢游帝居，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及寤，表請為道士，求還鄉里，即舍住宅為千秋觀，上許之。詔賜鏡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>湖剡溪一曲，以給漁樵。帝賦詩及太子、百官祖餞。壽八十六。集今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>  ○包何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    何，字幼嗣，潤州延陵人，包融之子也。與弟佶，俱以詩鳴，時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>稱“二包”。天寶七年楊譽榜及第。曾師事孟浩然，授格法。與李嘉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>祐相友善。大歷中，仕終起居舍人。詩傳者可數，蓋流離世故，率多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>素辭。大播芳名，亦當時望族也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○包佶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    佶，字幼正。天寶六年楊護榜進士。累遷秘書監。劉晏治財，奏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為汴東兩稅使。及晏罷，以佶為諸道鹽鐵等使。未几，遷刑部侍郎、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>太常少卿，拜諫議大夫、御史中丞。居官謹確，所在有聲。佶天才贍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>逸，氣宇清深，神和大雅，詩家老斫輪也。與劉長卿、竇叔向諸公皆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>莫逆之愛。晚歲沾風痺之疾，辭寵樂高，不及榮利。卒封丹陽郡公。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有詩集行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○張彪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    彪，潁上人。初赴舉，無所遇，適遭喪亂，奉老母避地隱居嵩山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，供養至謹。與孟云卿為中表，俱工古調詩。云卿有贈云：“善道居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貧賤，潔服蒙塵埃。行行無定心，坎壈難歸來。”性高簡，善草書。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>志在輕舉，《詠神仙》云：“五谷非長年，四氣乃靈藥。列子何必待</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，吾心滿寥廓。”時與杜甫往還，嘗《寄張十二山人》詩云：“靜者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>心多妙，先生藝絕倫。草書何太古，詩興不無神。曹植休前輩，張芝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>更后身。數篇吟可老，一字買堪貧。”觀工部之作，可知其人矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李嘉祐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嘉祐，字從一，趙州人。天寶七年楊譽榜進士，為秘書正字。以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>罪謫南荒，未几何，有詔量移為鄱陽宰，又為江陰令。后遷台、袁二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>州刺史。善為詩，綺麗婉靡，與錢、郎別為一體，往往涉于齊、梁時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風，人擬為吳均、何遜之敵。自振藻天朝，大收芳譽，中興風流也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○賈至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    至，字幼几，洛陽人，曾之子也。曾開元間與蘇晉同掌制誥。至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天寶十年明經擢第，累官起居舍人，知制誥。從幸西川，當撰傳位肅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宗冊文，既進稿，玄宗曰：“先天誥命，乃父所為。今茲大冊，爾又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為之。兩朝盛典，出卿家父子，可謂繼美矣。”大歷初，遷京兆尹，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以散騎常侍卒。初，嘗以事謫守巴陵，與李白相遇，日酣杯酒，追憶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>京華舊游，多見酬唱。白贈詩有云：“聖主恩深漢文帝，憐君不遣到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>長沙。”至特工詩，俊逸之氣，不減鮑昭、庾信。調亦清暢，且多素</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>辭，蓋厭于漂流淪落者也。有集三十余卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○鮑防</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    防，字子慎，天寶十二年楊儇榜進士，襄陽人也。善辭章，篤志</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于學。累官至太原尹、河東節度使。人樂其治，不減龔、黃，詔圖形</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>別殿。又歷福建、江西觀察使。丁亂，從幸奉天，除禮部侍郎，封東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>海公。又遷御史大夫。貞元元年，策賢良方正，得穆質、柳公綽等，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>皆位至台鼎，世美其知人。時比歲旱，質對：漢故事，免三公，烹弘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>羊。權近獨孤愐欲下按治，防曰：“使上聞所未聞，不亦善乎“置質</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>高第，帝見策嘉之。授工部尚書，卒。防工于詩，興思優足，風調嚴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>整，凡有感發，以譏切世弊，正國音之宗派也。與謝良弼為詩友，時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亦稱鮑、謝云。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>  ○殷遙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    遙，丹陽人。天寶間，嘗仕為忠王府倉曹參軍。與王維結交，同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>慕禪寂，志趣高疏，多云岫之想。而苦家貧，死不能葬，一女才十歲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，日哀號于親，愛憐之者賵贈，埋骨石樓山中。工詩，詞彩不群，而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多警句，杜甫嘗稱許之。有詩傳于今。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張繼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    繼，字懿孫，襄州人。天寶十二年禮部侍郎楊浚下及第。與皇甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>冉有髫年之故，契逾昆玉。早振詞名。初來長安，頗矜氣節，有《感</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>懷》詩云：“調與時人背，心將靜者論。終年帝城里，不識五侯門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”嘗佐鎮戎軍幕府，又為鹽鐵判官。大歷間，入內侍，仕終檢校祠部</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎中。繼博覽有識，好談論，知治體，亦嘗領郡，輒有政聲。詩情爽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>激，多金玉音。蓋其累代詞伯，積襲弓裘，其于為文，不雕自飾，丰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>姿清迥，有道者風。集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○元結</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    結，字次山，武昌人。魯山令元紫芝族弟也。少不羈，弱冠始折</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節讀書。天寶十三年進士。禮部侍郎楊浚見其文曰：“一第慁子耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”遂擢高品。后舉制科。會天下亂，沉浮人間，蘇源明荐于肅宗，授</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>右金吾兵曹。累遷御史，參山南來瑱府，除容管經略使。始隱商於山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，稱“元子”。逃難入猗玗洞，稱“猗玗子”。或稱浪士，漁者或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>稱聱叟，酒徒呼“漫叟”。及為官，呼漫郎。皆以命所著。性梗僻，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>深憎薄俗，有懮道閔世之心。《中興頌》一文，燦爛金石，清奪湘流</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。作詩著辭，尚聱牙。天下皆知敬仰。復嗜酒，有句云：“有時逢惡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>客。”自注：“非酒徒，即惡客也。”有《文編》十卷，及所集當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人詩為《篋中集》一卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○郎士元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    士元，字君胄，中山人也。天寶十五載盧庚榜進士。寶應初，選</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>京畿縣官。詔試政事中書，補渭南尉，歷左拾遺，出為郢州刺史。與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>員外郎錢起齊名。時朝廷自丞相以下，出牧奉使，無兩君詩文祖餞，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人以為愧，其珍重如此。二公體調，大抵欲同，就中郎君稍更閑雅，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>逼近康樂。珠聯玉映，不覺成編，掩映時流，名不虛矣。有別業在半</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>日吳村，王季友、錢起等皆見題詠，每夸勝絕。詩集今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○道人靈一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    一公，剡中人。童子出家，瓶缽之外，余無有。天性超穎，追蹤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謝客，隱麻源第三谷中，結茆讀書。后白業精進，居若耶溪云門寺，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>從學者四方而至矣。尤工詩，氣質淳和，格律清暢。兩浙名山，暨衡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、廬諸甲剎，悉所經行。與皇甫昆季、嚴少府、朱山人、徹上人等為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩友，酬贈甚多。刻意聲調，苦心不倦，騁譽叢林。后順寂于岑山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集今傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    論曰：自齊、梁以來，方外工文者，如支遁、道遒、惠休、寶月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之儔，馳驟文苑，沉淫藻思，奇章偉什，綺錯星陳，不為寡矣。厥后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>喪亂，兵革相尋，緇素亦已狼藉，罕有復入其流者。至唐累朝，雅道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大振，古風再作，率皆崇衷像教，駐念津梁，龍象相望，金碧交映。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雖寂寥之山河，實威儀之淵藪。寵光優渥，無逾此時。故有顛頓文場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之人，憔悴江海之客，往往裂冠裳，撥矰繳，杳然高邁，云集蕭齋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一食自甘，方袍便足，靈台澄皎，無事相干，三余有簡牘之期，六時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>分吟諷之隙。青峰瞰門，綠水周舍，長廊步□，幽徑尋真，景變序遷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，蕩入冥思。凡此數者，皆達人雅士，夙所欽懷，雖則心侔跡殊，所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>趣無間。會稽傳孫、許之玄談，廬阜接謝、陶于白社，宜其日鍛月煉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，志彌厲而道彌精。佳句縱模，不廢禪定，岩穴相邇，更唱迭酬，苦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于三峽猿，清同九皋鶴，不其偉歟。與夫迷津畏途，埋玉世慮，蓄憤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于心，發在篇詠者，未可同年而論矣。然道或淺深，價有輕重，未能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悉采。其喬松于灌莽，野鶴于雞群者，有靈一、靈徹、皎然、清塞、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無可、虛中、齊己、貫休八人，皆東南產秀，共出一時，已為錄實。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其或雖以多而寡稱，或著少而增價者，如惟審、護國、文益、可止、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>清江、法照、廣宣、無本、修睦、無悶、太易、景云、法振、棲白、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>隱巒、處默、卿云、棲一、淡交、良乂、若虛、云表、曇域、子蘭、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僧鸞、懷楚、惠標、可朋、懷浦、慕幽、善生、亞齊、尚顏、棲蟾、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>理瑩、歸仁、玄寶、惠侃、法宣、文秀、僧泚、清尚、智暹、滄浩、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不特第四十五人，名既隱僻，事且微冥，今不復喋喋云爾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○皇甫冉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    冉，字茂政，安定人。避地來寓丹陽，耕山釣湖，放適閑淡。或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云秘書少監彬之侄也。十歲能屬文，張九齡一見，嘆以清才。天寶十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>五年盧庚榜進士。調無錫尉，營別墅陽羨山中。大歷初，王縉為河南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節度，辟掌書記，后入為左金吾衛兵曹參軍，仕終拾遺、左補闕。公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自擢桂禮闈，便稱高格。往以世道艱虞，遂心江外，故多飄薄之嘆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>每文章一到朝廷，而作者變色，當年才子，悉願締交，推為宗伯。至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其造語玄微，端可平揖沈、謝，雄視潘、張。惜乎長轡未騁，芳蘭早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>凋，良可痛哉！有詩集三卷，獨孤及為序，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○皇甫曾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    曾，字孝常，冉之弟也。天寶十二年楊儇榜進士。善詩，出王維</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之門。與兄名望相亞，當時以比張氏景陽、孟陽，協居上品，載處下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>流，侍御、補闕，文詞亦然。體制清緊，華不勝文，為士林所尚。仕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷侍御史。后坐事貶舒州司馬，量移陽翟令。有詩一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○獨孤及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    及，字至之，河南人。丱角時，誦《孝經》，父試之曰：“爾志</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何語“曰：“立身行道，揚名于后世。”天寶末，以道舉高第，代宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>召為左拾遺。遷禮部員外郎，歷濠、舒、常三州刺史。及性孝友，喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鑒拔，為文必彰明善惡，長于議論。工詩，格調高古，風塵迥絕，得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大名當時。有集傳世。嘗讀《選》中沈、謝諸公詩，有題《新安江水</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至清淺深見底貽京邑游好》及《石門新營所住四面高山回溪石瀨茂林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>修竹》及《田南樹園激流植援》、《齋中讀書》、《南樓中望所遲客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》、《晚登三山還望京邑》等數端，皆奇崛精當，冠絕古今，無曾發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其韞奧者。逮盛唐，沈、宋、獨孤及、李嘉祐、韋應物等諸才子集中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，往往各有數題，片言不苟，皆不減其風度，此則無傳之妙。逮元和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以下，佳題尚罕，況于詩乎！立題乃詩家切要，貴在卓絕清新，言簡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而意足，句之所到，題必盡之，中無失節，外無余語，此可與智者商</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>搉云，因舉而論之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉方平</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    方平，河南人。白皙美容儀。二十工詞賦，與元魯山交善。隱居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>潁陽大谷，尚高不仕。皇甫冉、李頎等相與贈答，有云：“籬邊潁陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>道，竹外少姨峰。”神意淡泊。善畫山水，墨妙無前。汧國公李勉延</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至齋中，甚敬愛之。欲荐于朝，不忍屈，辭還舊隱。工詩，多悠遠之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>思，陶寫性靈，默會風雅，故能脫略世故，超然物外。區區斗筲，何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>足以系劉先生哉！有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○秦系</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    系，字公緒，會稽人。天寶末，避亂剡溪，自稱“東海釣客”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>北都留守薛兼訓奏為倉曹參軍，不就。客泉州，南安九日山中有大松</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>百余章，俗傳東晉時所植，系結廬其上，穴石為研，注《老子》，彌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年不出。時姜公輔以直言罷為泉州別駕，見系輒窮日不能去，筑室與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相近，遂忘流落之苦。公輔卒，妻子在遠，系為營葬山下，每好義如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此。張建封聞系不可致，請就加校書郎。與劉長卿、韋應物善，多以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩相贈答。權德輿曰：“長卿自以為五言長城，系用偏師攻之矣。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雖老益壯，年八十余卒。南安人思之，號其山為“高士峰”，今有“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>麗句亭“在焉。集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張眾甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    眾甫，京口人。隱居不務進取，與皇甫御史友善，精廬接近。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>各游四方，曾寄處士詩曰：“伏臘同雞黍，柴門閉雪天。”時宦亦有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>征辟者，守死善道，卒不就。眾甫詩婉媚綺錯，巧用文字，工于興喻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，文流中佳士也。同在一時者，有趙微明、于逖、蔣渙、元季川，俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山顛水涯，苦學貞士，名同蘭茞之芳，志非銀黃之慕。吟詠性靈，陶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陳衷素，皆有佳篇，不能湮落。惜其行藏之大概，不見于記錄，故缺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其考詳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○嚴維</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    維，字正文，越州人。初，隱居桐廬，慕子陵之高風。至德二年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，江淮選補使侍郎崔渙下以詞藻宏麗進士及第，以家貧親老，不能遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>離，授諸暨尉，時已四十余。后歷秘書郎。嚴中丞節度河南，辟佐幕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>府。遷余姚令。仕終右補闕。維少無宦情，懷家山之樂。以儒素從升</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>斗之祿，聊代耕耳。詩情雅重，挹魏晉之風，鍛煉鏗鏘，庶少遺恨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一時名輩，孰匪金蘭。詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○于良史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    良史，至德中仕為侍御史。詩體清雅，工于形似，又多警句。蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其珪璋特達，早步清朝，興致不群，詞苑增價。雖平生似昧，而篇什</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○靈徹上人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    靈徹，姓湯氏，字澄源，會稽人。自童子辭父兄入淨，戒行果潔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。方便讀書，便覺勤苦，授詩法于嚴維，遂藉藉有聲。及維卒，乃抵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吳興，與皎然居何山游講。因以書荐于包侍郎佶，佶得之大喜；又以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書致于李侍郎紓。時二公以文章風韻為世宗。貞元中，西游京師，名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>振輦下。緇流疾之，遂造飛語激動中貴，因誣奏得罪，徙汀洲。會赦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，歸東越。時吳、楚間諸侯，各賓禮招延之。元和十一年，終于宣州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>開元寺，年七十有一。門人遷歸，建塔于山陰天柱峰下。上人詩多警</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>句，能備眾體。如《芙蓉寺》云：“經來白馬寺，僧到赤烏年。”《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謫汀州》云：“青蠅為吊客，黃耳寄家書。”性巧逸，居沃洲寺，嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>取桐葉剪刻制器為蓮花漏，置盆水之上，穿細孔漏水，半之則沉，每</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>晝夜十二沉，為行道之節。初居嵩陽蘭若，后來住匡廬東林寺。如天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>目、四明、棲霞及衡、湘諸名山，行錫几遍。嘗與靈一上人約老天台</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，未得遂志。雖結念云壑，而才名拘牽，罄息經微，吟諷無已，所謂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>拔乎其萃，游方之外者也。有集十卷，及錄大歷至元和中名人《酬唱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集》十卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陸羽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    羽，字鴻漸，不知所生。初，竟陵禪師智積得嬰兒于水濱，育為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>弟子。及長，恥從削發，以《易》自筮，得《蹇》之《漸》曰：“鴻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>漸于陸，其羽可用為儀。”始為姓名。有學，愧一事不盡其妙。性詼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>諧，少年匿優人中，撰《談笑》萬言。天寶間，署羽伶師，后遁去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>古人謂“潔其行而穢其跡“者也。上元初，結廬苕溪上，閉門讀書。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名僧高士，談宴終日。貌寢，口吃而辯。聞人善，若在己。與人期，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雖阻虎狼不避也。自稱“桑苧翁”，又號“東崗子”。工古調歌詩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>興極閑雅。著書甚多。扁舟往來山寺，唯紗巾藤鞋，短褐犢鼻，擊林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>木，弄流水。或行曠野中，誦古詩，裴回至月黑，興盡慟哭而返。當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時以比接輿也。與皎然上人為忘言之交。有詔拜太子文學。羽嗜茶，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>造妙理，著《茶經》三卷，言茶之原、之法、之具，時號“茶仙”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天下益知飲茶矣。鬻茶家以瓷陶羽形，祀為神，買十茶器，得一鴻漸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初，御史大夫李季卿宣慰江南，喜茶，知羽，召之。羽野服絜具而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>入，李曰：“陸君善茶，天下所知。揚子中泠水，又殊絕。今二妙千</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>載一遇，山人不可輕失也。”茶畢，命奴子與錢。羽愧之，更著《毀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>茶論》。與皇甫補闕善。時鮑尚書防在越，羽往依焉，冉送以序曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“君子究孔、釋之名理，窮歌詩之麗則。遠野孤島，通舟必行；魚梁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>釣磯，隨意而往。夫越地稱山水之鄉，轅門當節鉞之重。鮑侯知子愛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子者，將解衣推食，豈徒嘗鏡水之魚，宿耶溪之月而已。”集并《茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>經》今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○顧況</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    況，字逋翁，蘇州人。至德二年，天子幸蜀，江東侍郎李希言下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>進士。善為歌詩，性詼諧，不修檢操，工畫山水。初為韓晉公江南判</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>官。德宗時，柳渾輔政，荐為秘書郎。況素善于李泌，遂師事之，得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其服氣之法，能終日不食。及泌相，自謂當得達官，久之，遷著作郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。及泌卒，作《海鷗詠》嘲誚權貴，大為所嫉，被憲劾貶饒州司戶，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作詩曰：“萬里飛來為客鳥，曾蒙丹鳳借枝柯。一朝鳳去梧桐死，滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>目鴟鳶奈爾何！”遂全家去，隱茅山，煉金拜斗，身輕如羽。況暮年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一子即亡，追悼哀切，吟曰：“老人喪愛子，日暮泣成血。老人年七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>十，不作多時別。”其年又生一子，名非熊，三歲始言，在冥漠中聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>父吟苦，不忍，乃來復生。非熊后及第，自長安歸慶，已不知況所在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。或云，得長生訣仙去矣。今有集二十卷傳世，皇甫湜為之序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○張南史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    南史，字季直，幽州人。工弈棋，神算無敵，游心太極。嘗幅巾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>藜杖，出入王侯之宅十年，高談闊視，慷慨奇士也。中歲感激，始苦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節學文，無希世苟合之意。數年間，稍入詩境，調體超閑，情致兼美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，如并、燕老將，氣韻沉雄，時少及之者。肅宗時，廟堂獎拔，仕為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>左衛倉曹參軍。后避亂寓居揚州揚子。難平再召，未及赴而卒。有詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○戎昱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    昱，荊南人。美風度，能談。少舉進士不上，乃放游名都。雖貧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士而軒昂，氣不消沮。愛湖湘山水，來客。時李夔廉察桂林，寓官舍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，月夜聞鄰居行吟之音清麗，遲明訪之，乃昱也。即延為幕賓，待之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甚厚。崔中丞亦在湖南，愛之，有女國色，欲以妻昱，而不喜其姓戎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，能改則訂議。昱聞之，以詩謝云：“千金未必能移姓，一諾從來許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>殺身。”自謂李大夫恩私至深，無任感激。初事顏平原，嘗佐其征南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>幕，亦累荐之。衛伯玉鎮荊南，辟為從事。歷虔州刺史。至德中，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>罪謫為辰州刺史。后客劍南，寄家隴西數載。憲宗時，邊烽累急，大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>臣議和親。上曰：“比聞一詩人姓名稍僻者為誰“宰相對以冷朝陽、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>包子虛，皆非。帝舉其詩，對曰：“戎昱也。“上曰：“嘗記其《詠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>史》云：‘漢家青史上，拙計是和親。社稷依明主，安危托婦人。豈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能將玉貌，便擬淨沙塵地下千年骨，誰為輔佐臣！’”因笑曰：“魏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>絳何其懦也此人如在，可與武陵桃花源足稱其清詠。”士林榮之。昱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩在盛唐，格氣稍劣，中間有絕似晚作。然風流綺麗，不虧政化，當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時賞音，喧傳翰苑，固不誣矣。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○古之奇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    之奇，寶應二年禮部侍郎洪源下及第，與耿水韋同時。嘗為安西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>幕府書記。與李司馬端有金蘭之好。工古調，足幽閑淡泊之思，婉而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>成章，得名藝圃，不泛然矣。詩集傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○蘇渙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    渙，廣德二年楊棲梧榜進士。本不平者，往來剽盜，善用白弩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>巴賨商人苦之，稱曰“白跖”。后自知非，折節從學，遂成名。累遷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍御史。湖南崔中丞瓘辟為從事。瓘遇害，繼走交、廣，扇動哥舒晃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>跋扈，如蛟龍見血，本質彰矣。居無何，伏誅。初嘗為《變律詩》十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>九首，上廣州節度李勉，其文章長于諷刺，亦有陳拾遺一鱗半甲，故</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>加待之。或曰：“此子羽冀嬖臣，侵敗王略，今尚其文，可歟“勉曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“漢策載蒯通說辭，皇史錄祖君檄草，此大容細者。善惡必書，《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>春秋》至訓；明言不廢，孔子格談。渙其庶乎，豈但存雕虫小技，亦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以深懲賊子也。”時以為名言。杜甫有與贈答之詩，今悉傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○朱灣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    灣，字巨川，大歷時隱君也，號滄洲子。率履貞素，潛輝不曜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>逍遙云山琴酒之間，放浪形骸繩檢之外。郡國交征，不應。工詩，格</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>體幽遠，興用弘深，寫意因詞，窮理盡性，尤精詠物，必含比興，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敏捷之奇。及李勉鎮永平，嘉其風操，厚幣邀來，署為府中從事，日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相談宴，分逾骨肉。久之。嘗謁湖州崔使君，不得志，臨發以書別之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“灣聞蓬萊山藏杳冥間，行可到，貴人門無媒通不可到；驪龍珠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>潛滉瀇之淵或可識，貴人顏無因而前不可識。自假道路，問津主人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一身孤云，兩度圓月，載請執事，三趨戟門。信知庭之與堂，不啻千</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>里。況寄食漂母，夜眠漁舟，門如龍而難登，食如玉而難得。食如玉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之粟，登如龍之門，實無機心，翻成機事，漢陰丈人聞之，豈不大笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>屬溪上風便，囊中金貧，望甘棠而嘆，自引分而退。灣白。”遂歸會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>稽山陰別墅，其耿介類如此也。有集四卷，今傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張志和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    志和，字子同，婺州人。初名龜齡，詔改之。十六擢明經，嘗以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>策干肅宗，特見賞重，命待詔翰林。以親喪辭去，不復仕。居江湖，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>性邁不束，自稱“煙波釣徒”。撰《玄真子》二卷，又為號焉。兄鶴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>齡恐其遁世，為筑室越州東郭，茅茨數椽，花竹掩映，嘗豹席棕屩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>沿溪垂釣，每不投餌，志不在魚也。觀察使陳少游頻往候問。帝嘗賜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奴、婢各一人，志和配為夫婦，號漁童、樵青。與陸羽嘗為顏平原食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>客。平原初來刺湖州，志和造謁，顏請以舟敝，欲為更之，曰：“願</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為浮家泛宅，往來苕、霅間足矣。”善畫山水，酒酣或擊鼓吹笛，舐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>筆輒就，曲盡天真。自撰《漁歌》，便復畫之。興趣高遠，人不能及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。憲宗聞之，詔寫真求訪，并其歌詩，不能致。后傳一旦忽乘云鶴而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去。李德裕稱以為“漁父賢而名隱，鴟夷智而功高，未若玄真隱而名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>彰，方而無事，不窮而達，其嚴光之比歟”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○盧綸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    綸，字允言，河中人。避天寶亂，來客鄱陽。大歷初，數舉進士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不入第。元載素賞重，取其文進之，補閿鄉尉。累遷檢校戶部郎中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>監察御史。稱疾去。渾瑊鎮河中，就家禮起為元帥判官。初，舅韋渠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>牟得幸德宗，因表其才，召見禁中，帝有所作，輒賡和。至是，帝忽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>問渠牟：“盧綸、李益何在“對曰：“綸從渾瑊在河中。”詔令驛召</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，會卒。綸與吉中孚、韓翃、耿湋、錢起、司空曙、苗發、崔峒、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>夏侯審、李端，聯藻文林，銀黃相望，且同臭味，契分俱深，時號大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷十才子。唐之文體，至此一變矣。綸所作特勝，不減盛時，如三河</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>少年，風流自賞。文宗雅愛其詩，問宰相：“綸沒后，文章几何亦有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子否“李德裕對：“綸四子皆擢進士，仕在台閣。”帝遣中使悉索其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>巾笥，得詩五百首進之。有別業在終南山中。集十卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○吉中孚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    中孚，楚州人。居鄱陽最久。初為道士，山阿寂寥。后還俗。李</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>端贈詩云：“舊山連藥賣，孤鶴帶云歸。”盧綸送詩云：“舊菉藏云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>穴，新詩滿帝鄉。”來長安，謁宰相，有荐于天子，日與王侯高會，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名動京師。無几何，第進士，授萬年尉，除校書郎。又登宏辭科，為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翰林學士，歷諫議大夫，戶部侍郎、判度支事。貞元初卒。初，拜官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后，以親垂白在堂，歸養至孝，終喪復仕。中孚神骨清虛，吟詠高雅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，若神仙中人也。集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韓翃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    翃，字君平，南陽人。天寶十三載楊紘榜進士。侯希逸素重其才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，至是表佐淄青幕府。罷，閑居十年。及李勉在宣武，復辟之。德宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時，制誥闕人，中書兩進除目，御筆不點，再請之，批曰：“與韓翃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”時有同姓名者為江淮刺史，宰相請孰與。上復批曰：“春城無處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不飛花韓翃也。”俄以駕部郎中知制誥。終中書舍人。翃工詩，興致</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>繁富，如芙蓉出水，一篇一詠，朝士珍之。比諷深于文房，筋節成于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>茂政，當時盛稱焉。有詩集五卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○耿湋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    湋，河東人也。寶應二年洪源榜進士。與古之奇為莫逆之交。初</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為大理司法，充括圖書使來江淮，窮山水之勝。仕終左拾遺。詩才俊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>爽，意思不群。似湋等輩，不可多得。詩集二卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○錢起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    起，字仲文，吳興人。天寶十年李巨卿榜及第。少聰敏，承鄉曲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之譽。初從計吏至京口客舍，月夜閑步，聞戶外有行吟聲，哦曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曲終人不見，江上數峰青。”凡再三往來，起遽從之，無所見矣。嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>怪之。及就試粉闈，詩題乃《湘靈鼓瑟》，起輟就，即以鬼謠十字為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>落句，主文李暐深嘉美，擊節吟味久之，曰：“是必有神助之耳。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遂擢置高第。釋褐授校書郎。嘗采箭竹，奉使入蜀。除考功郎中。大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷中為太清宮使、翰林學士。起詩體制新奇，理致清贍，芟宋、齊之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>浮游，削梁、陳之嫚靡，迥然獨立也。王右丞許以高格，與郎士元齊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名，士林語曰：“前有沈、宋，后有錢、郎。”集十卷，今傳。子徽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能詩，外甥懷素善書，一門之中，藝名森出，可尚矣。凡唐人燕集祖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>送，必探題分韻賦詩，于眾中推一人擅場者。劉相巡察江淮，詩人滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>座，而起擅場。郭曖尚主盛會，李端擅場。緬懷盛時，往往文會，群</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賢畢集，觥籌亂飛，遇江山之佳麗，繼歡好于疇昔，良辰美景，賞心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>樂事，于此能并矣。況賓無絕纓之嫌，主無投轄之困，歌闌舞作，微</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聞香澤，冗長之禮，豁略去之，王公不覺其大，韋布不覺其小，忘形</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>爾汝，促席談諧，吟詠繼來，揮毫驚座。樂哉！古人有秉燭夜游，所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謂非淺，同宴一室，無及干亂，豈不盛也！至若殘杯冷炙，一獻百拜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，察喜怒于眉睫之間者，可以休矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○司空曙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    曙，字文明，廣平人也。磊落有奇才。韋皋節度劍南，辟致幕府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。授洛陽主薄，未几遷長林縣丞。累官左拾遺，終水部郎中。與李約</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>員外至交。性耿介，不干權要。家無儋石，晏如也。嘗病中不給，遣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其愛姬，亦自流寓長沙。遷謫江右，多結契雙林，暗傷流景。《寄暕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>上人》詩云：“欲就東林寄一身，尚憐兒女未成人。柴門客去殘陽在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，藥圃虫喧秋雨頻。近水方同梅市隱，曝衣多笑阮家貧。深山蘭若何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時到，羨與閑云作四鄰。”閑園即事，高興可知。屬調幽閑，終篇調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>暢，如新花笑日，不容熏染。鏘鏘美譽，不亦宜哉！有詩集二卷，今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○苗發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    發，潞洲人也。晉卿長子。初為東平令，授兵部員外，遷駕部員</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外郎，仕終都官郎中。雖名齒才子，少見詩篇。當時名士，咸與贈答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔峒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    峒，博陵人。工文有價。初辟潞府功曹，后歷左拾遺，終右補闕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。詞彩炳然，意思方雅，時人稱其句為披沙揀金，往往見寶。詩集一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，今行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○夏侯審</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    審，建中元年禮部侍郎令狐峘下試軍謀越眾科第一。釋褐授校書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎，又為參軍，仕終侍御史。初于華山下多買田園為別墅，水木幽閟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，云煙浩渺，晚歲退居其下，諷吟頗多。今稍零落，時見一二，皆錦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>制也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李端</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    端，趙州人，嘉祐之侄也。少時居廬山，依皎然讀書，意況清虛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，酷慕禪侶。大歷五年李搏榜進士及第，授秘書省校書郎。以清羸多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>病，辭官，居終南山草堂寺。未几，起為杭州司馬，牒訴敲朴，心甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>厭之。買田園在虎丘下，為耽深癖，泉石少幽，移家來隱衡山，自號</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>衡岳幽人。彈琴讀《易》，登高望遠，神意泊然。初元宦情，懷箕、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>潁之志。嘗曰：“余少尚神仙，且未能去。友人暢當以禪門見導，余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>心知必是，未得其門。”詩更高雅，于才子中名響錚錚。與處士京兆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>柳中庸、大理評事江東張芬友善唱酬。初來長安，詩名大振。時令公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子郭曖尚升平公主，賢明有才，延納俊士，端等皆在館中。曖嘗進官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，大宴酒酣，主屬端賦詩，頃刻而就，曰：“青春都尉最風流，二十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>功成便拜侯。金距斗雞過上苑，玉鞭騎馬出長楸。熏香荀令偏憐小，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傅粉何郎不解愁。日暮吹簫楊柳陌，路人遙指鳳皇樓。”主甚喜，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>座賞嘆。錢起曰：“此必端宿制，請以起姓為韻。”端立獻一章曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“方塘似鏡草芊芊，初月如鉤未上弦。新開金埒看調馬，舊踢銅山許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鑄錢。楊柳入樓吹玉笛，芙蓉出水妒花鈿。今朝都尉如相顧，願脫長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>裾逐少年。”作者驚伏。主厚賜金帛，終身以榮，其工捷類此。集三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇叔向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    叔向，字遺直，扶風平陵人也。有卓絕之行，登第于大歷初，遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>振嘉名，為文物冠冕。詩法謹嚴，又非常格。一流才子，多仰飆塵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>少與常袞同燈火，及袞相，引擢左拾遺、內供奉。及坐貶，亦出為溧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>水令。卒，贈工部尚書。五子：常、牟、群、庠、鞏，俱能詩，咄咄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有跨灶之譽，當時羨之。《藝文志》載《叔向集》七卷，今存詩甚寡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，蓋零落之矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○康洽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    洽，酒泉人，黃須美丈夫也。盛時攜琴劍來長官，謁當道，氣度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>豪爽。工樂府詩篇，宮女梨園，皆寫于聲律。玄宗亦知名，嘗嘆美之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。所出入皆王侯貴主之宅，從游與宴，雖駿馬蒼頭如其己有。觀服玩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之光，令人歸欲燒物，憐才乃能如是也。后遭天寶亂離，飄蓬江表。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至大歷間，年已七十余，龍鐘衰老，談及開元繁盛，流涕無從。往來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>兩京，故侯館谷空，咸陽一布衣耳。于時文士願與論交。李端逢之，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>贈詩云：“聲名常壓鮑參軍，班位不過揚執戟。”又云：“同時獻賦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人皆盡，共壁題詩君獨在。”后卒杜陵山中。文章不得見矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李益</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    益，字君虞，隴西姑臧人。大歷四年齊映榜進士，調鄭縣尉。同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>輩行稍進達，益久不升，郁郁去游燕、趙間，幽州節度劉濟辟為從事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，未几，又佐邠寧幕府。風流有詞藻，與宗人賀相埒，每一篇就，樂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工賂求之，被于雅樂，供奉天子。如《征人》、《早行》篇，天下皆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>施繪畫。二十三受策秩，從軍十年，運籌決勝，尤其所長。往往鞍馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>間為文，橫槊賦詩，故多抑揚激厲悲離之作，高適、岑參之流也。憲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宗雅聞其名，召為秘書少監、集賢殿學士。自負其才，凌轢士眾，有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不能堪，諫官因暴其詩“不上望京樓“等句，以涉怨望，詔降職。俄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>復舊，除侍御史，遷禮部尚書致仕。太和初卒。益少有僻疾，多猜忌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，防閑妻妾，過為苛酷，有散灰扃戶之談，時稱為“妒痴尚書李十郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”。有同姓名者，為太子庶子，皆在朝，人恐莫辨，謂君虞為“文章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李益”，庶子為“門戶李益“云。有集，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○冷朝陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    朝陽，金陵人。大歷四年齊映榜進士及第。不待調官，言歸省覲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。自狀元以下，一時名士大夫及詩人李嘉祐、李端、韓翃、錢起等，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大會賦詩攀餞。以一布衣，才名如此，人皆羨之。朝陽工詩，在大歷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>諸才子，法度稍弱，字韻清越不減也。有集傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○章八元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    八元，睦州桐廬人。少喜為詩，嘗于郵亭偶題數語，蓋激楚之音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。宗匠嚴維到驛，見而異之，問八元曰：“爾能從我授格乎“曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“素所願也。”少頃遂發，八元已辭親矣。維大器之，親為指諭，數</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歲間，詩賦精絕。大歷六年王漵榜第三人進士。居京既久，床頭金盡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，歸江南，訪韋蘇州，待贈甚厚。復來都應制科。貞元中調句容主簿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，況薄辭歸。時有清江上人善詩，與八元為兄弟之好。初長安慈恩寺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>浮圖，前后名流詩版甚多，八元亦題，有云：“卻怪鳥飛平地上，自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>驚人語半天中。”后元微之、白樂天至塔下遍覽，因悉除去，惟存八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元版在，吟詠久之，曰：“名下無虛士也。”其警策稱是。有詩集傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于世，一卷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○暢當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    當，河東人。大歷七年張式榜及第。當少諳武事，生亂離間，盤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>馬彎弓，摶沙寫陳，人曾伏之。時山東有寇，以子弟被召參軍。貞元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>初，為太常博士，仕終果州刺史。與李司馬、司空郎中有膠漆之契。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多往來嵩、華間，結念方外，頗參禪道，故多松桂之興，深存不死之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>志。詞名藉甚，表表凌云。有詩二卷，傳于世。同時有鄭常，亦鳴詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。集一卷，今行。嘗觀建安初，陳琳、阮瑀數子，從戎管書記之任，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所得經奇，英氣逼人也。承平則文墨議論，警急則橐鞬矢石，金羈角</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>逐，珠符相照，草檄于盾鼻，勒銘于山頭，此磊磊落落，通方之士，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>皆古書生也。容有郁志窗下，抱膝呻吟，而曰時不我與，人不我知耶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大道無窒，徒自為老夫耳。唐間如此特達甚多，光烈垂遠，慨然不能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不以之興懷也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王季友</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    季友，河南人。暗誦書萬卷。論必引經。家貧賣屐，好事者多攜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酒就之。其妻柳氏，疾季友窮丑，遣去。來客酆城，洪州刺史李公，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一見傾敬，即引佐幕府。工詩，性磊浪不羈，愛奇務險，遠出常性之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外。白首短褐，崎嶇士林，傷哉貧也！嘗有詩云：“山中誰余密白發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>日相親。雀鼠晝夜無，知我廚廩貧。”又：“自耕自刈食為天，如鹿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>如麋飲野泉。亦知世上公卿貴，且養丘中草木年。”觀其篤志山水，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>可謂遠性風疏，逸情云上矣。有集，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張謂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    謂，字正言，河內人也。少讀書嵩山，清才拔萃，泛覽流觀，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>屈于權勢。自矜奇骨，必談笑封侯。二十四受辟，從戎營、朔十載，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亭障間稍立功勛。以將軍得罪，流滯薊門。有以非辜雪之者，累官為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>禮部侍郎。無几何，出為潭州刺史。性嗜酒簡淡，樂意湖山。工詩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>格度嚴密，語致精深，多擊節之音。今有集傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○于鵠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鵠，初買山于漢陽高隱，三十猶未成名。大歷中，嘗應荐歷諸府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>從事，出塞入塞，馳逐風沙。有詩甚工，長短間作，時出度外，縱橫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>放逸，而不陷于疏遠，且多警策云。集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王建</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    建，字仲初，潁川人。大歷十年丁澤榜第二人及第。釋褐授渭南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尉，調昭應縣丞。諸司歷荐，遷太府寺丞、秘書丞、侍御史。大和中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，出為陝州司馬。從軍塞上，弓劍不離身。數年后歸，卜居咸陽原上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初游韓吏部門牆，為忘年之友。與張籍契厚，唱答尤多。工為樂府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歌行，格幽思遠。二公之體，同變時流。建性耽酒，放浪無拘。宮詞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>特妙前古。建初與樞密使王守澄有宗人之分，守澄以弟呼之。談間故</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多知禁掖事，作《宮詞》百篇。后因過燕飲，以相譏謔，守澄深銜之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，忽曰：“吾弟所作《宮詞》，內庭深邃，何由知之明當奏上。”建</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作詩以謝，末句云：“不是姓同親說向，九重爭得外人知。”守澄恐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>累己，事遂寢。建才贍，有作皆工。蓋嘗跋涉畏途，甘分窮苦。其《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自傷》詩云：“衰門海內几多人，滿眼公卿總不親。四授官資元七品</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，再經婚娶尚單身。圖書亦為頻移盡，兄弟還因數散貧。獨自在家常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>似客，黃昏哭向野田春。”又于征戍遷謫、行旅離別、幽居官況之作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，俱能感動神思，道人所不能道也。集十卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韋應物</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    應物，京兆人也。尚俠，初以三衛郎事玄宗。及崩，始悔，折節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>讀書。為性高潔，鮮食寡欲，所居必焚香掃地而坐，冥心象外。天寶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時，扈從游幸。永泰中，任洛陽丞，遷京兆府功曹。大歷十四年，自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄠縣令制除櫟陽令，以疾辭歸，寓善福寺精舍。建中二年，由前資除</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>比部員外郎，出為滁州刺史。居傾之，改江州刺史。追赴闕，改左司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎中。或媢其進，媒孽之。貞元初，又出為蘇州刺史。大和中，以太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>仆少卿兼御史中丞，為諸道鹽鐵轉運、江淮留后。罷居永定，齋心屏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>除人事。初，公豪縱不羈，晚歲逢楊開府，贈詩言事曰：“少事武皇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帝，無賴恃恩私。身作里中橫，家藏亡命兒。朝持樗蒱局，暮竊東鄰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>姬。司隸不敢捕，立在白玉墀。驪山風雪夜，長楊羽豬時。一字都不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>識，飲酒肆頑痴。武皇升仙去，憔悴被人欺。讀書事已晚，把筆學題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩。兩府始收跡，南宮謬見推。非才果不容，出守撫惸嫠。忽逢楊開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>府，論舊涕俱垂。坐客何由識，唯有故人知。”足見古人真率之妙也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。論云：“詩律自沈、宋之下，日益靡嫚，鎪章刻句，揣合浮切，音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>韻婉諧，屬對藻密，而閑雅平淡之氣不存矣。獨應物馳驟建安以還，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>各有風韻，自成一家之體，清深雅麗，雖詩人之盛，亦罕其倫，甚為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時論所右。而風情不能自已，如贈米嘉榮、杜韋娘等作，皆杯酒之間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，見少年故態，無足怪矣。有集十卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○皎然上人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    皎然，字清晝，吳興人。俗姓謝，宋靈運之十世孫也。初入道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>肄業杼山，與靈徹、陸羽同居妙喜寺。羽于寺旁創亭，以癸丑歲癸卯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朔癸亥日落成，湖州刺史顏真卿名以“三癸”，皎然賦詩，時稱“三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>絕”。真卿嘗于郡齋集文士撰《韻海鏡源》，預其論著，至是聲價藉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甚。貞元中，集賢御書院取高僧集上人文十卷，藏之，刺史于□為之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>序。李端在匡岳，依止稱門生。一時名公，俱相友善，題云“晝上人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“是也。時韋應物以古淡矯俗，以嘗擬其格，得數解為贄，韋心疑之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。明日，又錄舊制以見，始被領略，曰：“人各有長，蓋自天分。子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而為我，失故步矣。但以所詣，自名可也。”公心服之。往時住西林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寺，定余多暇，因撰序作詩體式，兼評古今人詩，為《晝公詩式》五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，及撰《詩評》三卷，皆議論精當，取舍從公，整頓狂瀾，出色騷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雅。公性放逸，不縛于常律。初，房太尉琯早歲隱終南峻壁之下，往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>往聞湫中龍吟，聲清而靜，滌人邪想。時有僧潛戛三金以寫之，惟銅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酷似。房公往來，他日至山寺，聞林嶺間有聲，因命僧出其器，嘆曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“此真龍吟也。”大歷間，有秦僧傳至桐江，皎然戛銅宛效之，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>警深寂。緇人有獻譏者，公曰：“此達僧之事，可以嬉禪。爾曹胡凝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>滯于物，而以瑣行自拘耶？”時人高之。公外學超然，詩興閑適，居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第一流、第二流不過也。詩集十卷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○武元衡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    元衡，字伯蒼，河南人。建中四年薛展榜進士。元和三年，以門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下侍郎平章事，出為劍南節度使。后秉政，明年早朝，遇盜從暗中射</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>殺之。元衡工詩，雖時見雕鐫，不動機構，要非高斫之所深忌。每好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事者傳之，被于絲竹。嘗夏夜作詩曰：“夜久喧暫息，池台惟月明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無因駐清景，日出事還生。”翌日遇害，詩蓋其讖也。議者謂工詩而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宦達者惟高適，達宦而詩工者惟元衡。今有《臨淮集》十卷傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    常，字中行，叔向之子也。京兆人。大歷十四年王儲榜及第。初</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷從事，累官水部員外郎，連除閬、夔、江、撫四州刺史。后人為國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子祭酒而終。常兄弟五人，聯芳比藻，詞價靄然，法度風流，相距不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遠。且俱陳力王事，膺寵清流，豈懷玉迷津區區之比哉。后人集所著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩通一百首為五卷，名《竇氏聯珠集》，謂若五星然。常集十八卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及撰韓翃至皎然三十人詩，合三百五十篇為《南薰集》，各系以贊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為三卷，今并傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇牟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    牟，字貽周，貞元二年張正甫榜進士。初，學問于江東，家居孝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謹，善事繼母，奇文異行，聞于京師。舅給事中袁高，當時專重名，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甄拔甚多，而牟未嘗干謁，竟捷文場。始佐六府五公，八遷至檢校虞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>部。元和五年，拜尚書虞部郎中，轉洛陽令、都官郎中，出為澤州刺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>史。仕終國子司業。牟晚從昭義盧從史，從史浸驕，牟度不可諫，即</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>移疾歸，居東都別業。長慶二年卒。昌黎韓先生為之《墓志》云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇群</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    群，字丹列，初隱毗陵，稱處士。性至孝，定省無少怠。及母卒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，哀踴不已，嚙一指置棺中，結廬墓次。終喪，蘇州刺史韋夏卿荐之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，舉孝廉，德宗擢為左拾遺。憲宗立，轉吏部郎中，出為唐州刺史。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節度使于□奇之，表以自副。武元衡輔政，荐為御史中丞。群引呂溫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、羊士諤為御史，宰相李吉甫不可。群等怨，遂捃摭吉甫陰事告之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帝面覆多誑，大怒，欲殺群等，吉甫又為力救得解。出為黔南觀察使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，遷容管經略使，卒官所。家無余財，惟圖書萬軸耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇庠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    庠，字胄卿，嘗應辟三佐大府，調奉先令，遷東都留守判官，拜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>戶部員外郎。貞元中，出為婺、登二州刺史。平生工文甚苦，著述亦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多，今并傳之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○竇鞏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鞏，字友封，狀貌瑰偉，少博覽，無不通。性宏放，好談古今，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所居多長者車轍。時諸兄已達，鞏尚來場屋間，頗抑初志。作《放魚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》詩云：“黃金贖得免刀痕，聞道禽魚亦感恩。好去長江千萬里，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>須辛苦上龍門。”人知其述懷也。元和二年王源中榜進士。佐緇青幕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>府，累遷秘書少監，拜御史中丞，仕終武昌觀察副使。鞏平居與人言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不出口，時號為“囁嚅翁“云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○劉言史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    言史，趙州人也。少尚氣節，不舉進士。工詩，美麗恢贍，世少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其倫。與李賀、孟郊同時為友。冀鎮節度使王武俊頗好詞藝，言史造</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，特加敬異。武俊嘗獵，有雙鴨起蒲稗間，一矢聯之，遂于馬上草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《射鴨歌》以獻。因表荐請官，詔授棗強令，辭疾不就，當時重之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>故相國隴西公李夷簡為漢南節度，與言史少同游習，因遣以襄陽髹器</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>千事，賂武俊請之。由是為漢南幕賓，日與談宴，歌詩唱答，大播清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才。問言史所欲為，曰：“司功掾甚閑，或可承闕。”遂署。雖居官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曹，敬待埒諸從事。歲余奏升秩，詔下之日，不恙而終。公初以言史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相薄，不俗貴，以惜其壽。至是慟哭之曰：“果然，微祿殺吾愛客也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>！”厚葬于襄城。皮日休稱其賦雕金篆玉，牢奇籠怪，百鍛為字，千</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>煉成句，真佳作也。有《歌詩》六卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉商</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    商，字子夏，徐州彭城人。擢進士第。貞元中，累官比部員外郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，改虞部員外郎。數年，遷檢校兵部郎中。后出為汴州觀察判官，辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>疾挂印，歸舊業。商性好酒，苦家貧。嘗對花臨月，悠然獨酌，亢音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>長謠，放適自遂。賦詩曰：“春草秋風老此身，一飄長醉任家貧。醒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>來還愛浮萍草，飄寄官河不屬人。”樂府歌詩，高雅殊絕。《擬蔡琰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>胡笳曲》，鱠炙當時。仍工畫山水樹石，初師吳郡張璪，后自造真。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>張貶衡州司馬，有惆悵之詩。好神仙，煉金骨，后隱義興胡父渚，結</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侶幽人，世傳沖虛而去，可謂江海冥滅，山林長往者矣。有集十卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>今傳，武元衡序之云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○盧仝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    仝，范陽人。初隱少室山，號玉川子。家甚貧，惟圖書堆積。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卜居洛城，破屋數間而已。一奴，長須，不裹頭；一婢，赤腳，老無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>齒。終日苦哦，鄰僧送米。朝廷知其清介之節，凡兩備禮征為諫議大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>夫，不起。時韓愈為河南令，愛其操，敬待之。嘗為惡少所恐，訴于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>愈，方為申理，仝復慮盜憎主人，願罷之，愈益服其度量。元和間，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月蝕，仝賦詩，意譏切當時逆黨，愈極稱工，余人稍恨之。時王涯秉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>政，胥怨于人。及禍起，仝偶與諸客會食涯書館中，因留宿，吏卒掩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>捕，仝曰：“我盧山人也，于眾無怨，何罪之有“吏曰：“既云山人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，來宰相宅，容非罪乎“蒼忙不能自理，竟同甘露之禍。仝老無發，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奄人于腦后加釘。先是生子名“添丁”，人以為讖云。仝性高古介僻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，所見不凡近。唐詩體無遺，而仝之所作特異，自成一家，語尚奇譎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，讀者難解，識者易知。后來仿效比擬，遂為一格宗師。有集一卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>今傳。古詩云：“枯魚過河泣，何時悔復及。作書與魴鱮，相戒慎出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>入。”斯所以防前之覆轍也。仝志懷霜雪，操擬松柏，深造括囊之高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，夫何戶庭之失。噫，一蹈非地，旋踵逮殃，玉石俱爛，可不痛哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○馬異</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    異，睦州人也。興元元年禮部侍郎鮑防下進士第二人。少與皇甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>湜同硯席，賦性高疏，詞調怪澀，雖風骨棱棱，不免枯瘠。盧仝聞之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，頗合己志，願與結交，遂立同異之論，以詩贈答，有云：“昨日仝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不同，異自異，是謂大同而小異。今日仝自同，異不異，是謂同不往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而異不至。”斯亦怪之甚也。后不知所終。集今傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉叉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    叉，河朔間人，一節士也。少尚義行俠，傍觀切齒，因被酒殺人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亡命，會赦乃出。更改志從學，能博覽，工為歌詩，酷好盧仝、孟郊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之體，造語幽蹇，議論多出于正。《冰柱》、《雪車》二篇，含蓄風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刺，出二公之右矣。時樊宗師文亦尚怪，見而獨拜之。恃故時所負，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自顧俯仰不能與世合，常破履穿結，筑環堵而居休焉。聞韓吏部接天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下貧士，步而歸之，出入門館無間。時韓碑銘獨唱，潤筆之貨盈缶，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>因持案上金數斤而去，曰：“此諛墓中人所得耳，不若與劉君為壽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”愈不能止。其曠達至此。初。玉川子履道守正，反關著述，《春秋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》之學，尤所精心，時人不得見其書，惟叉愜意，曾授之以奧旨，后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無所傳。叉剛直，能面白人短長，其服義則又彌縫若親屬然。后以爭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>語不能下客，去游齊魯，不知所終。詩二十七篇，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李賀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    賀，字長吉，鄭王之孫也。七歲能辭章，名動京邑。韓愈、皇甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>湜覽其作，奇之而未信，曰：“若是古人，吾曹或不知，是今人，豈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有不識之理。”遂相過其家，使賦詩。賀總角荷衣而出，欣然承命，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>旁若無人，援筆題曰《高軒過》。二公大驚，以所乘馬命聯鑣而還，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>親為束發。賀父名晉肅，不得舉進士，公為著《諱辯》一篇。后官至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>太常寺奉禮郎。賀為人纖瘦，通眉，長指爪，能疾書。旦日出，騎弱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>馬，從平頭小奴子，背古錦囊，遇有所得，書置囊里。凡詩不先命題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，及暮歸，太夫人使婢探囊中，見書多，即怒曰：“是兒要嘔出心乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>已耳！”上燈，與食，即從婢取書，研墨疊紙足成之。非大醉吊喪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>率如此。賀詩稍尚奇詭，組織花草，片片成文，所得皆驚邁，絕云翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>墨畦徑，時無能效者。樂府諸詩，云韶眾工，諧于律呂。嘗嘆曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>我年二十不得意，一生愁心，謝如梧葉矣。”忽疾篤，恍惚晝見人緋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>衣賀赤虯騰下，持一版書，若太古雷文，曰：“上帝新作白玉樓成，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>立召君作記也。”賀叩頭辭，謂母老病，其人曰：“無上比人間差樂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不苦也。”居傾，窗中勃勃煙氣，聞車聲甚速，遂絕。死時才二十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>七，莫不憐之。李藩綴集其歌詩，因托賀表兄訪所遺失，并加點竄，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>付以成本。彌年絕跡。乃詰之，曰：“每恨其傲忽，其文己焚之矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“今存十之四五。杜牧為序者五卷，今傳。孟子曰：“其進銳者其退</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>速。”信然。賀天才俊拔，弱冠而有極名。天奪之速，豈吝也耶若少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>假行年，涵養盛德，觀其才，不在古人下矣。今茲惜哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李涉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    涉，洛陽人，渤之仲兄也。自號清溪子。早歲客梁園，數逢亂兵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，避地南來，樂佳山水，卜隱匡廬香爐峰下石洞間。嘗養一白鹿，甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>馴狎，因名所居曰白鹿洞。與弟渤、崔膺昆季茅舍相接。后徙居終南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，偶從陳許辟命，從事行軍。未几，以罪謫夷陵宰，十年蹭蹬峽中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>病瘧成痼，自傷羈逐，頭顱又復如許。后遇赦得還，賦詩云：“荷蓑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不是人間事，歸去滄江有釣舟。”遂放船重來訪吳、楚舊游，登天台</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>石橋，望海得風水之便，挂席浮瀟、湘、岳陽，逢張祜話故，因盤桓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。歸洛下，營草堂，隱少室。身自耕耘，妾能織紝，稚子供漁樵，拓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>落生計，伶俜酒鄉，罕交人事。大和中，宰相累荐，征起為太學博士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，致仕。卒。妻亦入道。涉工為詩，詞意卓犖，不群世俗。長篇敘事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，如行云流水，無可牽制，才名一時欽動。初，嘗過九江皖口，遇夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>客，方跧伏，問何人曰：“李山人。”豪首曰：“若是，勿用剽奪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>久聞詩名，願題一篇足矣。”涉欣然書曰：“暮雨瀟瀟江上村，綠林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>豪客夜知聞。他時不用藏名姓，世上如今半是君。”大喜，因以牛酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>厚遺，再拜送之。夫以跖、蹻之輩，猶曰憐才，而至寶橫道，君子不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>顧，忍哉。詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○朱晝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    晝，廣陵人。貞元間，慕孟郊之名，為詩格范相似，曾不遠千里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而訪之，不厭勤苦，體尚奇澀。與李涉友善，相酬唱。晝《古鏡》詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“我有古時鏡，初自壞陵得。蛟龍猶泥蟠，魑魅幸月蝕。磨久見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>菱蕊，青于藍水色。贈君將照心，無使心受惑。“凡如此警策者稍多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○賈島</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    島，字閬仙，范陽人也。初，連敗文場，囊篋空甚，遂為浮屠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名無本。來東都，旋往京，居青龍寺。時禁僧午后不得出，為詩自傷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。元和中，元、白變尚輕淺，島獨按格入僻，以矯浮艷。當冥搜之際</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，前有王公貴人皆不覺，游心萬仞，慮入無窮。自稱碣石山人。嘗嘆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“知余素心者，惟終南紫閣、白閣諸峰隱者耳。”嵩丘有草廬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>欲歸未得，逗留長安。雖行坐寢食，苦吟不輟。嘗跨蹇驢張蓋，橫截</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天衢，時秋風正厲，黃葉可掃，遂吟曰：“落葉滿長安。”方思屬聯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，杳不可得，忽以“秋風吹渭水“為對，喜不自勝。因唐突大京兆劉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棲楚，被系一夕，旦釋之。后復乘閑策蹇訪李余幽居，得句云：“鳥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宿池中樹，僧推月下門。”又欲作“僧敲”，煉之未定，吟哦引手作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>推敲之勢，傍觀亦訝。時韓退之尹京兆，車騎方出，不覺沖至第三節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，左右擁到馬前，島具實對，未定推敲，神游象外，不知回避。韓駐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>久之曰：“敲字佳。”遂并轡歸，共論詩道，結為布衣交，遂授以文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>法，去浮屠，舉進士。愈贈詩云：“孟郊死葬北邙山，日月風云頓覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閑。天恐文章渾斷絕，再生賈島在人間。”自此名著。時新及第，寓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>居法乾無可精舍，姚合、王建、張籍、雍陶，皆琴樽之好。一日，宣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宗微行至寺，聞鐘樓上有吟聲，遂登，于島案上取卷覽之，島不識，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>因作色攘臂，睨而奪取之曰：“郎君鮮醲自足，何會此耶“帝下樓去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。既而覺之，大恐，伏闕待罪，上訝之。他日，有中旨，令與一清官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謫去者，乃授遂州長江主簿。后稍遷普州司倉。臨死之日，家無一錢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，惟病驢、古琴而已。當時誰不愛其才，而惜其命薄。島貌清意雅，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>談玄抱佛，所交悉塵外之人。況味蕭條，生計岨峿。自題曰：“二句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三年得，一吟雙淚流。知音如不賞，歸臥故山秋。”每至除夕，必取</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一歲所作置几上，焚香再拜，酹酒祝曰：“此吾終年苦心也。”痛飲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>長謠而罷。今集十卷，并《詩格》一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○莊南杰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    南杰，與賈島同時，曾從受學。工樂府雜歌，詩體似長吉，氣雖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遒壯，語過鐫鑿，蓋其天資本劣，未免按抑，不出自然，亦一好奇尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僻之士耳。集二卷，今行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張碧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    碧，字太碧。貞元間舉進士，累不第，便覺三山跬步，云漢咫尺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初慕李翰林之高躅，一杯一詠，必見清風，故其名字皆亦逼似，如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>司馬長卿希藺相如為人也。天才卓絕，氣韻不凡，委興山水，投閑吟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酌，言多野意，俱狀難摹之景焉。有《歌行集》二卷傳世。子瀛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○朱放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    放，字長通，南陽人也。初，居臨漢水，遭歲歉，南來卜隱剡溪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><h5>、鏡湖間。排青紫之念，結廬云臥，釣水樵山。嘗著白接滿A鹿裘筍</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>屨，盤桓酒家。時江浙名士如林，風流儒雅，俱從高義。如皇甫兄弟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，皎、徹上人，皆山人良友也。大歷中，嗣曹王皋鎮江西，辟為節度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>參謀。有《別同志》曰：“潺湲寒溪上，自此成離別。回首望歸人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>移舟逢暮雪。頻行識草樹，漸老傷年發。唯有白云心，為向東山月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”未几，不樂鞅掌，扁舟告還。貞元二年，詔舉韜晦奇才，特下聘禮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，拜左拾遺，不就，表謝之。忘懷得失，以此自終。放工詩，風度清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>越，神情蕭散，非尋常之比。集二卷，今行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○羊士諤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    士諤，貞元元年禮部侍郎鮑防下進士。順宗時，累至宣歙巡官，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為王叔文所惡，貶汀州寧化尉。元和初，宰相李吉甫知獎，擢為監察</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>御史，掌制誥。后以與竇群、呂溫等誣論宰執，出為資州刺史。士諤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工詩，妙造梁《選》，作皆典重。早歲嘗游女几山，有卜隱之志，勛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名相迫，不遂初心。有詩集行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○姚系</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    系，河中人。貞元元年進士，與韋應物同時。有詩名，工古調，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>善彈琴，好游名山，希蹤謝、郭，終身不言祿，祿亦不及之也。與林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棲谷隱之士往還酬酢，興趣超然。弟倫，詩亦清麗，有集，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○`信陵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    信陵，貞元元年鄭全濟榜及第。仕為舒州望江縣令，卒。工詩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    登，初隱居。性剛潔，幅巾短褐，交友名公。后就辟，歷衛府參</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謀，遷廷尉平。久之，拜監察御史。貞元中，改河南士曹掾，遷殿中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍御史、漳州刺史，退居告老。嘗晚春乘輕車出南薰門，抵暮詣宜春</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>門入，關吏捧牌請書官位，登醉題曰：“閑游靈沼送春回，關吏何須</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>苦見猜。八十老翁無品秩，三曾身到鳳池來。”其狷迫如此。數年，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>坐公累被劾，吏議捃摭不堪，感疾而卒。有集六卷，權德輿為序云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○令狐楚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    楚，字殼士，敦煌人也。五歲能文章。貞元七年尹樞榜進士及第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。時李說、嚴綬、鄭儋繼領太原，高其才行，引在幕府，由掌書記至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>判官。德宗喜文，每省太原奏疏，必能辨楚所為，數稱美之。憲宗時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，累擢知制誥。皇甫鎛荐為翰林學士，遷中書舍人，拜中書侍郎、同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>平章事。楚工詩，當時與白居易、元稹、劉禹錫唱和甚多。有《漆奩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集》一百三十卷，行于世。自稱曰：“白云孺子”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○楊巨源</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    巨源，字景山，蒲中人。貞元五年劉太真下第二人及第。初為張</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>弘靖從事，拜虞部員外郎，后遷太常博士、國子祭酒。大和中，為河</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中少尹，入拜禮部郎中。巨源才雄學富，用意聲律，細挹得無窮之源</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，緩雋有愈永之味。長篇刻琢，絕句清泠，蓋得于此而失于彼者矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有詩一卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○馬逢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    逢，關中人。貞元五年盧頊榜進士。佐鎮戎幕府，嘗從軍出塞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>得詩名，篇篇警策。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○王涯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    涯，字廣津，貞元八年賈棱榜及第。博學工文，尤多雅思。梁肅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>異其才，荐于陸贄。又舉宏辭。憲宗時，知制誥、翰林學士，俄拜中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書侍郎、平章事。長慶中，節度劍南，召為御史大夫，遷戶部尚書，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>監鹽鐵使。進仆射。涯榷鹽苛急，百姓怨之。及甘露禍起，就誅，悉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詬罵，投以瓦礫，須臾成堆。性嗇，不蓄妓妾，家財累鉅萬，嘗布衣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蔬食。酷好前古名書名畫，充積左右，有不可得，必百計傾陷以取之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。及家破，往來人得卷軸，皆剔取奩盒金玉牙錦，余棄道途，車馬踐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>踏，悉損污矣。惜哉！善為詩，風韻遒然，殊超意表。集十卷，今傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。否泰遞復，盈虛消息，乃理之常。夫物盛者，衰之漸也；散者，積</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之極也。有能終滿而不覆者乎！況圖書人變化之際，神物所深忌者焉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。前修耽玩成癖，往往殺身，猶非剽剝而至也。王涯掊克聚斂，以邀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>穹爵，逼孤凌弱，以積珍奇，知己之利，忘人之害，至于天奪其魄，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鬼瞰其家，一旦飄零，殊可長嘆。孟子曰：“死矣，盆成括。”《傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》曰：“貨悖而入者，亦悖而出。”不亦宜哉。庶來者之少戒云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韓愈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    愈，字退之，南陽人。早孤依嫂，讀書日記數千言，通百家。貞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元八年擢第。凡三指光范上書，始得調。董晉表署宣武節度推官。汴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>軍亂，去依張建封，辟府推官。遷監察御史。上疏論宮市，德宗怒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貶陽山令。有善政，改江陵法曹參軍。元和中，為國子博士、河南令</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。愈以才高難容，累下遷，乃作《進學解》以自諭。執政奇其才，轉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>考功、知制誥，進中書舍人。裴度宣慰淮西，奏為行軍司馬。賊平，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遷刑部侍郎。憲宗遣使迎佛骨入禁中，因上表極諫，帝大怒，欲殺，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>裴度、崔群力救，乃貶潮州刺史。任后上表，陳情哀切，詔量移袁州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刺史。召拜國子祭酒，轉兵部侍郎、京兆尹、兼御史大夫。長慶四年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卒。公英偉間生，才名冠世，繼道德之統，明列聖之心。獨濟狂瀾，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詞彩燦爛，齊、梁綺艷，毫發都捐。有冠冕珮玉之氣，宮商金石之音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，為一代文宗，使頹綱復振，豈易言也哉固無辭足以贊述云。至若歌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩累百篇，而驅駕氣勢，若掀雷走電，撐決于天地之垠，詞鋒學浪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>先有定價也。時功曹張署亦工詩，與公同為御史，又同遷謫，唱答見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于集中。有詩賦雜文等四十卷，今行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○柳宗元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗元，字子厚，河東人。貞元九年苑論榜第進士。又試博學宏辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，授校書郎，調藍田縣尉，累遷監察御史里行。與王叔文、韋執誼善</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，二人引之謀事，擢禮部員外郎，欲大用，值叔文敗，貶邵州刺史，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>半道，有詔貶永州司馬。遍貽朝士書言情，眾忌其才，無為用心者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元和十年，徙柳州刺史。時劉禹錫同謫，得播州，宗元以播非人所居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，且禹錫母老，具奏以柳州讓禹錫，而自往播，會大臣亦有為請者，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遂改連州。宗元在柳多惠政，及卒，百姓追慕，立祠享祀，血食至今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。公天才絕倫，文章卓偉，一時輩行，咸推仰之。工詩，語意深切，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>發纖穠于簡古，寄至味于淡泊，非余子所及也。司空圖論之曰：“梅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>止于酸，鹽止于咸，飲食不可無，而其美常在酸咸之外，可以一唱而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三嘆也。子厚詩在陶淵明下，韋應物上，退之豪放奇險則過之，而溫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>厲靖深不及也。”今詩賦雜文等三十卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陳羽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    羽，江東人。貞元八年，禮部侍郎陸贄下第二人登科，與韓愈、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王涯等共為龍虎榜。后仕歷東宮衛佐。羽工吟，與靈一上人交游唱答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。寫難狀之景，了了目前；含不盡之意，皎皎言外。如《自遣》詩云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“稚子新能編筍笠，山妻舊解補荷衣。秋山隔岸清猿叫，湖水當門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>白鳥飛。”此景何處無之，前后誰能道者二十八字，一片畫圖，非造</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>次之謂也。警句甚多。有集傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉禹錫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    禹錫，字夢得，中山人。貞元九年進士。又中博學宏辭科，工文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>章。時王叔文得幸，禹錫與之交，嘗稱其有宰相器。朝廷大議，多引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>禹錫及柳宗元與議禁中。判度支鹽鐵案，憑藉其勢，多中傷人。御史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>竇群劾云：“挾邪亂政。”即日罷。憲宗立，叔文敗，斥朗州司馬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>州接夜郎，俗信巫鬼，每祠，歌《竹枝》，鼓吹俄延，其聲傖佇。禹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>錫謂屈原居沅、湘間，作《九歌》，使楚人以迎送神。乃倚聲作《竹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>枝辭》十篇，武陵人悉歌之。始，坐叔文貶者，雖赦不原。宰相哀其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才且困，將澡用之，乃悉詔補遠州刺史，諫官奏罷之。時久落魄，郁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郁不自抑，其吐辭多諷托遠，意感權臣，而憾不釋。久之，召還，欲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>任南省郎，而作《玄都觀看花君子》詩，語譏忿，當路不喜，又謫守</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>播州。中丞裴度言：“播，猿狖所宅，且其母年八十余，與子死決，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>恐傷陛下孝治，請稍內遷。”乃易連州，又徙夔州。后由和州刺史入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為主客郎中。至京后，游玄都詠詩，且言：“始謫十年，還輦下，道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士種桃，其盛苦霞。又十四年而來，無復一存，唯兔葵燕麥動搖春風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>耳。“權近聞者，益薄其行。裴度荐為翰林學士，俄分司東都，遷太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子賓客。會昌時，加檢校禮部尚書，卒。公恃才而放，心不能平，行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年益晏，偃蹇寡合，乃以文章自適。善詩，精絕，與白居易酬唱頗多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，嘗推為“詩豪”，曰：“劉君詩在處，有神物護持。”有集四十卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○孟郊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    郊，字東野，洛陽人。初隱嵩少，稱處士。性介，不諧合。韓愈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一見為忘形交，與唱和于詩酒間。貞元十二年李程榜進士，時年五十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>矣。調溧陽尉。縣有投金瀨、平陵城，林薄蓊蘙，下有積水。郊間往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>坐水傍，命酒揮琴，裴回賦詩終日，而曹務多廢。縣令白府，以假尉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>代之，分其半俸。辭官家居。李翱分司洛中，日與談宴，荐于興元節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>度使鄭余慶，遂奏為參謀，試大理評事，卒。余慶給錢數萬營葬，仍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>贍其妻子者累年。張藉謚為貞曜先生，門人遠赴心喪。郊拙于生事，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一貧徹骨，裘褐懸結，未嘗俯眉為可憐之色。然好義者更遺之。工詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，大有理致，韓吏部極稱之。多傷不遇，年邁家空，思苦奇澀，讀之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>每令人不歡，如“借車載家具，家具少于車。“如《謝炭》云“吹霞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>弄日光不定，暖得曲身成直身”，如“愁人獨有夜燭見，一紙鄉書淚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>滴穿”，如《下第》云“棄置復棄置，情如刀劍傷“之類，皆哀怨清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>切，窮人冥搜。其初登第，吟曰：“昔日齷齪不足嗟，今朝曠蕩思無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>涯。春風得意馬蹄疾，一日看盡長安花。”當時議者，亦見其氣度窘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>促，卒漂淪薄宦，詩讖信有之矣。天實為之，謂之何哉！李觀論其詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，曰“高處在古無上，平處下顧二謝“云。時陸長源工詩，相與來往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，篇什稍多，亦佳作也。有《咸池集》十卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○戴叔倫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    叔倫，字幼公，潤州金壇人。師事蕭穎士為門生。賦性溫雅，善</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舉止，能清談，無賢不肖，相接盡心。工詩。貞元十六年陳權榜進士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。嘗在租庸幕下數年，夕惕匪怠。吏部尚書劉公與祠部員外郎張繼書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，博訪選材，日揖賓客，叔倫投刺，一見稱心，遂就荐。累遷撫州刺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>史。政擬龔、黃，民樂其治，圜扉寂然，鞠為茂草，詔書褒美，封譙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郡男，加金紫。后遷容管經略使，威名益振，治亦清明，仁恕多方，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所至稱最。德宗賦《中和節詩》，遣使者寵賜，世以為榮。還，上表</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>請為道士，未几卒。叔倫初以淮、汴寇亂，魚肉江上，攜親族避地來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄱陽。肄業勤苦，志樂清虛，閉門卻掃，與處士張眾甫、朱放素厚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>范、張之期，曾不虛月。詩興悠遠，每作驚人。有《述稿》十卷，今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張仲素</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    仲素，字繪之。貞元十四年李隨榜進士，與李翱、呂溫同年。以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中朝無援不調，潛耀久之，復中博學宏辭，始任武康軍從事。貞元二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>十年，遷司勛員外郎，除翰林學士。時憲宗求盧綸詩文遺草，敕仲素</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>編集進之。后拜中書舍人。仲素能屬文，法度嚴確。魏文帝有云：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文以意為主，以氣為輔，以詞為衛。”此言得之矣。其每詞未達而意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>先備也。善詩，多警句。尤精樂府，往往和在宮商，古人有未能慮及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者。集一卷，及《賦樞》三卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○呂溫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    溫，字和叔，河中人。初從陸贄治《春秋》，梁肅為文章。貞元</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>十四年李隨榜及第。中宏辭。與王叔文厚善，驟遷左拾遺，除侍御史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。使吐蕃，留不得遣彌年。溫在絕域，常自悲惋。元和元年還，進戶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>部員外郎。與竇群、羊士諤相愛。群為中丞，荐溫為御史，宰相李吉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甫持久不報。會吉甫病，夜召術上，群等因奏之，事見群傳。上怒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貶筠州，再貶道州刺史，詔徙衡州，卒官所。溫藻翰粗贍，一時流輩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>咸推尚。性險躁，譎怪而好利。今有集十卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張籍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    籍，字文昌，和州烏江人也。貞元十五年封孟紳榜及第。授秘書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎，歷太祝，除水部員外郎。初至長安，謁韓愈，一會如平生歡，才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名相許，論心結契。愈力荐為國子博士。然性狷直，多所責諷于愈，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>愈亦不忌之。時朝野名士皆與游，如王建、賈島、于鵠、孟郊諸公集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，多所贈答，情愛深厚。皆別家千里，游宦四方，瘦馬羸童，青衫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>烏帽，故每邂逅于風塵，必多殷勤之思，銜杯命素，又況于同志者乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。聲調相似，況味頗同。公于樂府古風，與王司馬自成機軸，絕世獨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>立。自李、杜之后，風雅道喪，至元和中，暨元、白歌詩，為海內宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>匠，謂之“元和體”，病格稍振，無愧洪河砥柱也。樂天贈詩曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>張公何為者業文三十春。尤工樂府詞，舉代少其倫。”仕終國子司業</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。有集七卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○雍裕之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    裕之，蜀人。有詩名。貞元后數舉進士不第，飄蓬四方。為樂府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，極有情致。集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○權德輿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    德輿，字載之，秦州人。未冠，以文章稱諸儒間。韓洄黜陟河南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，辟置幕府。復從江西觀察使李兼府為判官。德宗聞其材，召為太常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>博士，改左補闕，中間累上書直言，遷起居舍人。貞元十五年知制誥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，進中書舍人。憲宗初，歷兵部侍郎、太子賓客。以陳說謀略多中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元和五年自太常卿拜禮部尚書、同中書門下平章事。德輿善辯論，開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陳古今，覺悟人生。主輔相，尚寬，不甚察察。封扶風郡公。德輿能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賦詩，工古調樂府，極多情致。積思經術，無不貫綜，手不釋卷。雖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>動止無外飾，其醞藉風流，自然可慕。貞元、元和間，為荐紳羽儀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有文集，今傳，楊嗣復為序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○長孫佐輔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    佐輔，朔方人。舉進士下第，放懷不羈。弟公輔，貞元間為吉州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刺史，遂往依焉。后卒不宦，隱居以求志。然風流醞藉，一代名儒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩格詞情，繁縟不雜，卓然有英邁之氣。每見其擬古、樂府數篇，極</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>怨慕傷感之心，如水中月，如鏡中相，言可盡而理無窮也。集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○楊衡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    衡，字中師，霅人。天寶間避地西來，與符載、崔群、李渤同隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>廬山，結草堂于五老峰下，號“山中四友”，日以琴酒寓意，云月遣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>懷。衡詩工，苦于聲韻奇拔，非常格敢窺其涯涘。嘗吟罷，自賞其作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，抵掌大笑，長謠曰：“一一鶴聲飛上天！”謂其響徹如此，人亦嘆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>伏。試大理評事。往來多山僧道士，為方外之期。詩一卷，今傳于世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○白居易</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    居易，字樂天，太原下邽人。弱冠名未振，觀光上國，謁顧況。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>況，吳人，恃才少所推可，因謔之曰：“長安百物皆貴，居大不易！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”及覽詩卷，至“離離原上草，一歲一枯榮，野火燒不盡，春風吹又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生，“乃嘆曰：“有句如此，居天下亦不難。老夫前言戲之爾。”貞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元十六年，中書舍人高郢下進士、拔萃皆中，補校書郎。元和元年，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作樂府及詩百余篇，規諷時事，流聞禁中，上悅之。召拜翰林學士，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷左拾遺。時盜殺宰相，京師洶洶，居易首上疏，請亟捕賊。權臣有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>嫌其出位，怒，俄有言居易母墮井死，而賦《新井篇》言既浮華，行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不可用，貶江州司馬。初以勛庸暴露不宜，實無他腸，怫怒奸黨，遂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>失志。亦能順所遇，托浮屠死生說，忘形骸者。久之，轉中書舍人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>知制誥。河朔亂，兵出無功，又言事不見聽，乞外，除為杭州刺史。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文宗立，召遷刑部侍郎。會昌初，致仕，卒。居易累以忠鯁遭擯，乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>放縱詩酒。既復用，又皆幼君，仕情頓爾索寞。卜居履道里，與香山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僧如滿等結淨社，疏沼種樹，構石樓，鑿八節灘，為游賞之樂，茶鐺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酒杓不相離。嘗科頭箕踞，談禪詠古，晏如也。自號“醉吟先生”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作傳。酷好佛，亦經月不葷，稱“香山居士”。與胡杲、吉皎、鄭據</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、劉真、盧貞、張渾、如滿、李文爽燕集，皆高年不仕，日相招致，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時人慕之，繪《九老圖》。公詩以六義為主，不尚艱難。每成篇，必</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>令其家老嫗讀之，問解則錄。后人評白詩如山東父老課農桑，言言皆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>實者也。雞林國行賈售于其國相，率篇百金，偽者即能辨之。與元稹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>極善膠漆，音韻亦同，天下曰“元、白”。元卒，與劉賓客齊名，曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“劉、白“云。公好神仙，自制飛云履，焚香振足，如撥煙霧，冉冉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生云。初來九江，居廬阜峰下，作草堂燒丹，今尚存。有《白氏長慶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集》七十五卷，及所撰古今事實為《六帖》，及述作詩格法，欲自除</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其病，名《白氏金針集》三卷，并行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○元稹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    稹，字微之，河南人。九歲工屬文，十五擢明經，書判入等，補</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>校書郎。元和初，對策第一，拜左拾遺。數上書言利害，當路惡之，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出為河南尉。后拜監察御史，按獄東川。還次敷水驛，中人仇士良夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至，稹不讓邸，仇怒，擊稹敗面。宰相以稹年少輕威，失憲臣體，貶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>江陵士曹參軍，李絳等論其枉。元和末，召拜膳部員外郎。稹詩變體</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，往往宮中樂色皆誦之，呼為才子。然綴屬雖廣，樂府專其警策也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>初在江陵，與監軍崔潭峻善。長慶中，崔進其歌詩數十百篇，帝大悅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，問今安在，曰：“為南宮散郎。”擢祠部郎中、知制誥，俄遷中書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舍人、翰林承旨，后拜同中書門下平章事。初以瑕舋，舉動浮薄，朝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>野雜笑，未几罷。然素無檢，望輕，不為公議所右，除武昌節度使，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卒。在越時，辟竇鞏。鞏工詩，日酬和，故鏡湖、秦望之奇益傳，時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>號“蘭亭絕唱”。微之與白樂天最密，雖骨肉未至，愛慕之情，可欺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>金石，千里神交，若合符契，唱和之多，無逾二公者。有《元氏長慶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集》一百卷及《小集》十卷，今傳。夫松柏飽風霜，而后勝梁棟之任</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，人必勞餓空乏，而后無充詘之態。譽早必氣銳，氣銳則志驕，志驕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>則斂怨。先達者未足喜，晚成者或可賀。況慶吊相望于門閭，不可測</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>哉。人評元詩如李龜年說天寶遺事，貌悴而神不傷。況尤物移人，侈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>俗遷性，足見其舉止斐薄丰茸，仍且不容勝己，至登庸成忝，貽笑于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多士，其來尚矣。不矜細行，終累大德。豈不聞言行君子之樞機，榮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>辱之主耶古人不恥能治而無位，恥有位而不能治也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李紳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    紳，字公垂，亳州人。元和元年武翊黃榜進士，與皇甫湜同年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>補國子助教。穆宗召為翰林學士，累遷中書舍人。武宗即位，拜中書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍郎平章事。紳為人短小精悍，于詩特有名，號“短李”。與李德裕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、元稹同時，稱“三俊”。集名《追昔游》，多紀行之作。又《批答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》一卷，皆傳。初為壽州刺史，有秀才郁渾，年甫弱冠，應百篇科，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>紳命題試之，未昏而就，警句佳意甚多，亦有集，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鮑溶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    溶，字德源，元和四年韋瓘榜第進士，在楊汝士一時。與李端公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>益少同袍，為爾汝交。初隱江南山中避地。家苦貧，勁氣不擾，羈旅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>四方，登臨懷昔，皆古今絕唱。過隴頭古天山大阪，泉水嗚咽，分流</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>四下，賦詩曰：“隴頭水，千古不堪聞。生歸蘇屬國，死別李將軍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>細響風凋草，清哀雁入云。”其警絕大概如此。古詩樂府，可稱獨步</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。蓋其氣力宏贍，博識清度，雅正高古，眾才無不備具云。卒飄蓬薄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宦，客死三川。有集五卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張又新</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    又新，字孔昭，深州人也。初應宏辭第一，又為京兆解頭。元和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>九年禮部侍郎韋貫之下狀元及第，時號為“張三頭”。應辟為廣陵從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事，歷補闕。為性傾邪，諂事宰相李逢吉，為之鷹犬，名在“八關十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>六子“之目。逢吉領山南節度，表為司馬，坐田伾事貶官。李訓專政</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，又新復見用。后竟坐事謫遠州刺史。仕終左司郎中。善為詩，恃才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多藺藉。其淫蕩之行，卒見于篇。嘗曰：“我少年擅美名，意不欲仕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宦，惟得美妻，平生足矣。”娶楊虔州女，有德無色，殊怏怏。后過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>淮南，李紳筵上得一歌姬，與之偕老，其狂斐類此。喜嗜茶，恨在陸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>羽后，自著《煎茶水記》一卷，及詩文等行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○殷堯藩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    堯藩，秀州人。為性簡靜，眉目如畫。工詩文，耽丘壑之趣。嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“吾一日不見山水，與俗人談，便覺胸次塵土堆積，急呼濁醪澆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，聊解穢耳。”元和九年韋貫之放榜，堯藩落第，楊尚書大為稱屈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>料理，因擢進士。數年，為永樂縣令。一舸之官，彈琴不下堂，而人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不忍欺。雍陶寄詩曰：“古縣蕭條秋景晚，昔時陶令亦如君。頭巾漉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酒臨黃菊，手板支頤向白云。百里豈能容驥足，九霄終自別雞群。相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>思不恨書來少，佳句多從闕下聞。”及與沈亞之、馬戴為詩友，贈答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甚多。后仕終侍御史。堯藩初游韋應物門牆，分契莫逆。及來長沙，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尚書李翱席上有舞《柘枝》者，容語淒惻，因感而賦詩以贈曰：“姑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蘇太守青娥女，流落長沙舞《柘枝》。滿座繡衣皆不識，可憐紅粉淚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雙垂。”眾客驚問之，果韋公愛姬所生女也，相于吁嘆。翱即命削丹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書，于賓館中擢士嫁之。今有集一卷傳世，皆鏗鏘蘊藉之作也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○清塞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    清塞，字南卿，居廬岳為浮屠，客南徐亦久，后來少室、終南間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。俗姓周，名賀。工為近體詩，格調清雅，與賈島、無可齊名。寶歷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，姚合守錢塘，因攜書投刺以丐品第，合延待甚異。見其《哭僧》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩云：“凍須亡夜剃，遺偈病中書。”大愛之，因加以冠巾，使復姓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>字。時夏臘已高，榮望落落，竟往依名山諸尊宿自終。詩一卷，今存</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○無可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    無可，長安人，高僧也。工詩，多為五言。初，賈島棄俗時，同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>居青龍寺，呼島為從兄。與馬戴、姚合、厲玄多有酬唱，律調謹嚴，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>屬興清越，比物以意，謂之“象外句”。如曰：“聽雨寒更盡，開門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>落葉深。”又曰：“微陽下喬木，遠燒入秋山。“凡此等新奇，當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翕然稱尚，妙在言用而不失其名耳。今集一卷相傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○熊孺登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    孺登，鐘陵人，有詩名。元和中為西川從事，與白舍人、劉賓客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>善，多贈答。亦祗役湘中數年。凡下筆，言語妙天下。如：“江流如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>箭月如弓，行盡三湘數夜中。無奈子規知向蜀，一聲聲似怨春風。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>又《經古墓》云：“碑折松枯山火燒，夜台從閉不曾朝。那將逝者比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>流水，流水東流逢上潮。”類此極多。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李約</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    約，字存博，汧公李勉之子也。元和中，仕為兵部員外郎。與主</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>客員外張諗極相知。每單枕靜言，達旦不寐。嘗贈韋況曰：“我有心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中事，不向韋郎說。秋夜洛陽城，明月照張八。”性清潔寡欲，一生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不近粉黛，博古探奇。初，汧公海內名臣，多蓄古今玩器，約愈好之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，所居軒屏公案，必置古銅怪石，法書名畫，皆歷代所寶。坐間悉雅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士，清談終日，彈琴煮茗，心略不及塵事也。嘗使江南，于海門山得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雙峰石及綠石琴荐，并為好事者傳閟。然亦寓意，未嘗戛然寡情，豪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奪吝與。復嗜茶，與陸羽、張又新論水品特詳。曾授客煎茶法，曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“茶須緩火炙，活火煎，當使湯無妄沸。始則魚目散布，微微有聲；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中則四畔泉涌，累累然；終則騰波鼓浪，水氣全消。此老湯之法，固</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>須活水，香味俱真矣。”時知音者賞之。有詩集。后棄官終隱。又著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《東杓引譜》一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○沈亞之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    亞之，字下賢，吳興人。初至長安，與李賀結交。舉進士不第，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為歌以送歸。元和十年侍郎崔群下進士。涇原李匯辟為掌書記。為秘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書省正字。長慶中，補櫟陽令。四年，遷福建團練副使，事徐晦。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>累遷殿中丞御史內供奉。大和三年，柏耆宣慰德州，取為判官。耆罷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，亞之貶南康尉，后終郢州掾。亞之以文辭得名，然狂躁貪冒，輔耆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為惡，頗憑陵晚達，故及于謫。嘗游韓吏部門。杜牧、李商隱俱有擬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>沈下賢詩，蓋甚為當時名輩器重云。有集九卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○徐凝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    凝，睦州人。元和間有詩名。方干師事之。與施肩吾同里□。日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>親聲調，無進取之意，交眷悉激勉，始游長安，不忍自衒鬻，竟不成</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名。將歸，以詩辭韓吏部云：“一生所遇惟元白，天下無人重布衣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>欲別朱門淚先盡，白頭游子白身歸。”知者憐之。遂歸舊隱，潛心詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酒。人間榮耀，徐山人不復貯齒頰中也。老病且貧，意泊無惱，優悠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自終。集一卷，今傳。余昔經桐廬古邑，山水蒼翠，嚴先生釣石，居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然無恙。忽自星沉，千載寥邈，后之學者，往往繼踵芳塵，文華偉杰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，義逼云天，產秀毓奇，此時為冠。至今有長吟高蹈之風，古碑石刻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>題名等，相傳不廢。攬轡徬徨，不忍去之。勝地以一人興，先賢為來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者重，固當相勉而無倦也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○裴夷直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    夷直，字禮卿，吳人。元和十年禮部侍郎崔群下進士，仕為中書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舍人。武宗立，以罪貶驩州司戶。宣宗初，為江、華二州刺史。終尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書左司員外郎、散騎常侍。工詩，有盛名。集一卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○薛濤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    濤，字洪度，成都樂妓也。性辨惠，調翰墨。居浣花里，種菖蒲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>滿門。傍即東北走長安道也。往來車馬留連。元和中，元微之使蜀，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>密意求訪，府公嚴司空知之，遣濤往侍。微之登翰林，以詩寄之曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“錦江滑膩峨嵋秀，幻出文君與薛濤。言語巧偷鸚鵡舌，文章分得鳳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>凰毛。紛紛詞客皆停筆，個個公侯欲夢刀。別后相思隔煙水，菖蒲花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>發五云高。”及武元衡入相，奏授校書郎。蜀人呼妓為校書，自濤始</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。后胡曾贈詩曰：“萬里橋邊女校書，枇杷樹下閉門居。掃眉才子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>知多少，管領春風總不知。”濤工為小詩，惜成都箋幅大，遂皆制狹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，不以為便，名曰：“薛濤箋”。且機警閑捷，座間談笑風生。高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>駢鎮蜀門日，命之佐酒，改一字愜音令，且得形象，曰：“口似沒梁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>斗。”答曰：“川似三條椽。”公曰：“奈一條曲何“曰：“相公為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>西川節度，尚用一破斗，況窮酒佐雜一曲椽，何足怪哉！”其敏捷類</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此特多，座客賞嘆。其所作詩，稍欺良匠，詞意不苟，情盡筆墨，翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>苑崇高，輒能攀附，殊不意裙裾之下出此異物，豈得匪其人而棄其學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>哉。大和中，卒。有《錦江集》五卷，今傳，中多名公贈答云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○姚合</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    合，陝州人，宰相崇之曾孫也。以詩聞。元和十一年，李逢吉知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貢舉，有夙好，因拔泥涂，鄭解榜及第。歷武功主簿，富平、萬年尉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。寶應中，除監察御史，遷戶部員外郎，出為金、杭二州刺史。后召</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人，拜刑戶二部郎中、諫議大夫、給事中。開成間，李商隱尉弘農，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以活囚忤觀察使孫簡，將罷去，會合來代簡，一見大喜，以風雅之契</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，即諭使還官，人雅服其義。后仕終秘書監。與賈島同時，號“姚、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賈”，自成一法。島難吟，有清冽之風；合易作，皆平澹之氣。興趣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>俱到，格調少殊。所謂方拙之奧，至巧存焉。蓋多歷下邑，官況蕭條</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，山縣荒涼，風景凋弊之間，最工模寫也。性嗜酒愛花，頹然自放，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人事生理，略不介意，有達人之大觀。所為詩十卷，及選集王維、祖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詠等一十八人詩為《極玄集》一卷，《序》稱維等皆詩家射雕手也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>又摭古人詩聯，敘其措意，各有體要，撰《詩例》一卷，今并傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李廓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    廓，宰相程之子也。少有志勛業，攬轡慨然，而未肯屑就，遂困</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>場屋中。作《下第》詩曰：“榜前潛制淚，眾里獨嫌身。氣味如中酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，情懷似別人。”時流皆稱賞，且憐之，因共推挽。元和十三年獨孤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>樟榜進士，調司經局正字，出為鄠縣令。累歷顯官，仕終武寧節度使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，政有奇績。工詩，極綺致。與賈島相友善。集今傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○章孝標</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    孝標，字道正，錢塘人。李紳鎮淮東時，春雪，孝標參座席，有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩名，紳命札請賦，唯然，索筆一揮云：“六出花飛處處飄，粘窗拂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>砌上寒條。朱門到晚難盈尺，盡是三軍喜氣消。”李大稱賞，荐于主</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文。元和十四年禮部侍郎庾承宣下進士及第，授校書郎。于長安將歸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>家慶，先寄友人曰：“及第全勝十政官，金湯鍍了出長安。馬頭漸入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>揚州郭，為報時人洗眼看。”紳適見，亟以一絕箴之曰：“假金方用</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>真金鍍，若是真金不鍍金。十載長安方一第，何須空腹用高心。”孝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>標慚謝。傷其氣宇窘急，終不大用。大和中，嘗為山南道從事，試大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>理評事。仕終秘書正字。有集一卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○施肩吾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    肩吾，字希聖，睦州人。元和十五年盧儲榜進士第后，謝禮部陳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍郎云：“九重城里無親識，八百人中獨姓施。”不待除授，即東歸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，張籍群公吟餞。人皆知有仙風道骨，寧戀人間升斗耶而少存箕、潁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之情，拍浮詩酒，搴擘煙霞。初讀書五行俱下，至是授真詮于仙長，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遂知逆順顛倒之法，與上中下精氣神三田反覆之義。以洪州西山，十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>二真君羽化之地，慕其真風，高蹈于此。題詩曰：“重重道氣結成神</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，玉闕金堂逐日新。若數西山得道者，兼余即是十三人。”早嘗賦《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閑居遣興詩》一百韻，頗述初心，大行于世。著《辨疑論》一卷，《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>西山傳道》、《會真》等記各一卷。述氣住則神住，神住則形住，為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《三住銘》一卷，及所為詩十卷，自為之序，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○袁不約</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    不約，字還朴，長慶三年鄭冠榜進士。大和中，以平判入等調官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。有詩傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○韓湘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    湘，字清夫，愈之侄孫也。長慶三年禮部侍郎王起下進士。落魄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不羈，見趣高遠，尤耽苦吟。公勉以經學，曰：“湘所學，公不知耶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“因賦詩以述志云：“青山云水窟，此地是吾家。后夜流瓊液，凌晨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>咀絳霞。琴彈碧玉調，爐煉白朱沙。寶鼎存金虎，元田養白鴉。一瓢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>藏世界，三尺斬妖邪。解造逡巡酒，能開頃刻花。有人能學我，同去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>看仙葩。”公笑曰：“子能奪造化乎“湘曰：“此事甚易。”公為開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>樽，湘聚土，以盆覆之，噀水，良久，開碧花二朵，花片上有詩一聯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“云橫秦嶺家何在，雪擁藍關馬不前。”公甚異怪，未喻其意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“他日驗之。”告違去。未几，公以諫佛骨事謫潮州刺史。一日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，途中見有人冒風雪從林間來，視乃湘也，再拜馬前曰：“公憶花上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之句乎“因詢其地，即藍關，嗟嘆久之，解鞍酒壚命酌，足成詩曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“一封朝奏九重天，夕貶潮陽路八千。本為聖朝除弊事，豈期衰朽送</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>殘年。云橫秦嶺家何在，雪擁藍關馬不前。知汝遠來應有意，好收吾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>骨瘴江邊。”又贈詩曰：“人才為世古來多，如子雄文孰可過。好待</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>功名成就日，卻抽身去上煙蘿。“湘笑而不答，獻詩別公曰：“舉世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>都為名利醉，惟吾來向道中醒。他時定是飛升去，沖破秋空一點青。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”遂別，竟不知所終。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韓琮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    琮，字成封，長慶四年李群榜進士及第。大中中，仕至湖南觀察</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>使。有詩名，多清新之制，錦不如也。《滻水送別》云：“綠暗紅稀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出鳳城，暮云樓閣古今情。行人莫聽宮前水，流盡年光是此聲。”《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>駱谷晚望》云：“秦川如畫渭如絲，去國還家一望時。公子王孫莫來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>好，嶺花多是斷腸枝。”如此等皆喧滿人口，余極多，皆稱是。集一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韋楚老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    楚老，長慶四年中書舍人李宗閔下進士，仕終國子祭酒。工詩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>氣既淳雄，語亦豪健。眾作古樂府居多。《祖龍行》曰：“黑云兵氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>射天裂，壯士朝眠夢冤結。祖龍一夜死沙丘，胡亥空隨鮑魚轍。腐肉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>偷生二千里，偽書先賜扶蘇死。墓接驪山土未干，瑞光已向芒碭起。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陳勝城中鼓三下，秦家天地如崩瓦。龍蛇撩亂入咸陽，少帝空隨漢家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>馬。”杰制頗多，俱當刮目。今并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○張祜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    祜，字承吉，南陽人，來寓姑蘇。樂高尚，稱處士。騷情雅思，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>凡知己者悉當時英杰。然不業程文。元和、長慶間，深為令狐文公器</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>許，鎮天平日，自草表荐，以詩三百首獻于朝，辭略曰：“凡制五言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，苞含六義，近多放誕，靡有宗師。祜久在江湖，早工篇什，研几甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>苦，搜象頗深，輩流所推，風格罕及。謹令繕錄，詣光順門進獻，望</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宣付中書門下。”祜至京師，屬元稹號有城府，偃仰內庭，上因召問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>祜之詞藻上下，稹曰：“張祜雕虫小巧，壯夫不為，若獎激大過，恐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>變陛下風教。”上頷之。由是寂寞而歸，為詩自悼云：“賀知章口徒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>勞說，孟浩然身更不疑。”遂客淮南。杜牧時為度支使，極相善待，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有贈云：“何人得似張公子，千首詩輕萬戶侯。“祜苦吟，妻孥每喚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之皆不應，曰：“吾方口吻生花，豈恤汝輩乎“性愛山水，多游名寺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，如杭之靈隱、天竺，蘇之靈岩、楞伽，常之惠山、善權，潤之甘露</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>、招隱，往往題詠絕唱。同時崔涯亦工詩，與祜齊名，頗自放行樂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>或乖興北里，每題詩倡肆，譽之則聲價頓增，毀之則車馬掃跡。涯尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>義，有《俠士》詩云：“太行嶺上三尺雪，崖涯袖中三尺鐵。一朝若</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遇有心人，出門便與妻兒別。”嘗共謁淮南李相，祜稱“釣鰲客”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李怪之曰：“釣鰲以何為竿“曰：“以虹。”“以何為鉤“曰：“新</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月。”“以何為餌“曰：“以‘短李’相也。”紳壯之，厚贈而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>晚與白樂天日相聚宴謔，樂天譏以“足下新作《憶柘枝》云‘鴛鴦鈿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帶拋何處，孔雀羅衫付阿誰’乃一問頭耳。”祜曰：“鄙薄之誚是也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。明公《長恨歌》曰：‘上窮碧落下黃泉，兩處茫茫都不見。’又非</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>目蓮尋母耶“一座大笑。初過廣陵曰：“十里長街市井連，月明橋上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>看神仙。人生只合揚州死，禪智山光好墓田。”大中中，果卒于丹陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>隱居，人以為讖云。詩一卷，今傳。衛蘧伯玉恥獨為君子，令狐公其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>庶几，元稹則不然矣。十譽不足，一毀有余，其事業淺深，于此可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>觀人也。爾所不知，人其舍諸稹謂祜雕虫瑣瑣，而稹所為，有不若是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>耶忌賢嫉能，迎戶而噬，略己而過人者，穿窬之行也。祜能以處士自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>終其身，聲華不借鐘鼎，而高視當代，至今稱之。不遇者天也，不泯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者亦天也，豈若彼取容阿附，遺臭之不已者哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉得仁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    得仁，公主之子也。長慶間以詩名。五言清瑩，獨步文場。自開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>成后至大中三朝，昆弟以貴戚皆擢顯仕，得仁獨苦工文。嘗立志，必</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不獲科第，不願儋人之爵也。出入舉場二十年，竟無所成，投跡幽隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，未嘗耿耿。有寄所知詩云：“外族帝王是，中朝親故稀。翻令浮議</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者，不許九霄蜚。”懮而不困，怨而不怒，哀而不傷，鏗鏘金玉，難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>合同流，而不厭于磨淬，端能確守格律，揣治聲病，甘心窮苦，不汲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>汲于富貴。王孫公子中，千載求一人不可得也。及卒，僧棲白吊之曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“思苦為詩身到此，冰魂雪魄已難招。直教桂子落墳上，生得一枝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>冤始銷。”有詩一卷行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○朱慶余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    慶余，字可久，以字行，閩中人。寶歷二年裴俅榜進士及第，授</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>秘省校書。得張水部詩旨，氣平意絕，社中哲匠也。有名當時。集一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷。今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○杜牧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    牧，字牧之，京兆人也。善屬文。大和二年韋籌榜進士，與厲玄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>同年。初未第，來東都，時主司侍郎為崔郾，太學博士吳武陵策蹇進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謁曰：“侍郎以峻德偉望，為明君選才，仆敢不薄施塵露。向偶見文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士十數輩，揚眉抵掌，共讀一卷文書，覽之，乃進士杜牧《阿房宮賦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》。其人，王佐才也。”因出卷，搢笏朗誦之。郾大加賞。曰：“請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>公與狀頭！”郾曰：“已得人矣。”曰：“不得，即請第五人。更否</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，則請以賦見還！”辭容激厲。郾曰：“諸生多言牧疏曠，不拘細行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，然敬依所教，不敢易也。”后又舉賢良方正科。沈傳師表為江西團</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>練府巡官。又為牛僧孺淮南節度府掌書記。拜侍御史，累遷左補闕，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷黃、池、睦三州刺史，以考功郎中知制誥，遷中書舍人。牧剛直有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>奇節，不為齪齪小謹，敢論列大事，指陳利病尤切。兵法戎機，平昔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>盡意。嘗以從兄悰更歷將相，而已困躓不振，怏怏難平。卒年五十，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>臨死自寫墓志，多焚所為文章。詩情毫邁，語率驚人。識者以擬杜甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，故稱“大杜““小杜“以別之。后人評牧詩，如銅丸走板，駿馬注</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>坡，謂圓快奮急也。牧美容姿，好歌舞，風情頗張，不能自遏。時淮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>南稱繁盛，不減京華，且多名妓絕色，牧恣心賞，牛相收街吏報杜書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>記平安帖子至盈篋。后以御史分司洛陽，時李司徒閑居，家妓為當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第一，宴朝士，以牧風憲，不敢邀。牧因遣諷李使召己，既至，曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“聞有紫云者，妙歌舞，孰是“即贈詩曰：“華堂今日綺筵開，誰喚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>分司御史來。忽發狂言驚四座，兩行紅袖一時回。”意氣閑逸，傍若</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無人，座客莫不稱異。大和末，往湖州，目成一女子，方十余歲，約</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以十年后吾來典郡，當納之，結以金幣。洎周墀入相，牧上箋乞守湖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>州，比至，已十四年，前女子從人，兩抱雛矣。賦詩曰：“自恨尋芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去較遲，不須惆悵怨芳時。如今風擺花狼藉，綠葉成陰子滿枝。”此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其大概一二。凡所牽系，情見于辭。別業樊川。有《樊川集》二十卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，及注《孫子》，并傳。同時有嚴惲，字子重，工詩，與牧友善，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《問春》詩得名。昔聞有集，今無之矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○楊發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    發，大和四年禮部侍郎鄭澣下第二人及第。工詩，亦當時聲韻之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>偉者。略舉一篇，《宿黃花館》云：“孤館蕭條槐葉稀，暮蟬聲隔水</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聲微。年年為客路長在，日日送人身未歸。何處離鴻迷浦月，誰家愁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>婦搗寒衣。夜深不臥帘猶卷，數點殘螢入戶飛。“俱瀏亮清新，頗驚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>凡聽。恨其出處事跡不得而知也。有詩傳世尚多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    遠，字求古，大和五年杜陟榜進士及第，蜀人也。少有大志，夸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>邁流俗，為詩多逸氣，五彩成文。早歷下邑，詞名卓然。宣宗時，宰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相令狐綯進奏擬遠杭州刺史，上曰：“朕聞遠詩有‘青山不厭千杯酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，白日惟銷一局棋。’是疏放如此，豈可臨郡理人“綯曰：“詩人托</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此以寫高興耳，未必實然。”上曰：“且令往觀之。”至，果有治聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。性簡儉，嗜啖鳧鴨。貴客經過，無他贈，厚者綠頭一雙而已。后歷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>忠、建、江三州刺史，仕終御史中丞。初牧湓城，求天寶遺物，得秦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僧收楊妃襪一裲，珍襲，呈諸好事者。會李群玉校書自湖湘來，過九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>江，遠厚遇之，談笑永日。群玉話及向賦《黃陵廟詩》，動朝云幕雨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之興，殊亦可怪。遠曰：“仆自獲凌波片玉，軟輕香窄，每一見，未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>嘗不在馬嵬下也。”遂更相戲笑，各有賦詩。后來頗為法家所短。蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多情少束，亦徒以微辭相感動耳。有詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李敬方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    敬方，字中虔，長慶三年鄭冠榜進士。大和中，仕為歙州刺史。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后坐事，左遷台州刺史。有詩一卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○許渾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    渾，字仲晦，潤州丹陽人，圉師之后也。大和六年李珪榜進士，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為當涂、太平二縣令。少苦學勞心，有清羸之疾，至是以伏枕免。久</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，起為潤州司馬。大中三年，拜監察御史，歷虞部員外郎，睦、郢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>二州刺史。嘗分司朱方，買田筑室，后抱病退居丁卯澗橋村舍，暇日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>綴錄所作，因以名集。渾樂林泉，亦慷慨悲歌之士。登高懷古，已見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>壯心，故為格調豪麗，猶強弩初張，牙淺弦急，俱無留意耳。至今慕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者極多，家家自謂得驪龍之照夜也。早歲嘗游天台，仰看瀑布，旁眺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>赤城，辨方廣于霏煙，躡石橋于懸壁，登陟兼晨，窮覽幽勝。朗誦孫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>綽古賦，傲然有思歸之想，志存不朽，再三信宿，彷徨不能去。以王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事不果，有負初心。后晝夢登山，有宮闕凌虛，問，曰：“此昆侖也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”少頃，遠見數人方飲，招渾就坐，暮而罷。一佳人出箋求詩，未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>成，夢破。后吟曰：“曉人瑤台露氣清，庭中惟見許飛瓊。塵心未斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>俗緣在，十里下山空月明。”他日復夢至山中，佳人曰：“子何題余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>姓名于人間“遂改為“天風吹下步虛聲”，曰：“善矣。”渾才思翩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翩，仙子所愛，夢寐求之，一至于此。昔子建賦《洛神》，人以徒聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>虛語，以是謂迂誕不信矣。未几遂卒。有詩二卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○雍陶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    陶，字國鈞，成都人。工于詞賦。少貧，遭蜀中亂后，播越羈旅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，有詩云：“貧當多病日，閑過少年時。”大和八年陳寬榜進士及第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，一時名輩，咸偉其作。然恃才傲睨，薄于親黨。其舅云安劉欽之下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第，歸三峽，卻寄陶詩云：“山近衡陽雖少雁，水連巴蜀豈無魚“得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩頗愧赧，遂通向不絕。大中六年，授國子毛詩博士。與賈島、殷堯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>藩、無可、徐凝、章孝標友善，以琴樽詩翰相娛，留長安中。大中末</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，出刺簡州，時名益重，自比謝宣城、柳吳興，國初諸人書奴耳。賓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至，必佯佯挫辱。投贄者少得通。秀才馮道明，時稱機捷，因罷舉請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謁，給閽者曰：“與太守有故。”陶倒屣，及見，呵責曰：“與足下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>素昧平生，何故之有“馮曰：“誦公詩文，室邇人遠，何隔平生“吟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陶詩數聯，如“立當青草人先見，行近白蓮魚未知。”又“閉門客到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>常如病，滿院花開未是貧。”又“江聲秋入峽，雨色夜侵樓“等句。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陶多其慕己，厚贈遣之。自負如此。后為雅州刺史，郭外有情盡橋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乃分衿祖別之所。因送客，陶怪之，遂于上立候館，改名折柳橋，取</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>古樂府《折楊柳》之義。題詩曰“從來只有情難盡，何事呼為情盡橋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自此改名為折柳，任它離恨一條條。”甚膾炙當時。竟辭榮，閑居廬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>岳，養鈳傲世，與塵事日冥矣。有《唐志集》五卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○賈馳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    馳，大和九年鄭確榜進士。初負才質，蹭蹬名場。來往公卿問，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>擔簦躡屩，莫伸其志。嘗入關賦詩云：“河上微風來，關頭樹初濕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>今朝關城吏，又見孤客人。上國誰與期，西來徒自急。”主司得聞，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有憐才之意，遂放第。不甚顯宦。詩文俱得美聲。后來文士集中，多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>稱賈先輩，其名譽為時所重云。有集傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○伍喬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    喬，少隱居廬山讀書，工為詩，與杜牧之同時擢第。初，喬與張</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>洎少友善，洎仕為翰林學士，眷寵優異，喬時任歙州司馬，自傷不調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，作詩寄洎，戒去仆曰：“俟張游宴，即投之。”洎得緘云：“不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何處好銷懮，公退攜樽即上樓。職事久參侯伯幕，夢魂長達帝王州。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>黃山向晚盈軒翠，黟水含春繞郡流。遙想玉堂多暇日，花時誰伴出城</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>游“洎動容久之，為言于上，召還為考功員外郎，卒官。今有詩二十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>余篇，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陳上美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    上美，開成元年禮部侍郎高鍇放榜第二人登科。以詩鳴當時，間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作悉佳制。論其骨格本峭，但少氣耳。有集今傳。夫矻矻窮經，志在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>死而不亡者，天道良難，無固必也。或稱碩儒，而名偶身喪；或乃頹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然，而青編不削。又若以位高金多，心廣體胖，而富貴驕人，文稱功</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>業黯黯，則未若腐草之有螢也。今群居論古終日，其人既遠，骨已朽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>矣，幸而照灼簡牘，未必皆揚雄、班、馬之流耳。于茲傳中，族匪聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>望，官不隆重，俱以一詠爭長歲月者亦多，豈曰小道而忽之。設有白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>璧，入地不滿尺，出土無膚寸，雖卞和憧憧往來其間，不失者亦鮮矣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。幸不幸之謂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李商隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    商隱，字義山，懷州人也。令狐楚奇其才，使游門下，授以文法</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，遇之甚厚。開成二年，高鍇知貢舉，楚善于鍇，獎譽甚力，遂擢進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>士。又中拔萃，楚又奏為集賢校理。楚出，王茂元鎮興元，素愛其才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，表掌書記，以子妻之。除待御史。茂元為李德裕黨，士流嗤謫商隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，以為詭薄無行，共排擯之。來京都，久不調。更依桂林總管鄭亞府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為判官，后隨亞謫循州，三年始回。歸窮于宰相綯，綯惡其忘家恩，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>放利偷合，從小人之辟，謝絕殊不展分。重陽日，因詣廳事，留題云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“十年泉下無消息，九日樽前有所思。”又云：“郎君官重施行馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，東閣無因許再窺。”綯見之惻然，乃補太學博士。柳仲郢節度東川</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，辟為判官。商隱廉介可畏，出為廣州都督，人或袖金以贈，商隱曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“吾自性分不可易，非畏人知也。”未几，入拜檢校吏部員外郎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>罷，客滎陽，卒。商隱工詩，為文瑰邁奇古，辭難事隱。及從楚學，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>儷偶長短，而繁縟過之。每屬綴，多檢閱書冊，左右鱗次，號“獺祭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>魚”。而旨能感人，人謂其橫絕前后。時溫庭筠、段成式各以穠致相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>夸。號“三十六體”。后評者謂其詩“如百寶流蘇，千絲鐵網，綺密</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>瑰妍，要非適用之具”。斯言信哉。初得大名，薄游長安，尚希識面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，因投宿逆旅，有眾客方酣飲，賦《木蘭花》詩就，呼與坐，不知為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>商隱也。后成一篇云：“洞庭波冷曉侵云，日日征帆送遠人。几度木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蘭船上望，不知元是此花身。”客問姓名，大驚稱罪。時白樂天老退</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，極喜商隱文章，曰：“我死后，得為爾兒足矣。”白死數年，生子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，遂以“白老“名之。既長，殊鄙鈍，溫飛卿戲曰：“以爾為待郎后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>身，不亦忝乎“后更生子，名袞師，聰俊。商隱詩云：“袞師我嬌兒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，英秀乃無匹。”此或其后身也。商隱文自成一格，后學者重之，謂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“西昆體“也。有《樊南甲集》二十卷，《乙集》二十卷，《玉溪生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩》三卷。初自號玉溪子。又賦一卷，文一卷，并傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○喻鳧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鳧，毗陵人，開成五年李從實榜進士，仕為烏程縣令。有詩名。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>晚歲變雅，鳧亦風靡，專工小巧，高古之氣掃地，所畏者務陳言之是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去耳。后來才子，皆稱“喻先輩”，向慕之情足見也。同時薛瑩亦工</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩。鳧詩一卷，瑩詩《洞庭集》一卷，今并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○薛逢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    逢，字陶臣，蒲州人。會昌元年，崔峴榜第三人進士。調萬年尉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。未几，佐河中幕府。崔鉉人相，引直宏文館。歷侍御史、尚書郎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>持論鯁切，以謀略高自顯布衣中，與劉瑑交，而文辭出逢下，常易瑑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，及當國，有荐逢知制誥者，瑑蝟言先朝以兩省官給事、舍人治州縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乃得除，逢未試州，不可。乃出為巴州刺史。初及第，與楊收、王鐸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>同年，而逢文藝最優。收輔政，逢有詩云：“誰知金印朝天客，同是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>沙堤避路人。”收銜之，斥為蓬、綿二州刺史。及鐸相，逢又賦詩云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“昨日鴻毛萬鈞重，今朝出岳一毫輕。”鐸怒。中外亦鄙逢褊傲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遷秘書監。卒。逢晚年岨峿宦途，嘗策羸赴朝，值新進士榜下，綴行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而出，呵殿整然，見逢行李蕭條，前導曰：“回避新郎君！”逢囅然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，因遣一介語之曰：“報道莫貧相，阿婆三五少年時，也曾東涂西抹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>來。”其人辟易。逢天資本高，學力亦贍，故不甚苦思，而自有豪逸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之態，第長短皆率然而成，未免失淺露俗，蓋亦當時所尚，非離群絕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>俗之詣也。夫道家三寶，其一不敢為天下先。前人者孰肯后之。加人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者孰能受之。觀逢恃才怠傲，恥在喧卑，而喋喋唇齒，亦猶惡醉而強</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酒也。累擯遠方，寸進尺退，至龍鐘而自憤不已，蓋禍福無不自己求</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者焉。有《詩集》十卷，又《別紙》十三卷，《賦集》十四卷，今并</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○趙嘏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嘏，字承祐，山陽人。會昌四年鄭言榜進士。大中中，仕為渭南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尉。一時名士大夫極稱道之。卑宦頗不如意。宣宗雅知其名，因問宰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相：“趙嘏詩人，曾為好官否可取其詩進來！”讀其卷首題秦詩云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“徒知六國隨斤斧，莫有群儒定是非。”上不悅，事寢。嘏嘗早秋賦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩曰：“殘星數點雁橫塞，長笛一聲人倚樓。”杜牧之呼為“趙倚樓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”，賞嘆之也。又初有詩，落句云：“早晚粗酬身事了，水邊歸去一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閑人。“仕途屹兀，豈其讖也！嘏豪邁爽達，多陪接卿相，出入館閤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，如親屬。然能以書生令遠近知重，所謂“一日名動京師，三日傳滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天下”，有自來矣。命沾仙尉，追蹤梅市，亦不惡耳。先嘏家浙西，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有美姬溺愛，及計偕，留侍母。會中元游鶴林寺，浙帥窺見悅之，奪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歸。明年嘏及第，自傷賦詩曰：“寂寞堂前日又曛，陽台去作不歸云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。當時聞說沙吒利，今日青娥屬使君。”帥聞之，殊慘慘，遣介送姬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>入長安。時嘏方出關，途次橫水驛，于馬上相遇，姬因抱嘏痛哭；信</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宿而卒，遂葬于橫水之陽。嘏思慕不已，臨終日有所見，時方四十余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。今有《渭南集》及《編年詩》二卷。悉取十三代史事跡，自始生至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>百歲，歲賦一首、二首，總得一百一十章。今并行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○薛能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    能，字太拙，汾州人。會昌六年狄慎思榜登第。大中末，書判入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>等中選，補盩厔尉。辟太原、陝虢、河陽從事。李福鎮滑台，表置觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>察判官。歷御史、都官、刑部員外郎。福徒帥西蜀，奏以自副。咸通</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，攝嘉州刺史。造朝，遷主客、度支、刑部郎中，俄為同州刺史、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>京兆大尹。出帥感化，入授工部尚書。復節度徐州，徙鎮忠武。廣明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元年，徐軍戍殷水，經許，能以軍多懷舊，惠館待于城中。許軍懼見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>襲，大將周岌乘眾疑怒，因為亂，逐能據城，自稱留后。數日，殺能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>并屠其家。能治政嚴察，絕請謁。耽癖于詩，日賦一章為課。性喜凌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人，格律卑卑，亦無甚高論。嘗以第一流自居，罕所拔拂。時劉得仁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>擅雅稱，持詩卷造能，能以句謝云：“千首加一首，卷初如卷終。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蓋譏其無變體也。量人如此，非厚德君子。晚節尚浮屠，奉法唯謹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>資性傲忽，又多佻輕忤世。及為藩鎮，每易武吏。嘗命其子屬橐鞬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雅拜新進士，或問其故，曰：“渠消弭災咎耳。”今有集十卷，及《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>繁城集》一卷傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李宣古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    宣古，字垂后，澧陽人。會昌三年盧肇榜進士。又試中宏辭。工</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文，極俊，有詩名。性謔浪，多所譏誚。時杜悰尚主，出守澧陽，宣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>古在館下，數陪宴賞，諧慢既深，悰不能忍，忿其戲己，辱之，使臥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于泥中，衣冠顛倒。長林公主素惜其才，勸曰：“尚書獨不念諸郎學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文，侍士如此，那得平陽之譽乎“遣人扶起，更以新服，赴中座，使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宣古賦詩，謝曰：“紅燈初上月輪高，照見堂前萬朵桃。觱栗調清銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>字管，琵琶聲亮紫檀槽。能歌奼女顏如玉，解飲蕭郎眼似刀。爭奈夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>深拋耍令，舞來挼去使人勞。”杜公賞之。后悰二子裔休、儒林皆中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第，人曰：“非母賢待師，不足成其子。”今諸集中往往載其作，有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>英氣，調頗清麗，惜不多見。竟薄命無印綬之譽，落莫自終。弟宣遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亦以詩鳴，今傳者可數也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○姚鵠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鵠，字居云，會昌三年禮部尚書王起下進士。多出入當時好士公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卿席幕，然吏才文價，俱不甚超。一名僅爾流播，亦多幸矣。詩一卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○項斯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    斯，字子遷，江東人也。會昌四年王起下第二人進士。始命潤州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>丹徒縣尉，卒于任所。開成之際，聲價藉甚，特為張水部所知賞，故</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其詩格頗與水部相類，清妙奇絕。鄭少師薰贈詩云：“項斯逢水部，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>誰道不關情。”斯性疏曠，溫飽非其本心。初筑草廬于朝陽峰前，交</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>結淨者，盤礡宇宙，戴蘚花冠，披鶴氅，就松陰，枕白石，飲清泉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>長哦細酌，凡如此三十余年。晚污一名，殊屈清致。其警聯如“病嘗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山藥遍，貧起草堂低。”如“客來因月宿，床勢向山移。”《下第》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“獨存過江馬，強拂看花衣”。《病僧》云：“不言身后事，猶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>坐病中禪。”又“湖山萬疊翠，門樹一行春。”又“一燈愁里夢，九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陌病中春。”如“月明古詩客初到，風度閑門僧未歸。”《宮人入道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“將敲碧落新齋磐，卻進昭陽舊賜箏“之類，不一而足，當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>盛稱。楊敬之祭酒贈詩云：“几度見君詩總好，及觀標格過于詩。平</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生不解藏人善，到處逢人說項斯。”其名以此益彰矣。集一卷，今行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○馬戴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    戴，字虞臣，華州人。會昌四年左仆射王起下進士，與項斯、趙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>嘏同榜，俱有盛名。初應辟佐大同軍幕府，與賈島、許棠唱答。苦家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貧，為祿代耕。歲廩殊薄，然終日吟事，清虛自如。《秋思》一絕曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“萬木秋霖后，孤山夕照余。田園無歲計，寒近憶樵漁。”調率如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此。后遷國子博士，卒。戴詩壯麗，居晚唐諸公之上，優游不迫，沉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>著痛快，兩不相傷，佳作也。早耽幽趣，既鄉里當名山，秦川一望，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>黃埃赤日，增起凌云之操。結茅堂玉女洗頭盆下，軒窗甚僻，對懸瀑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三十仞，往還多隱人。誰謂白頭從宦，俸不醫貧，徒興猿鶴之誚，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能無也。有詩一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○孟遲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    遲，字遲之，平昌人。會昌五年易重榜進士。有詩名，尤工絕句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，風流嫵媚，皆宮商金石之聲。情與顧非熊甚相得，且同年。有詩一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○任蕃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    蕃，會昌間人，家江東，多游會稽、苕、霅間。初亦舉進士之京</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不第。榜罷進謁主司曰：“仆本寒鄉之人，不遠萬里，手遮赤日，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>步來長安，取一第榮父母不得。侍郎豈不聞江東一任藩，家貧吟苦，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>忍令其去如來日也敢從此辭，彈琴自娛，學道自樂耳。”主司慚，欲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>留不可得。歸江湖，專尚聲調。去游天台巾子峰，題寺壁間云：“絕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>頂新秋生夜涼，鶴翻松露滴衣裳。前峰月照一江水，僧在翠微開竹房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”既去百余里，欲回改作“半江水”，行到題處，他人已改矣。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>復有題詩者，亡其姓名，曰：“任蕃題后無人繼，寂寞空山二百年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”才名類是。凡作必使人改視易聽，如《洛陽道》云：“憧憧洛陽道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，塵下生春草。行者豈無家，無人在家老。雞鳴前結束，爭去恐不早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。百年路傍盡，白日車中曉。求富江海狹，取貴山岳小。二端立在途</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，奔走何由了。”想蕃風度，此不足舉其梗概。有詩七十七首，為一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，今傳非全文矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○顧非熊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    非熊，姑蘇人，況之子也。少俊悟，一覽輒能成誦。工吟，揚譽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遠近。性滑稽好辯，頗雜笑言。凌轢氣焰子弟，既犯眾怒，擠排者紛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然。在舉場角藝三十年，屈聲破入耳。會昌五年，諫議大夫陳商放榜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初，上洽聞非熊詩價，至是怪其不第，敕有司進所試文章，追榜放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>令及第。劉得仁賀以詩曰：“愚為童稚時，已解念君詩。及得高科早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，須逢聖主知。”授盯眙主簿，不樂拜迎，再厭鞭撻，因棄官歸隱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王司馬建送詩去：“江城柳色海門煙，欲到茅山始下船。知道君家當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>瀑布，菖蒲潭在草堂前。”一時餞別吟贈俱名流。不知所終，或傳住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>茅山十余年，一旦遇異人，相隨入深谷，不復出矣。有詩一卷，今行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○曹鄴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鄴，字鄴之，桂林人。累舉不第，為《四怨三愁五情》詩，雅道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甚古。時為舍人韋愨所知，力荐于禮部侍郎裴休。大中四年張溫琪榜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中第。看榜日，上主司詩云：“一辭桂岩猿，九泣都門月。年年孟春</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至，看花如看雪。”《杏園宴間呈同年》云：“岐路不在天，十年行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不至。一旦公道開，青云在平地。”又云：“匆匆出九衢，童仆顏色</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>異。故衣未及換，尚有去年淚。”又云：“永持共濟心，莫起胡越意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”佳句類此甚多，志特勤苦。仕至洋州刺史。有集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鄭嵎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嵎，字賓光，大中五年李郜榜進士。有集一卷，名《津陽門詩》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。津陽，即華清宮之外闕。詢求父老，為詩百韻，皆紀明皇時事者也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉駕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    駕，字司南，大中六年禮部侍郎崔嶼下進士。初與曹鄴為友，深</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相結，俱工古風詩。鄴既擢第，不忍先歸，待長安中，賀成名，乃同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歸范蠡故山。時國家復河、湟故地，有歸馬放牛之象，賀獻樂府十章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，《序》曰：“駕生唐二十八年，獲見明天子以德歸河、湟，臣得與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天下夫婦復為太平人。恨愚且賤，不得拜舞上前，作詩十篇，雖不足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貢聲宗廟，形容盛德，願與耕稼陶漁者，歌江湖田野間，亦足自快。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”詩奏，上甚悅，累歷達官。駕詩多比興含蓄，體無定規，意盡即止</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，為時所宗。今集一卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○方干</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    干，字雄飛，桐廬人。幼有清才，散拙無營務。大中中，舉進士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不第，隱居鏡湖中，湖北有茅齋，湖西有松島，每風清月明，攜稚子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄰叟，輕棹往返，甚愜素心。所住水木幽閟，一草一花，俱能留客。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>家貧，蓄古琴，行吟醉臥以自娛。徐凝初有詩名，一見干器之，遂相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>師友，因授格律。干有贈凝詩云：“把得新詩草里論。”時謂反語為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>村里老，疑干譏誚，非也。干貌陋兔缺，性喜凌侮。王大夫廉問浙東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，禮邀干至，誤三拜，人號為“方三拜”。王公嘉其操，將荐于朝，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>托吳融草表，行有日，王公以疾逝去，事不果成。干早歲偕計，往來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>兩京，公卿好事者爭延納，名竟不入手，遂歸，無復榮辱之念。浙中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>凡有園林名勝，輒造主人，留題几遍。初李頻學干為詩，頻及第，詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僧清越賀云：“弟子已折桂，先生猶灌園。”咸通末卒。門人相與論</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>德謀跡。謚曰玄英先生。樂安孫郃等綴其遺詩三百七十余篇，為十卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，王贊論之曰：“鏝肌滌骨，冰瑩霞絢。嘉肴自將，不吮余雋。麗不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>葩芬，苦不瞿棘。當其得志，倏與神會。詞若未至，意已獨往。”郃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>亦論曰：“其秀也，仙蕊于常花；其鳴也，靈鼉于眾響。”觀其所述</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>論，不過矣。古黔婁先生死，曾參與門人來吊，問曰：“先生終，何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以謚“妻曰：“以‘康’。”參曰：“先生存時，食不充遝，衣不蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>形，死則手足不斂，傍無酒肉。生不美，死不榮，何樂而謚為康哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”妻曰：“昔先生國君用為相，辭不受，是有余貴也。君饋栗三十鐘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，辭不納，是有余富也。先生甘天下之淡味，安天下之卑位，不戚戚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于貧賤，不遑遑于富貴，求仁得仁，求義得義，謚之以康，不亦宜乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”方干，韋布之士，生稱高尚，死謚玄英，其梗概大節，庶几乎黔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>婁者耶！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李頻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    頻，字得新，睦州壽昌人。少秀悟，長，廬西山。多記覽，于詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>特工。與同里方干為師友。給事中姚合時稱詩穎，頻不憚走千里丐其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>品第，合見，大加獎挹，且愛其標格，即以女妻之。大中八年，顏標</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>榜擢進士，調秘書郎，為南陵主簿。試判入等，遷武功令。頻性耿介</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，難干以非理。賑飢民，戢豪右，于是京畿多賴，事事可傳。懿宗嘉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之，賜緋銀魚，擢侍御史。守法不阿，遷都官員外郎。表乞建州刺史</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，至則布條教，以禮治下。時盜所在沖突，惟建賴頻以安。未几卒官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下，櫬隨家歸，父老相與扶柩哀悼，葬永樂州，為立廟于梨山，歲時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>祭祠，有災沴必禱，垂福逮今。頻詩雖出晚年，體制多與劉隨州相抗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，騷嚴風謹，慘慘逼人。有詩一卷，今行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李群玉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    群玉，字文山，澧州人也。清才曠逸，不樂仕進，專以吟詠自適</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，詩筆遒麗，文體丰妍。好吹笙，美翰墨。如王、謝子弟，別有一種</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風流。親友強之赴舉，一上即止。裴相公休觀察湖南，厚禮延致之郡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，嘗勉之曰：“處士被褐懷玉，浮云富貴，名高而身不知，神寶寧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>久棄荒途子其行矣。”大中八年，以草澤臣來京，詣闕上表，自進詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三百篇。休適人相，復論荐。上悅之，敕授弘文館校書郎。李頻使君</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>呼為從兄。歸湘中，題詩二妃廟，是暮宿山舍，夢見二女子來曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>兒娥皇、女英也，承君佳句，徽珮將游于汗漫，願相從也。”俄而影</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>滅。群玉自是郁郁，歲余而卒。段成式為詩哭曰：“曾話黃陵事，今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為白日催。老無男女累，誰哭到泉台。”今有詩三卷、后集五卷行世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。夫澧浦，古騷人之國。屈平仁遭譖毀，不知所訴，心煩意亂，賦為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《離騷》。騷，愁也。已矣哉。國無人知我兮，又何懷乎故都委身魚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>腹，魂招兮不來。芳草萎薾，蕭艾參天，奚獨一時而然也。群玉繼稟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>修能，翱翔大化，人不知而不恤，祿不及而不言。望涔陽之亡極，挹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>杜蘭之緒馨，款君門以披懷，沾一命而潛退，風景滿目，寧無愧于古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人。故其格調清越，而多登山臨水、懷人送歸之制，如“遠客坐長夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，雨聲孤寺秋。請量東海水，看取淺深愁“等句，已曲盡羈旅坎壈之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>情。壯心千里，于方寸不擾，亦大難矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李郢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    郢，字楚望，大中十年崔鉶榜進士及第。初居余杭，出有山水之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>興，人有琴書之娛，疏于馳競。歷為藩鎮從事，后拜侍御史。郢工詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，理密辭閑，個個珠玉。其清麗極能寫景狀懷，每使人竟日不能釋卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。與清塞、賈島最相善。時塞還俗，聞島尋卒，郢重來錢塘，俱絕音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>響，感而賦詩曰：“卻到城中事事傷，惠休還俗賈生亡。誰人收得文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>章篋，獨我重經苔鮮房。一命未沾為逐客，萬緣初盡別空王。蕭蕭竹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>塢殘陽在，葉覆閑階雪擁牆。”其它警策率類此。有集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○儲嗣宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嗣宗，大中十三年孔緯榜及第。與顧非熊先生相結好，大得詩名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。苦思夢索，所謂逐句留心，每字著意，悠然皆塵外之想。覽其所作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，及見其人。警聯如：“綠毛辭世女，白發人壺翁。”又“片水明在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>野，萬花深見人。”又“黃鶴有歸語，白云無忌心。”又“蟬鳴月中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>樹，風落客前花。”又“池亭千里月，煙水一封書。”又“鶴語松上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月，花明云里春。”又“一酌水邊酒，數聲花下琴。”又“宿草風悲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>夜，荒村月吊人。”《哭彭先生》云：“空階鶴戀丹青影，秋雨苔封</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>白石床。”《題閑居》云：“鳥啼碧樹閑臨水，花滿青山靜掩門。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>等句，皆區區所當避舍者也。有集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○劉滄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    滄，字蘊靈，魯國人也。體貌魁梧，尚氣節，善飲酒，談古今令</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人終日喜聽。慷慨懷古，率見于篇。大中八年禮部侍郎鄭薰下進士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>榜后進謁謝，薰曰：“初謂劉君銳志，一第不足取。故人別來三十載</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不相知聞，誰渭今白頭紛紛矣。”調華原尉。與李頻同年。詩極清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>麗，句法絕同趙嘏、許渾，若出一絇綜然。詩一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陳陶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    陶，字嵩伯，鄱陽劍浦人。嘗舉進士輒下，為詩云：“中原不是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無麟鳳，自是皇家結網疏。”頗負壯懷，志遠心曠，遂高居不求進達</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，恣游名山，自稱“三教布衣”。大中中，避亂入洪州西山，學神仙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>咽氣有得，出入無間。時嚴尚書宇牧豫章，慕其清操，嘗備齋供，俯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>就山中，揮談終日。而欲試之，遣小妓蓮花往侍，陶笑不答。蓮花賦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩求去曰：“蓮花為號玉為腮，珍重尚書送妾來。處士不生巫峽夢，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>虛勞云雨下陽台。”陶賦詩贈之云：“近來詩思清于水，老去風情薄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>似云。已向升天得門戶，錦衾深愧卓文君。”宇見詩益嘉貞節。陶金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>骨已堅，戒行通體，夜必鶴氅，焚香巨石上，鳴金步虛，禮星月，少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寐。所止茅屋，風雷洶洶不絕。忽一日不見，惟鼎灶杵臼依然。開寶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>間，有樵者入深谷，猶見無恙。后不知所終。陶工賦詩，無一點塵氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。于晚唐諸人中，最得平淡，要非時流所能企及者。有《文錄》十卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鄭巢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    巢，錢塘人。大中間舉進士。時姚合號詩宗，為杭州刺史，巢獻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所業，日游門館，累陪登覽燕集，大得獎重，如門生禮然。體效格法</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，伏膺無斁，句意且清新。巢性疏野。兩浙湖山寺宇幽勝，多名僧，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外學高妙，相與往還酬酢，竟亦不仕而終。有詩一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○于武陵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    武陵，名鄴，以字行，杜曲人也。大中時，嘗舉進士，不稱意，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>攜書與琴，往來商洛、巴蜀間，或隱于卜中，存獨醒之意。避地嘿嘿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，語不及榮貴，少與時輩交游。嘗南來至瀟湘，愛汀洲芳草，況是古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>騷人舊國，風景不殊，欲卜居未果，歸老嵩陽別墅。詩多五言，興趣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>飄逸多感，每終篇一意，策名當時，集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○來鵬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鵬，豫章人，家徐孺子亭邊，林園自樂，師韓、柳為文。大中、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>咸通間，才名藉甚。鵬工詩，蓄銳既久，自傷年長，家貧不達，頗亦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>忿忿，故多寓意譏訕。當路雖賞清麗，不免忤情，每為所忌。如《金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>錢花》云：“青帝若教花里用，牡丹應是得錢人。“《夏云》云：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無限旱苗枯欲盡，悠悠閑處作奇峰。”《偶題》云：“可惜青天好雷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>電，只能驚起懶蛟龍。”坐是凡十上不得第。韋岫尚書獨賞其才，延</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>待幕中，攜以游蜀。又欲納為婿，不果。是年力荐，夏課卷中獻詩有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“一夜綠荷風剪破，嫌它秋雨不成珠。”岫以為不祥，果失志。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時遭廣明庚子之亂，鵬避地游荊襄，艱難險阻，南返。中和，客死于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>維揚逆旅，主人賢，收葬之。有詩一卷，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○溫庭筠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    庭筠，字飛卿，舊名岐，并州人，宰相彥博之孫也。少敏悟，天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才雄贍，能走筆成萬言。善鼓琴吹笛，云：“有弦即彈，有孔即吹，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何必爨桐與柯亭也。”側詞艷曲，與李商隱齊名，時號“溫、李”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才情綺麗，尤工律賦。每試，押官韻，燭下未嘗起草，但籠袖憑几，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>每一韻一吟而已，場中曰：“溫八吟”。又謂八叉手成八韻，名“溫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>八叉”。多為鄰鋪假手。然薄行無檢幅，與貴胄裴誠、令狐滈等飲博</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。后夜嘗醉詬狹邪間，為邏卒折齒，訴不得理。舉進士，數上又不第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。出入令狐相國書館中，待遇甚優。時宣宗喜歌《菩薩蠻》，綯假其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>新撰進之，戒令勿泄，而遽言于人。綯又嘗問玉條脫事，對以出《南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>華經》，且曰：“非僻書，相公燮理之暇，亦宜覽古。”又有言曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“中書省內坐將軍。”譏綯無學，由是漸疏之。自傷云：“因知此恨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人多積，悔讀《南華》第二篇。”徐商鎮襄陽，辟巡官，不得志，游</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>江東。大中末，山北沈侍郎主文，特召庭筠試于帘下，恐其潛救。是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>日不樂，逼暮先請出，仍獻啟千余言。詢之，已占授八人矣。執政鄙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其為，留長安中待除。宣宗微行，遇于傳舍，庭筠不識，傲然詰之曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“公非司馬、長史流乎“又曰：“得非六參、簿、尉之類“帝曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“非也。”后謫方城尉，中書舍人裴坦當制，忸怩含毫久之，詞曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“孔門以德行居先，文章為末。爾既早隨計吏，宿負雄名，徒夸不羈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之才，罕有適時之用。放騷人于湘浦，移賈誼于長沙，尚有前席之期</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，未爽抽毫之思。”庭筠之官，文士詩人爭賦詩祖餞，惟紀唐夫擅場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，曰：“鳳凰詔下雖沾命，鸚鵡才高卻累身。”唐夫舉進士，有詞名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。庭筠仕終國子助教。竟流落而死。今有《漢南真稿》十卷，《握蘭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>集》三卷，《金筌集》十卷，詩集五卷，及《學海》三十卷。又《采</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><h5>茶錄》一卷。及著《乾蓬S子》一卷，《序》云“不爵不觥，非炰非</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><h5>炙，能悅諸心，庶乎乾蓬S之義“等，并傳于世。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○魚玄機</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    玄機，長安人，女道士也。性聰慧，好讀書，尤工韻調，情致繁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>縟。咸通中及笄，為李億補闕侍寵。夫人妒，不能容，億遣隸咸宜觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>披戴。有怨李詩云：“易求無價寶，難得有心郎。”與李郢端公同巷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，居止接近，詩筒往反。復與溫庭筠交游，有相寄篇什。嘗登崇真觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>南樓，睹新進士題名，賦詩曰：“云峰滿目放春情，歷歷銀鉤指下生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。自恨羅衣掩詩句，舉頭空羨榜中名。”觀其志意激切，使為一男子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，必有用之才，作者頗賞憐之。時京師諸宮宇女郎，皆清俊濟楚，簪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>星曳月，惟以吟詠自遣，玄機杰出，多見酬酢云。有詩集一卷，今傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○邵謁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    謁，韶州翁源縣人。少為縣廳吏，客至倉卒，令怒其不搘床迎待</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，逐去。遂截髻著縣門上，發憤讀書。書堂距縣十余里，隱起水心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謁平居如里中兒未著冠者，發鬅鬠，野服。苦吟，工古調。咸通七年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>抵京師，隸國子。時溫庭筠主試，憫擢寒苦，乃榜謁詩三十余篇，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>振公道，曰：“前件進士，識略精微，堪裨教化，聲詞激切，曲備風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謠，標題命篇，時所難著，燈燭之下，雄辭卓然。誠宜榜示眾人，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敢獨專華藻，仍請申堂，并榜禮部。”已而釋褐。后赴官，不知所終</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。它日，縣民祠神者，持幘舞鈴，忽自稱“邵先輩降”。鄉里前輩皆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>至，作禮問曰：“今者辱來，能強為我賦詩乎“巫即書一絕云：“青</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山山下少年郎，失意當時別故鄉。惆悵不堪回首望，隔溪遙見舊書堂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”詞詠淒苦，雖椽筆不逮，鄉老中曉聲病者，至為感泣咨嗟。今有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○于濆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    濆，字子漪，咸通二年裴延魯榜進士。患當時作詩者，拘束聲律</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而入輕浮，故作《古風》三十篇以矯弊俗，自號“逸詩”。今一卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳于世。觀唐詩至此間，弊亦極矣，獨奈何國運將弛，士氣日喪，文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不能不如之。嘲云戲月，刻翠粘紅，不見補于采風，無少裨于化育，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>徒務巧于一聯，或伐善于只字，悅心快口，何異秋蟬亂鳴也。于濆、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>邵謁、劉駕、曹鄴等，能反棹下流，更唱瘖俗，置聲祿于度外，患大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雅之凌遲，使耳厭鄭、衛，而忽洗云和；心醉醇醲，而乍爽玄酒。所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謂清清泠泠，愈病析酲。逃空虛者，聞人足音，不亦快哉。晉處士戴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>顒春日攜斗酒，往樹下聽黃鸝，曰“此俗耳針砭，詩腸鼓吹“者，豈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>徒然哉。于數子亦云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○李昌符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    昌符，字若夢，咸通四年禮部侍郎蕭仿下進士。工詩，在長安與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭谷酬贈，仕終膳部員外郎。嘗作《奴婢詩》五十首，有云：“不論</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>秋菊與春花，個個能童空肚茶。”無事莫教頻入庫，每般閑物要些些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“等句。后為御史劾奏，以為輕薄為文，多妨政務，虧嚴重之德，唱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>誹戲之風。謫去，匏系終身。有詩集一卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○翁綬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    綬，咸通六年中書舍人李蔚下進士。工詩，多近體，變古樂府，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>音韻雖響，風骨憔悴，真晚唐之移習也。后亦間關，名不甚顯。固知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閭巷之人，欲砥行立名者，非附青云之上，惡能施于后世哉。有詩今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○汪遵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    遵，宣州涇縣人。幼為小吏，晝夜讀書良苦，人皆不覺。咸通七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年韓袞榜進士。遵初與鄉人許棠友善，工為絕句詩，而深自晦密。以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>家貧難得書，必借于人，徹夜強記，棠實不知。一旦辭役就貢，棠時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>先在京師，偶送客至灞、滻間，忽遇遵于途，行李索然，棠訊之曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“汪都何事來“遵曰：“此來就貢。”棠怒曰：“小吏不忖，而欲與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棠同研席乎“甚侮慢之。后遵成名五年，棠始及第。洛中有李相德裕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>平泉莊，佳景殊勝，李未几坐事貶朱崖，遵過，題詩曰：“平泉風景</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>好高眠，水色嵐光滿目前。剛欲平它不平事，至今惆悵滿南邊。”又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《過楊相宅》詩云：“倚伏從來事不遙，無何平地起青霄。才到青霄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卻平地，門對古槐空寂寥。”俱為時人稱賞。其余警策稱是。有集今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳。汪遵，涇之一走耳。拔身卑污，奪譽文苑。家貧借書，以夜繼日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，古人閱市偷光，殆不過此。昔溝中之斷，今席上之珍，丈夫自修，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不當如是耶與夫朱門富家，積書萬卷，束在高閣，塵暗簽軸，蠹落帙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>帷，網好學之名，欺盲聾之俗，非三變之敗，無一展之期，諺曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>金玉有余，買鎮宅書。”嗚呼哀哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○沈光</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    光，吳興人。咸通七年禮部侍郎趙騭下進士。工文章古詩，標致</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翹楚，大得美稱。嘗作《洞庭樂賦》，韋岫見之曰：“此乃一片宮商</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。”又如《太白酒樓記》等文，皆儀表于世。有詩集及《云夢子》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>五卷，并傳世。光風鑒澄爽，神情俊邁。后仕終侍御史云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○趙牧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    牧，不知何處人。大中、咸通中，累舉進士不第。有俊才，負奇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>節，遂舍場屋，放浪人間。效李長吉為歌詩，頗涉狂怪，聳動當時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蹙金結繡，而無痕跡裝染。其余輕巧之詞甚多。同時有劉光遠，亦慕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>長吉，凡作體效猶，能埋沒意緒。竟不知所終。俱有詩傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○羅鄴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鄴，余杭人也。家貲鉅萬，父則為鹽鐵吏，子二人，俱以文學干</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>進。鄴尤長律詩。時宗人隱、虯，俱以聲格著稱，遂齊名，號“三羅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”。隱雄麗而坦率，鄴清致而聯綿，虯則區區而已。咸通中，數下第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，有詩云：“故鄉依舊空歸去，帝里如同不到來。”崔安潛侍郎廉問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>江西，鄴適飄蓬湘、浦間，崔素賞其作，志在弓旌，竟為幕吏所沮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>既而俯就督郵，不得志，踉蹌北征，赴職單于牙帳。鄴去家逾遠，萬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>里沙漠，滿目誰親，因茲舉事闌珊無成，于邑而卒。鄴素有英資，筆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>端超絕，其氣宇亦不在諸人下。初無箕裘之訓，頓改門風，崛興音韻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，馳譽當時，非易事也。而跋前疐后，絕域無聊，獨奈其命薄何！孔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子曰：“才難”，信然。有詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○胡曾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    曾，長沙人也。咸通中進士。初，再三下第，有詩云：“翰苑几</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時休嫁女，文章早晚罷生兒。上林新桂年年發，不許閑人折一枝。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曾，天分高爽，意度不凡，視人間富貴亦悠悠。遨歷四方，馬跡窮歲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月，所在必公卿館谷。上交不諂，下交不瀆，奇士也。嘗為漢南節度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>從事。作《詠史詩》，皆題古君臣爭戰廢興塵跡。經覽形勝，關山亭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>障，江海深阻，一一可賞。人事雖非，風景猶昨，每感輒賦，俱能使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人奮飛。至今庸夫孺子，亦知傳誦。后有擬效者，不逮矣。至于近體</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>律絕等，哀怨清楚，曲盡幽情，擢居中品，不過也。惜其才茂而身未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>穎脫，痛哉。今《詠史詩》一卷，有咸通中人陳蓋注，及《安定集》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>十卷行世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李山甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    山甫，咸通中累舉進士不第，落魄有不羈才。須髯如戟，能為青</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>白眼。生平憎俗子，尚豪俠，雖簞食豆羹，自甘不厭。為詩托諷，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>得志，每狂歌痛飲，拔劍斫地，少攄郁郁之氣耳。后流寓河、朔間，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>依樂彥稹為魏博從事，不得眾情，以陵傲之，故無所遇。嘗有《老將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩》曰：“校獵燕山經几春，雕弓白羽不離身。年來馬上渾無力，望</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>見飛鴻指擬人。”此傷其蹇薄無成，時人憐之。后不知所終。山甫詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文激切，耿耿有齊氣，多感時懷古之作。今集一卷、賦二卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○曹唐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    唐，字堯賓，桂州人。初為道士，工文賦詩。大中間舉進士，咸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>通中，為諸府從事。唐與羅隱同時，才情不異。唐始起清流，志趣澹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然，有凌云之骨，追慕古仙子高情，往往奇遇而已，才思不減，遂作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《大游仙詩》五十篇，又《小游仙詩》等，紀其悲歡離合之要，大播</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于時。唐嘗會隱，各論近作。隱曰：“聞兄《游仙》之制甚佳，但中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聯云：‘洞里有天春寂寂，人間無路月茫茫，’乃是鬼耳。”唐笑曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“足下《牡丹》詩一聯，乃詠女子障，‘若教解語應傾國，任是無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>情也動人。’“于是座客大笑。唐平生志甚激昂，至是薄宦，頗自郁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悒，為《病馬》詩以自況，警聯如：“尾盤夜雨紅絲脆，頭捽秋風白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>練低。”又云：“風吹病骨無驕氣，土蝕驄花見臥痕。“又云：“飲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>驚白露泉花冷，吃怕清秋豆葉寒。”皆膾炙人口。忽一日晝夢仙女，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鶯服花冠，衣如煙霧，倚樹吟唐詠天台劉、阮詩，欲相招而去者，唐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>驚覺，頗怪之。明日暴病卒，亦感憶之所致也。有詩集二卷，今傳于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。人云：有德者或無文，有文者或無德。文德兼備，古今所難。《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>典論》謂文人相輕，從古而然，各以所長，相輕所短。矛盾之極，則</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>是非鋒起，隙始于毫末，禍大于丘山，前后類此多矣。夫以口舌常談</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，無益無損，每至喪清德，負良友，承輕薄子之名，乏藏疾匿瑕之量</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。如此，功業未見其超者矣。君子所慎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○皮日休</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    日休，字襲美，一字逸少，襄陽人也。隱居鹿門山，性嗜酒，癖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩，號“醉吟先生”，又自稱“醉士“；且傲誕，又號“間氣布衣”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，言已天地之間氣也。以文章自負，尤善箴銘。咸通八年禮部侍郎鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>愚下及第。為著作郎，遷太常博士。時值末年，虎狼放縱，百姓手足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無措，上下所行，皆大亂之道，遂作《鹿門隱書》六十篇，多譏切謬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>政。有云：“毀人者自毀之，譽人者自譽之。”又曰：“不思而立言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，不知而定交，吾其憚也。”又曰：“古之殺人也怒，今之殺人也笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”又曰：“古之置吏也將以逐盜，今之置吏也將以為盜“等，皆有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所指云爾。日休性沖泊無營，臨難不懼。乾符喪亂，東出關，為毗陵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>副使，陷巢賊中，巢惜其才，授以翰林學士。日休惶恐，跼踧欲死，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>未能劫。令作言□文以惑眾，曰：“欲知聖人姓，田八二十一；欲知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聖人名，果頭三屈律。”賊疑其衷恨必譏己，遂殺之。臨刑神色自若</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，無知不知皆痛惋也。日休在鄉里，與陸龜蒙交擬金蘭，日相贈和。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自集所為文十卷，名《文藪》，及詩集一卷，《滑台集》七卷，又著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《皮氏鹿門家鈔》九十卷，并傳。夫次韻唱酬，其法不古，元和以前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，未之見也。暨令狐楚、薛能、元稹、白樂天集中，稍稍開端。以意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相和之法漸廢間作。逮日體、龜蒙，則飆流頓盛，猶空谷有聲，隨響</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>即答。韓偓、吳融以后，守之愈篤，汗漫而無禁也。于是天下翕然，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>順下風而趨，至數十反而不已，莫知非焉。夫才情斂之不盈握，散之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>彌八紘，遣意于時間，寄興于物表，或上下出入，縱橫流散，游刃所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及，孰非我有，本無拘縛惉懘之忌也。今則限以韻聲，莫違次第，得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>佳韻則杳不相干，岨峿難入；有當事則韻不能強，進退雙違。必至窘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>束長才，牽接非類，求無瑕片玉，千不遇焉，詩家之大弊也。更以言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>巧稱工，夸多斗麗，足見其少雍容之度。然前修有恨其迷途既遠，無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>法以救之矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陸龜蒙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    龜蒙，字魯望，姑蘇人。幼而聰悟，有高致，明《春秋》，善屬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>文，尤能談笑。詩體江、謝，名振全吳。家藏書萬卷，無少聲色之娛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。舉進士一不中。嘗從張搏游，歷湖、蘇二州，將辟以自佐。又嘗至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>饒州，三日無所詣，剌吏率官屬就見，龜蒙不樂，拂衣去。居松江甫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>里，多所撰論。有田數百畝，屋三十楹。田苦下，雨澇則與江通，故</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>常患飢。身自畚鍤，菻刺無休時，或譏其勞，曰：“堯、舜霉瘠，禹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>胼胝。彼聖人也，吾一褐衣，敢不勤乎“龜蒙嗜飲茶，置小園顧渚山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下，歲人茶租，薄為甌蟻之費。著書一編，繼《茶經》、《茶訣》之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后，又判品張又新《水說》為七種。好事者雖惠山、虎丘、松江，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遠百里為致之。又不喜與流俗交，雖造門亦罕納。不乘馬，每寒暑得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，體無事時，放扁舟，挂蓬席，賚束書、茶灶、筆床、釣具，鼓棹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鳴榔，太湖三萬六千傾，水天一色，直入空明。或往來別浦，所詣小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不會意，徑往不留。自稱“江湖散人”，又號“天隨子“、“甫里先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生”。漢涪翁、漁父、江上丈人，嘗謂即已。后以高士征，不至。苦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吟，極清麗。與皮日休為耐久交。中和初，遘疾卒。吳融誄文曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>霏漠漠，淡涓涓，春融冶，秋鮮妍。觸即碎，潭下月；拭不滅，玉上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>煙。”今有《笠澤叢書》三卷，《詩編》十卷，賦六卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○司空圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    圖，字表聖，河中人也。父輿，大中時為商州刺史。圖，咸通十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年歸仁紹榜進士。主司王凝初典絳州，圖時方應舉，自別墅到郡上謁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，去，閽吏遽申司空秀才出郭門。后人郭訪親知，即不造郡齋。公謂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其尊敬，愈重之。及知貢，圖第四人捷，同年鄙薄者謗曰：“此司空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>圖得一名也。”公頗聞，因宴全榜，宣言曰：“凝叨忝文柄，今年榜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>貼，專為司空先輩一人而已。”由是名益振。未几，凝為宣歙觀察使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，辟置幕府。召拜殿中侍御史，不忍去凝府，台劾，左遷光祿寺主簿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。盧相攜還朝，過陝虢，訪圖，深愛重，留詩曰：“氏族司空貴，官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>班御史雄。老夫如且在，未可嘆途窮。”就屬于觀察使盧渥曰：“司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>空御史，高士也。”渥遂表為僚佐。攜執政，召拜禮部員外郎，尋遷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎中。丁黃巢亂，間關至河中，僖宗次鳳翔，知制誥、中書舍人。景</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>福中，拜諫議大夫，不赴。昭宗在華州，召為兵部侍郎，以足疾自乞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，聽還。圖家本中條山王官谷，有先人田廬，遂隱不出，作亭榭素室</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，悉畫唐興節士文人像。嘗曰：“其宦情蕭索，百事無能。量才一宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>休，揣分二宜休。耄而聵三宜休。”遂名其亭曰“三休”。作文以伸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>志，自號“知非子“、“耐辱居士”。言涉詭激不常，欲免當時之禍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。初以風雨夜得古寶劍，慘淡精靈，嘗佩出入。性苦吟，舉筆緣興，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>几千萬篇。自致于繩檢之外，豫置塚棺，遇勝日，引客坐壙中，賦詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酌酒，沾醉高歌。客有難者，曰：“君何不廣耶生死一致，吾寧暫游</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>此中哉。”歲時祠禱，與閭里父老鼓舞相樂。時寇盜所過齏粉，獨不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>入谷中，知圖賢，如古王蠋也。士民依以避難。后聞哀帝遇弒，不食</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>扼腕，嘔血數升而卒，年七十有二。先撰自為文于濯纓亭一鳴窗，今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有《一鳴集》三十卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○僧虛中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    虛中，袁州人。少脫俗從佛，雖然讀書工吟不綴。居玉笥山二十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寒暑，后來游瀟湘，與齊己、顧棲蟾為詩友。住湘西宗城寺。長沙馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>侍中希振敬愛之，每其來，延納于書閣中。虛中好炙柴火，燒豆煮茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，煙熏彩翠塵暗，去必復飾，初不介意。嘗題閣中曰：“嘉魚在深處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，幽鳥立多時。”益見賞重。時司空圖懸車告老，卻掃閉門，天下懷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>仰。虛中欲造見論交，未果，因歸華山人寄詩曰：“門徑放莎垂，往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>來投刺稀。有時開御札，特地挂朝衣。岳信僧傳去，天香鶴帶歸。他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時周召化，無復更衰微。”圖得詩大喜，《言懷》云：“十年華岳山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>前往，只得虛中一首詩。”其見重如此。今有《碧云集》一卷，傳于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。顧棲蟾者，亦洞庭人，以聲律聞，今不見其作也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○周繇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    繇，江南人。咸通十三年鄭昌圖榜進士。調福昌縣尉。家貧，生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>理索寞，只苦篇韻，俯有思，仰有詠，深造閫域，時號為“詩禪”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>警聯如《送人尉黔中》云：“公庭飛白鳥，官俸請丹砂。”《望海》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“島間應有國，波外恐無天。”《甘露寺》云：“殿鎖南朝像，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>龕禪外國僧。”又“山從平地有，水到遠天無。”又“白云連晉閣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>碧樹盡蕪城。”《江州上薛能尚書》云：“樹翳樓台月，帆飛鼓角風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”又“郡齋多岳客，鄉戶半漁翁“等句甚多，讀之使人竦，誠好手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。落拓杯酒，無榮辱之累，所交游悉一時名公。集今傳世。同登第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有張演者。工詩，間見一二篇，亦佳作也。嘗謂禪家者流，論有大小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乘，有邪正法，要能具正法眼，方為第一義，出有無間。若聲聞、辟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>支、四果，已非正也，況又墮野狐外道鬼窟中乎！言詩亦然。宗派或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>殊，風義必合。品則有神妙，體則有古今，才則有聖凡，時則有取舍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。自魏晉以降，遞至盛唐，大歷、元和以下，逮晚年，考其時變，商</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其格制，其邪正了然在目，不能隱也。經云：過而不改，是謂過矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悟門洞開，慧燈深照，頓漸之境，各天所賦。觀于時以詩禪許周繇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為不入于邪見，能致思于妙品，固知其衣冠于裸人之國。昔謂學詩如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>學仙，此之類歟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔道融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    道融，荊人也，自號“東甌散人”，與司空圖為詩友。出為永嘉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宰。工絕句，語意妙甚，如《銅雀妓》云：“歌咽新翻曲，香銷舊賜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>衣。陵園風雨暗，不見六龍歸。“《春閨》云：“寒食月明雨，落花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>香滿泥。佳人持錦字，無雁寄征西”。《寄人》云：“澹澹長江水，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悠悠遠客情。落花相與恨，到地一無聲。”《寒食夜》云：“滿地梨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>花白，風吹碎月明。大家寒食夜，獨貯遠鄉情“等尚眾。誰謂晚唐間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>忽有此作，使古人復生，亦不多讓，可謂出乎其類，拔乎其萃者矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人悉推服其風情雅度，猶恨出處未能梗概之也。有《東浮集》十卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自序云：“乾寧乙卯夏，寓永嘉山齋，收拾草稿，得五百余篇，“今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>存于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○聶夷中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    夷中，字坦之，河南人也。咸通十二年禮部侍郎高湜進士，與許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棠、公乘億同袍。時兵革多務，不暇銓注，夷中滯長安久，皂裘已弊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，黃糧如珠，始得調華陰縣尉，之官惟琴書而已。性儉，蓋奮身草澤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，備嘗辛楚，率多傷俗閔時之舉，哀稼穡之艱難。適值險阻，進退維</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>谷，才足而命屯，有志卒爽，含蓄諷刺，亦有謂焉。古樂府尤得體，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>皆警省之辭，裨補政治，樂而不淫，哀而不傷，正國風之義也。其詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○許棠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    棠，字文化，宣州涇人也。苦于詩文，性僻少合。既久困名場，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時馬戴佐大同軍幕，為詞宗，棠往謁之，一見如舊交，留連累月，但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>從事詩酒而已，未嘗問所欲。一旦，大會賓客，命使以棠家書授之，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>棠驚愕不喻其來，啟緘，即知戴潛遣一介恤其家矣。古人溫良泛愛，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>振窮周急，謙退不伐，亦皆絕異之姿也。咸通十二年李筠榜進士及第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，時及知命，嘗曰：“自得一第，稍覺筋骨輕健，愈于少年，則知一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名乃孤進之還丹也。”調涇縣尉，之官，鄭谷送詩曰：“白頭新作尉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，縣在故山中。高第能卑宦，前賢尚此風。”后潦倒辭榮。初作《洞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>庭詩》，膾炙時□，號“許洞庭”，云。今集一卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○公乘億</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    億，字壽山，咸通十二年進士。善作賦，擅名場屋間，時取進者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>法之，命中。有賦集十二卷、詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○章碣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    碣，錢塘人，孝標之子也。累上著不第，咸通末以篇什稱。乾符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，高湘侍郎自長沙攜邵安古來京及第，碣恨湘不知己，賦《東都望</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>幸》詩曰：“懶修珠翠上高台，眉月連妍恨不開。縱使東巡也無益，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>君王自領美人來。”后竟流落，不知所終。碣有異才，嘗草創詩律，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于八句中，足字平側，各從本韻，如“東南路盡吳江畔，正是窮愁薄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>暮天。鷗鷺不嫌斜雨岸，波濤欺得逆風船。偶逢島寺停帆看，深羨漁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>翁下釣眠。今古若論英達算，鴟夷高興固無邊。”自稱變體。當時趨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風者亦紛紛而起也。今有詩一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○唐彥謙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    彥謙，字茂業，并州人也。咸通末舉進士及第。中和，王重榮表</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為河中從事，歷節度副使，晉、絳二州刺使。重榮遇害，彥謙貶漢中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>掾。興元節度使楊守亮留署判官，尋遷副使，為閬州刺使。卒。彥謙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>才高負氣，毫發逆意，大怒叵禁。博學足藝，尤長于詩，亦其道古心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>雄，發言不苟，極能用事，如自己出。初師溫庭筠，調度逼似，傷多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>纖麗之詞，后變淳雅，尊崇工部。唐人效甫者，惟彥謙一人而已。自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>號“鹿門先生”。有詩集，傳于世。薛廷珪序云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○林嵩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嵩，字降臣，長樂人也。乾符二年禮部侍郎崔沆下進士，官至秘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書省正字。工詩善賦，才譽與公乘億相高，功名之士，翕然而慕之，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有詩一卷，賦一卷，傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○高蟾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    蟾，河朔間人。乾符三年孔緘榜及第。與鄭郎中谷為友，酬贈稱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“高先輩”。初累舉不上，題省牆間曰：“冰柱數條搘白日，天門几</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>扇鎖明時。陽春發處無根蒂，憑仗東風次第吹。”怨而切。是年人論</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不公，又下第。《上馬侍郎》云：“天上碧桃和露種，日邊紅杏倚云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>栽。芙蓉生在秋江上，莫向春風怨未開。”意亦指直馬憐之。又有“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>顏色如花命如葉“之句，自況時運蹇窒，馬因力荐，明年，李昭知貢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，遂擢挂。官至御史中丞。蟾本寒士，遑遑于一名，十年始就。性倜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>儻離群，稍尚氣節。人與千金無故，即身死亦不受。其胸次磊塊詩酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能為消破耳。詩體則氣勢雄偉，態度諧遠，如狂風猛雨之來，物物竦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>動，深造理窟，亦一奇逢掖也。詩集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○高駢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    駢，字千里，幽州人也。崇文之孫。少閑鞍馬弓發，善射，有膂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>力。更剉銳為文學，與諸儒交，硜硜談治道。初事朱叔明為府司馬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>遷侍御史。一日校獵圍合，有雙雕并飛，駢曰：“我后大富貴，當貫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之。”遂一發聯翩而墜，眾大驚，號“落雕御史”。駢為西川節度，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>筑成都城四十里，朝廷疑之。以宴間詠風箏云：“依稀似曲才堪聽，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>又被風吹別調中。”明日詔下，移鎮渚宮，亦讖之類也。仕至平章事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，封渤海郡王。初駢以戰討之勛，累拜節度，手握王爵，口含天憲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>國家倚之。時巢賊日日甚，兩京亦陷，大駕蒙塵，遂無勤王之意，包</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>藏禍心，欲便徼幸。帝知之，以王鐸代為都統，加侍中。駢失兵柄，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>攘袂大詬，一旦離勢，威望頓盡，方且棄人間事，絕女色，屬意神仙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。鄱陽離儈呂用之會妖術，役鬼神，及狂人諸葛殷、張守一等相引而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>進，多為謬悠長年飛化之說，羽衣鶴氅，詭辯風生，駢事之若神。造</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>迎仙樓，高八十尺，日同方士登眺，計鸞笙在云表而下，用之等叱吒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>風雷，或望空揖拜，言睹仙過，駢輒隨之。用之曰：“玉皇欲補公真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>官，吾謫限亦滿，必當陪幢節同歸上清耳。”其造怪不可勝紀。至以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>用之、守一、殷等為將，分掌兵將，皆稱將軍，開府置官屬，禮與駢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>均。卒至叛逆首亂，磔尸道途，死且不悟。裹駢以破氈，與子弟七人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，一坎而瘞，名書于唐史叛臣傳，亦何足道矣。有詩一卷，今傳。大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>順中，謝蟠隱為之序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○牛嶠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    嶠，字延峰，隴西人，宰相僧孺之后。博學有文，以歌詩著名。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乾符五年孫偓榜第四人進士，仕歷拾遺、補闕一尚書郎。王建鎮西川</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，辟為判官。及偽蜀開國，拜給事中。卒。有集，本三十卷，自序云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“竊慕李長吉所為歌詩，輒效之。”今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○錢珝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    珝，吳興人，起之孫也。乾符六年鄭藹榜及第。昭宗時，仕為中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>書舍人。工詩，有集傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○趙光遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    光遠，丞相隱之猶子也。幼而聰悟。咸能、乾符中稱氣焰。善為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩。溫庭筠、李商隱輩梯媒之。恃才不拘小節，皆金鞍駿馬。嘗將子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>弟恣游狹邪，著《北里志》，頗述青樓紅粉之事，及有詩等傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>光遠等千金之子，厭飫膏粱，仰蔭承榮，視若談笑，驕侈不期而至矣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。況年少多才，京邑繁盛，耳目所蕩，素少閑邪之慮者哉。故辭意多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>裙裾妖艷之態，無足怪矣。有孫啟、崔玨同時恣心狂狎，相為唱和，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>頗陷輕薄，無退讓之風。惟盧弼氣象稍嚴，不遷狐惑，如《邊庭四時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>怨》等作，賞音大播，信不偶然。區區涼德，徒曰貴介，不暇錄尚多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○周朴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    朴，字見素，長樂人，嵩山隱君也。工為詩，抒思尤艱。每有所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>得，必極雕琢。時詩家稱為月鍛年煉，未及成篇，已播人口，取重當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時如此。貫休尤與往還，深為憐才。而朴本無奪名競利之心，特以道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>尊德貴，美價益超耳。乾符中，為巢賊所得，以不屈，竟及于禍，遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>近聞之，莫不流涕。林嵩得其詩百余篇為二卷，僧棲浩序首，今傳于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。周朴山林之瞿，槁衣糲食，以為黔婁、原憲不殄天物，庶足保身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>而長年。今則血染縕袍，魂散茅宇，盜跖不仁，竟嚼虎口，天道福善</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>禍淫，果何如哉！古稱飾變詐為奸軌者，自足乎一世之間；守道循理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者，不免于飢寒之患，殺戮無辜，亂世之道。每讀至止，未嘗不廢書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>撫髀欷歔也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○羅隱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    隱，字昭諫，錢塘人也。少英敏，善屬文，詩筆尤俊拔，養浩然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之氣。乾符初舉進士，累不第。廣明中，遇亂歸鄉里，時錢尚父鎮東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>南，節鉞崇重，隱欲依焉。進謁，投素作，卷首《過夏口》云：“一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>個檷衡容不得，思量黃祖謾英雄。”鏐得之大喜遇，以書辟曰：“仲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宣遠托劉荊州，蓋因亂世；夫子樂為魯司寇，祇為故鄉。”隱曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>是不可去矣。”遂為掌書記。性簡傲，高談闊論，滿座風生。好諧謔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，感遇輒發。鏐愛其才，前后賜予無數，陪從不頃刻相背。表遷節度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>判官、鹽鐵發運使。未几，奏授著作郎。鏐初授鎮，命沈崧草表謝，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>盛言浙西富庶。隱曰：“今浙西焚蕩之余，朝臣方切賄賂，表奏，將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鷹犬我矣。”鏐請隱為之，有云：“天寒而麋鹿曾游，日暮而牛羊不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下。“又為賀昭宗改名表云：“左則姬昌之半字，右為虞舜之全文。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”作者稱賞。轉司勛郎中。自號“江東生”。魏博節度羅紹威慕其名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，推宗人之分，拜為叔父，時亦老矣，嘗表荐之。隱恃才忽睨，眾頗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>憎忌。自以當得大用，而一第落落，傳食諸侯，因人成事，深怨唐室</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。詩文凡以譏刺為主，雖荒祠木偶，莫能免者。且介僻寡合，不喜軍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>旅。獻酬俎豆間，綽綽有余也。隱初貧來赴舉，過鐘陵，見營妓云英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有才思。后一紀，下第過之。英曰：“羅秀才尚未脫白“隱贈詩云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“鐘陵醉別十余春，重見云英掌上身。我未成名英未嫁，可能俱是不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>如人。”與顧云同謁淮南高駢，駢不禮。駢后為畢將軍所殺，隱有延</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>和閣之譏。又以詩投相國鄭畋，畋有女殊麗，喜詩詠，讀隱作至“張</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>華謾出如丹語，不及劉侯一紙書”。由是切慕之。精爽飛越，莫知所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>從。隱忽來謁，女從帘后窺見迂寢之狀，不復念矣。隱精法書，喜筆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工萇鳳，謂曰：“筆，文章貨也。今助子取高價。”即以雁頭箋百幅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為贈，士大夫踵門問價，一致千金。率多借重如此。所著《讒書》《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>讒本》、《淮海寓言》、《湘南應用集》、《甲乙集》、《外集》、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《啟事》等，并行于世。《易》戒毋以小善為無益而弗為，小惡為無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傷而弗去也。羅隱以褊急性成，動必嘲訕，率成謾作，頃刻相傳。以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其事業非不五鼎也，學術非不經史也，夫何齊東野人，猥巷小子，語</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及譏誚，必以隱為稱首。凋喪淳才，揄揚穢德，白日能蔽于浮翳，美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>玉曾玷于青蠅，雖亦未必盡然，是皆闕慎微之豫。阮嗣宗臧否不挂口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，欲免其身。如滑稽玩世東方朔之流，又不相類也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○羅虯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    虯，詞藻富贍，與族人隱、鄴齊名，咸通間稱“三羅”，氣宇終</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不逮。廣明庚子亂后，去從鄜州李孝恭為從事，虯狂宕無檢束，時雕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>陰籍中有妓杜紅兒，善歌舞，姿色殊絕，嘗為副戎屬意。會副戎聘鄰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>道，虯久慕之，至是請紅兒歌，贈以繒彩。孝恭以為副戎所貯，從事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>則非禮，勿令受貺，虯不稱意，怒，拂衣起，詰旦，手刃殺之。孝恭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以虯激己坐之，頃會赦。虯追其冤，于是取古之美女有姿艷才德者，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作絕句一百首，以比紅兒，當時盛傳，此外不見有他作。體固凡庸，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>無大可采。《序》曰：“紅兒美貌年少，機智慧悟，不與群妓等。余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>知紅者，擇古灼然美色，優劣于章句間。”其卒章云：“花落塵中玉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>墮泥，香魂應上窈娘堤。欲知此恨無窮處，長倩城烏夜夜啼。”情極</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>哀切。初以白刃相加，今曰“余知紅者”，虯實一狂夫也。且拘律之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>道大爽，姑錄為笑談耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔魯或作櫓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    魯，廣時間舉進士。工為雜文，才麗而蕩。詩慕杜紫微風范，警</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>句絕多。如《梅花》云：“強半瘦因前夜雪，數枝愁向晚來天。”又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“初開已入雕梁畫，未落先愁玉笛吹。”《蓮花》云：“何人解把無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>塵袖，盛取清香盡日憐。”《山鵲》云：“一番春雨吹巢冷，半朵山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>花咽嘴香。”又《別題》云：“云生柱礎降龍地，露洗林巒放鶴天“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>等，皆綺制精深，膾炙人口。頗嗜酒，無德，嘗醉辱陸肱郎中，旦日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>慚甚，為詩謝曰：“醉時顛蹶醒時羞，□薛催人不自由。叵耐一雙窮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>相眼，不堪花卉在前頭。”陸亦諒之。悠悠亂世，竟無所成。魯詩善</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>于狀景詠物，讀之如咽冰雪，心爽神怡，能遠聲病，氣象清楚，格調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>且高，中間別有一種風情，佳作也。詩三百余篇，名《無機集》，今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○秦韜玉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    韜玉，字中明，京兆人。父為左軍軍將。韜玉少有詞藻，工歌吟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，恬和瀏亮。慕柏耆為人，然險而好進，諂事大閹田令孜，巧宦，未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>期年，官至丞郎、判鹽鐵、保大軍節度判官。僖宗幸蜀，從駕。中和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>二年，禮部侍郎歸仁紹放榜，特敕賜進士及第，令于二十四人內安排</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，編入春榜，令孜引擢工部侍郎。韜玉歌詩，每作人必傳誦。《貴公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子行》云：“階前莎毯綠未卷，銀龜噴香挽不斷。亂花織錦柳捻線，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>妝點池台畫屏展。主人功業傳國初，六親聯絡馳朝車。斗雞走狗家世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事，抱來皆佩黃金魚。卻笑書生把書卷，學得顏回忍飢面。”又瀟水</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出道州九疑山中，湘水出桂林海陽山中，經靈渠，至零陵與瀟水合，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>謂之“瀟湘”，為永州二水也。清泚一色，高秋八九月，才丈余，淺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>碧見底。過衡陽，抵長沙，入洞庭。韜玉賦詩云：“女媧羅裙長百尺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，搭在湘江作山色。”又云：“嵐光楚岫和空碧，秋染湘江到底清。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”由是大知名，號為絕唱。今有《投知小錄》三卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鄭谷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    谷，字守愚，袁州宜春人。父史，開成中為永州刺史。谷幼穎悟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>絕倫，七歲能詩。司空侍郎圖與史同院，見而奇之，問曰：“予詩有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>病否“曰：“大夫《曲江晚望》云：‘村南斜日閑回首，一對鴛鴦落</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>渡頭。’此意深矣。”圖拊谷背曰：“當為一代風騷主也。”光啟三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>年，右丞柳玼下第進士，授京兆鄠縣尉，遷右拾遺、補闕。乾寧四年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，為都官郎中，詩家稱“鄭都官”。又嘗賦《鷓鴣》警絕，復稱“鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鷓鴣“云。未几，告歸，退隱仰山書堂，卒于北岩別墅。谷詩清婉明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>白，不俚而切，為薛能、李頻所賞，與許棠、任濤、張蠙、李棲遠、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>張喬、喻坦之、周繇、溫憲、李昌符唱答往還，號“芳林十哲”。谷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多結契山僧，曰：“蜀茶似僧，未必皆美，不能舍之。”齊已攜詩卷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>來袁謁谷，《早梅》云：“前村深雪里，昨夜數枝開。”谷曰：“數</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>枝非早也，未若一枝佳。”已不覺投拜，曰：“我一字師也。”嘗從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僖宗登三峰，朝謁之暇，寓于云台道舍，編所作為《云台編》三卷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歸編《宜陽集》三卷。及撰《國風正訣》一卷，分六門，摭詩聯，注</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>其比為君臣賢否、國家治亂之意。今并傳焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○齊己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    齊己，長沙人。姓胡氏，早失怙恃。七歲穎悟，為大溈山寺司牧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，往往抒思，取竹枝畫牛背為小詩。耆夙異之，遂共推挽入戒。風度</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>日改，聲價益隆。游江海名山，登岳陽，望洞庭，時秋高水落，君山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>如黛，唯湘川一條而已。欲吟杳不可得，徘徊久之。來長安數載，遍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>覽終南、條、華之勝。歸過豫章，時陳陶近仙去，已留題有云：“夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>過修竹寺，醉打老僧門。”至宜春，投詩鄭都官云：“自封修藥院，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>別下著僧床。”谷曰：“善則善矣，一字未安。”經數日，來曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>別掃如何“谷嘉賞，結為詩友。曹松、方干皆己良契。性放逸，不滯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>土木形骸，頗任琴樽之好。嘗撰《玄機分別要覽》一卷，摭古人詩聯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，以類分次，仍別諷、賦、比、興、雅、頌。又撰《詩格》一卷。又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>與鄭谷、黃損等共定用韻為葫蘆、轆轤、進退等格，并其詩《白蓮集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》十卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○崔涂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    涂，字禮山，光啟四年鄭貽矩榜進士及第。工詩，深造理窟，端</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>能竦動人意，寫景狀懷，往往宣陶肺腑。亦窮年羈旅，壯歲上巴蜀，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>老大游隴山。家寄江南，每多離怨之作。警策如“流年川暗度，往事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月空明。”《巫娥》云：“江山非舊主，云雨是前身。”如：“病知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>新事少，老別故交難。”《孤雁》云：“渚云低暗度，關月冷相隨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”《山寺》云：“夕陽高鳥過，疏雨一鐘殘。”又：“谷樹云埋老，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>僧窗瀑照寒。”《鸚鵡州》云：“曹瞞尚不能容物，黃祖何因解愛才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”《春夕》云：“胡蝶夢中家萬里，杜鵑枝上月三更。”《隴上》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云：“三聲戍角邊城暮，萬里鄉心塞草春。”《過峽》云：“五千里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外三年客，十二峰前一望秋“等聯，作者于此斂衽。意味俱遠，大名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不虛。有詩一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○喻坦之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    坦之，睦州人。咸通中舉進士不第，久寓長安，囊罄，憶漁樵，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>還居舊山。與李建州頻為友。頻以詩送歸云：“從容心自切，飲水勝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>銜杯。共在山中住，相隨闕下來。修身空有道，取事各無媒。不信升</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>平代，終遺草澤才。”又“彼此無依倚，東西又別離。”蓋困于窮蹇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，情見于辭矣。同時嚴維、徐凝、章八元，枌榆相望，前后唱和亦多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。詩集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○任濤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    濤，筠川人也。章句之名早擅。乾符中，應數舉，每敗垂成。李</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>常侍騭廉察江西，素聞濤名，取其詩覽之，見云：“露摶沙鶴起，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>臥釣船流。”大加賞嘆曰：“任濤奇才也，何故不成名會當荐之。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>特與放鄉里雜役，仍令本貫優禮。時盲俗互有論列，騭判曰：“江西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>境內，凡為詩得及濤者，即與放役，豈止一任濤而已哉。”未几，濤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>逝云，有才無命，大可憐也。詩集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○溫憲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    憲，庭筠之子也。龍紀元年李瀚榜進士及第，去為山南節度府從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事。大著詩名。詞人李巨川草荐表，盛述憲先人之屈，辭略曰：“蛾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>眉先妒，明妃為去國之人；猿臂自傷，李廣乃不侯之將。”上讀表惻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>然稱美，時宰相亦有知者，曰：“父以竄死，今孽子宜稍振之，以厭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>公議，庶几少雪忌才之恨。”上頷之。后遷至郎中，卒。有集文賦等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李洞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    洞，字才江，雍州人，諸王之孫也。家貧，吟極苦，至廢寢食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>酷慕賈長江，遂銅寫島像，戴之巾中。常持數珠念賈島佛，一日千遍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。人有喜島詩者，洞必手錄島詩贈之，叮嚀再四，曰：“此無異佛經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，歸焚香拜之。”其仰慕一何如此之切也。然洞詩逼真于島，新奇或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>過之。時人多誚僻澀，不貴其卓峭，唯吳融賞異。融以大才，八面受</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敵，新律著稱，游刃頗攻騷雅。嘗以百篇示洞，洞曰：“大兄所示中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一聯‘暖漾魚遺子，晴游鹿引麑。’絕妙也。”融不怨所鄙，而善其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>許。洞詩大略，如《終南山》云：“殘陽高照蜀，敗葉遠浮涇，屬竹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>煙嵐凍，偷湫雨雹腥。”“遠平丹鳳闕，冷射五侯廳。”《贈司空圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“馬飢餐落葉，鶴病晒殘陽。”又曰：“卷箔清溪月，敲松紫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閣書。”《送僧》云：“越講迎騎象，蕃齋懺射雕。”《歸日本》云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“島嶼分諸國，星河共一天。”《夜》云：“藥杵聲中搗殘夢，茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鐺影里煮孤燈。”皆偉拔時流者。昭宗時，凡三上，不第。裴公第二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>榜，帘前獻詩云：“公道此時如不得，昭陵慟器一生休。”果失意，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>流落往來，寓蜀而卒。初，島任長江，乃東蜀，塚在其處，鄭谷哭洞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩云：“得近長江死，想君勝在生。”言死生不相遠也。洞嘗集島警</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>句五十聯，及唐諸人警句五十聯為《詩句圖》，自為之序。及所為詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一卷，并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○吳融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    融，字子華，山陰人。初力學，富辭，調工捷。龍紀元年李瀚榜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及進士第。韋昭度討蜀，表掌書記。坐累去官，流浪荊南，依成汭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>久之，召為左補闕，以禮部郎中為翰林學士，拜中書舍人。天復元年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>元旦，東內反正，既御樓，融最先至，上命于前座跪草十數詔，簡備</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>精當，曾不頃刻，皆中旨，大加賞激，進戶部侍郎。帝幸鳳翔，融不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>及從，去客閿鄉，俄召為翰林承旨，卒。為詩靡麗有余，而雅重不足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。集四卷及制誥一卷，并行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○韓偓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    偓，字致堯，京兆人。龍紀元年禮部侍郎趙崇下擢第。天復中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>王溥荐為翰林學士，遷中書舍人。從昭宗幸鳳翔，進兵部侍郎、翰林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>承旨。嘗與崔胤定策誅劉季述。昭宗反正，論為功臣。帝疾宦人驕橫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，欲去之。偓畫策稱旨，帝前膝曰：“此一事終始以屬卿。”偓因荐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>座主御史大夫趙崇，時稱能讓。李彥弼倨甚，因譖偓漏禁省語，帝怒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>曰：“卿有官屬，日夕議事，奈何不欲我見韓學士耶“帝勵精政事，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>偓處可機密，卒與上意合。欲相者三四，讓不敢當。偓喜侵侮有位，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朱全忠亦惡之，乃構禍貶濮州司馬。帝流涕曰：“我左右無人矣！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天祐二年，復召為學士，偓不敢入朝，挈其族南依王審知而卒。偓自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>號“玉山樵人”。工詩，有集一卷。又作《香奩集》一卷，詞多側艷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>新巧，又作《金鑾密記》五卷，今并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○唐備</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    備，龍紀元年進士。工古詩，多極諷剌，頗干教化，非浮艷輕斐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之作。同時于瀆者，共一機軸，大為時流所許。備詩有“天若無雪霜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，青松不如草；地若無山川，何人重平道“又曰：“狂風拔倒樹，樹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>倒根已露，上有數枝藤，青青猶未悟。”又：“一日天無風，四溟波</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>自息。人心風不吹，波浪高百尺。”又《別家》云：“兄弟惜分離，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>揀日皆言惡。”于瀆《對花》云：“花開蝶滿枝，花謝蝶來稀，惟有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>舊巢燕，主人貧亦舊“等詩，發為澆俗，至今人話間，必舉以為警戒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，足見之矣。余詩多傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王駕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    駕，字大用，蒲中人，自號“守素先生”。大順元年楊贊禹榜登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第，授校書郎，仕至禮部員外郎。棄官嘉遁于別業，與鄭谷、司空圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為詩友，才名藉甚。圖嘗與駕書評詩曰：“國初雅風特盛，沈、宋始</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>興之后，杰出江寧，宏思至李、杜極矣。右丞、蘇州，趣味澄敻，若</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>清流之貫遠。大歷十數公，抑又其次。元、白力勍而氣孱，乃都市豪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>估耳。。劉夢得、楊巨源亦各有勝會。浪仙、無可、劉得仁輩，時得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>佳致，亦足滌煩。厥后所聞，徒褊淺矣。河汾蟠郁之氣，宜繼有人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>今王生者寓居其間，沉漬益久，五言所得，長于思與境偕，乃詩家之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>所尚者。則前所謂必推于其類，豈若神躍色揚而已哉。”駕得書，自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以譽不虛己。當時價重，乃如此也。今集六卷，行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○戴思顏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    思顏，大順元年楊贊禹榜進士及第，與王駕同袍。有詩名，氣宇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>盤礡，每有過人，遂得名家，豈泛然矣。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○杜荀鶴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    荀鶴，字彥之，牧之微子也。牧會昌末，自齊安移守秋浦時，妾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有妊，出嫁長林鄉正杜筠，生荀鶴。早得詩名，嘗謁梁王朱會忠，與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之坐，忽無云而雨，王以為天泣不祥，命作詩，稱意，王喜之。荀鶴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寒畯，連敗文場，甚苦，至是遣送名春官。大順二年裴贄侍郎下第八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人登科。正月十日放榜，正荀鶴生朝也。王希羽獻詩曰：“金榜曉懸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生世日，玉書潛記上升時。九華山色高千尺，未必高于第八枝。”荀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鶴居九華，號“九華山人”。張曙拾遺亦工詩，又同年，嘗醉謔曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“杜十五大榮，而得與曙同年。”荀鶴曰：“是公榮。天下只知有荀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鶴，若個知有張五十郎耶“各大笑而罷。宣州田頵甚重之，常致箋問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。梁王立，荐為翰林學士，遷主客員外郎。頗恃勢悔慢縉紳，為文多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>主箴刺，眾怒欲殺之，未得。天祐元年卒。荀鶴苦吟，平生所志不遂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，晚始成名，況丁亂世，殊多懮惋思慮之語，于一觴一詠，變俗為雅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，極事物之情，足丘壑之趣，非易能及者也。與太常博士顧云初隱一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山，登第之明年，寧親相會，云撰集其詩三百余篇，為《唐風集》三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，且序以為：“壯語大言，則決起逸發，可以左攬工部袂，右拍翰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>林肩，吞賈、喻八九于胸中，曾不芥蒂。或情發乎中，則極思冥搜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>神游希夷，形兀枯木，五聲勞于呼吸，萬象貧于抉剔，信詩家之雄杰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者矣。“荀鶴嗜酒，善彈琴，風情雅度，千載猶可想望也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    卷十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王煥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    煥，大順二年禮部侍郎裴贄下進士及第。俄自左史拜考功員外郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，同年皆得美除，煥首唱感恩長句，上謝座主裴公，當時甚榮之。后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以禮部侍郎致仕，年九十，見《睢陽五老圖》。煥工詩，情極婉麗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>嘗為《惆悵詩》十三首，悉古佳人才子深懷感怨者，以崔氏鶯鶯、漢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>武李夫人、陳樂昌主、綠珠、張麗華、王昭君，及蘇武、劉、阮輩事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>成篇，哀傷媚嫵，如“謝家池館花籠月，蕭寺房廊竹颭風。夜半酒醒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>憑檻立，所思多在別離中。”又“夢里分明入漢宮，覺來燈背錦屏空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。紫台月落關山曉，腸斷君王信畫工“等，皆絕唱，喧炙士林。在晚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>唐諸人中，霄壤不侔矣。有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○徐寅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    寅，莆田人也。大順三年蔣詠下進士及第。工詩，嘗賦《路傍草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“楚甸秦川萬里平，誰教根向路傍生。輕蹄繡轂長相蹋，合是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>榮時不得榮。”時人知其蹭蹬，后果須鬢交白，始得秘書省正字，竟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>蓬轉客途，不知所終云。有《探龍集》五卷，謂登科射策，如探睡龍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之珠也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張喬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    喬，隱居九華山，池州人也。有高致，十年不窺園以苦學。詩句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>清雅，迥少其倫。當時東南多才子，如許棠、喻坦之、劇燕、吳罕、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>任濤、周繇、張蠙、鄭谷、李棲遠與喬，亦稱“十哲”，俱以韻律馳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>聲。大順中，京兆府解試，李參軍頻時主文，試《月中桂》詩，喬云</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“根非生下土，葉不墜秋風。”遂擅場。其年頻以許棠久困場屋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以為首荐。喬與喻坦之復受許下薛尚書之，欲表于朝，以他不果。竟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>岨峿名途，徒得一進耳。有詩集二卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○鄭良士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    良士，字君夢。咸通中累舉進士不第。昭宗時，自表獻詩五百余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>篇，敕授補闕而終。以布衣一旦俯拾青紫，易若反掌，浮俗莫不駭羨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，難其比也。今有《白岩集》十卷傳世。舊言詩，或窮人，或達人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>達者，良士是矣。亦命之所為，詩何能與過詩則不揣其本也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張鼎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    鼎，字台業，景福二年崔膠榜進士。工詩，集一卷，今行。同時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>趙摶，有爽邁之度，工歌詩。韋靄，亦進而無遇，退而有守者。詩各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一卷。及謝蟠隱，云是靈運之遠孫，有清才，知天下之將亂，作《雜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>感詩》一卷。張為，閩中人，離群拔類，工詩，存一卷，及著《唐詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>主客圖》等，并傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○韋莊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    莊，字瑞己，京兆杜陵人也。少孤貧，力學，才敏過人。莊應舉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時，正黃巢犯闕，兵火交作，遂著《秦婦吟》，有云：“內庫燒為錦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>繡灰，天街蹈盡卻重回。”亂定，公卿多訝之，號為“奏婦吟秀才。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”乾寧元年蘇檢榜進士。釋褐校書郎。李詢宣諭西川，舉莊為判官。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>后王建辟為掌書記。尋征起居郎，建表留之。及建開偽蜀，莊托在腹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>心，首預謀畫，其郊廟之禮，冊書赦令，皆出莊手。以功臣授吏部侍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎同平章事。莊早嘗寇亂，間關頓躓，攜家來越中，弟妹散居諸郡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>西江、湖南，所在曾游，舉目有山河之異，故于流離漂泛，寓目緣情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，子期懷舊之辭，王粲傷時之制，或離群軫虎，或反袂興悲，四愁九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>怨之文，一詠一觴之作，俱能感動人也。莊自來成都，尋得杜少陵所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>居浣花溪故址，雖蕪沒已久，而柱砥猶存，遂誅茅重作草堂而居焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>性儉，秤薪而爨，數米而飲，達人鄙之。弟藹，撰莊詩為《浣花集》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>六卷，及莊嘗選杜甫、王維等五十二人詩為《又玄集》，以續姚合之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《極玄》，今并傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○王貞白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    貞白，字有道，信州永丰人也。乾寧二年登第。時榜下物議紛紛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，詔翰林學士陸扆于內殿覆試，中選，授校書郎，時登科后七年矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭谷以詩贈曰：“殿前新進士，闕下校書郎”。初，蘭溪僧貫休雅得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名，與貞白居去不遠而未會，嘗寄《御溝詩》，有云：“此波涵帝澤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，無處濯塵纓。”后會，語及此，休曰：“剩一字”。貞白拂袂而去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。休曰：“此公思敏，當即來。”休書字于掌心，逡巡，貞白還曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“‘此中涵帝澤’如何？”休以掌示之，無異所改，遂訂深契。后值</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>天王狩于岐，乃退居著書，不復干祿，當時大獲芳譽。性恬和，明《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>易•象》。手編所為詩三百篇及賦、文等，為《靈溪集》七卷，傳于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。卒葬家山。貞白學力精贍，篤志于詩，清潤典雅，呼吸間兩獲科</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>甲，自致于青云之上，文價可知矣。深惟存亡取舍之義，進而就祿，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>退而保身，君子也。梁陶宏景棄官隱居三茅，國事必咨請，稱“山中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>宰相，號貞白。今王公慕其為人而云爾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○張蠙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    蠙，字象文，清河人也。乾寧二年，趙觀文榜進士及第。釋褐為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>校書郎，調櫟陽尉，遷犀浦令。偽蜀王建開國，拜膳部員外郎，后為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>金堂令。王衍與徐后游大慈寺，見壁間題：“牆頭細雨垂纖草，水面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>回風聚落花。”愛賞久之，問誰作，左右以蠙對，因給箋，令以詩進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，蠙上二百篇，衍尤待重，將召掌制誥，宋光嗣以其輕傲駙馬宜疏之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，止賜白金千兩而已。蠙生而秀穎，幼能為詩，《登單于台》有“白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>日地中出，黃河天上來“句，由是知名。初以家貧累下第，留滯長安</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，賦詩云：“月里路從何處上，江邊身合几時歸十年九陌寒風夜，夢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>掃蘆花絮客衣。”主司知為非濫成名。余詩皆佳，各有意度，過人遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>矣。詩集二卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○翁承贊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    承贊，字文堯，乾寧三年禮部侍郎獨孤損下第四人進士，又中宏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詞敕頭。承贊工詩，體貌甚偉，且詼諧，名動公侯。唐人應試，每在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>八月，諺曰：“槐花黃，舉士忙。“承贊《詠槐花》云：“雨中妝點</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>望中黃，勾引蟬聲送夕陽。憶得當年隨計吏，馬蹄終日為君忙。”甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>為當時傳誦。嘗奉使來福州，見友僧亞齊，贈詩云：“蕭蕭風雨建陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>溪，溪畔維舟見亞齊。一軸新詩劍潭北，十年舊識華山西。吟魂昔向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>江村老，空性元知世路迷。應笑乘軺青瑣客，此時無暇聽猿啼。”他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩高妙稱是。仕王審知，終諫議大夫。有詩，以兵火散失，尚存百二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>十余篇，為一卷，秘書郎孫郃為序云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○王轂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    轂，字虛中，宜春人，自號臨沂子。以歌詩擅名，長于樂府。未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>第時嘗為《玉樹曲》云：“璧月夜，瓊樹春，鶯舌泠泠詞調新。當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>狎客盡丰祿，直諫犯顏無一人。歌未闋，晉王劍上粘腥血。君臣猶在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>醉鄉中，一面已無陳日月”。大播人口，適有同人為無賴輩毆，轂前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>救之，曰：“莫無禮！我便是道‘君臣猶在醉鄉中’者。”無賴聞之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，慚謝而退。轂亦大節士，輕財重義，以鄉里所譽。頗不平久困，適</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>生離難間，辭多寄寓比興之作，無不知名。乾寧五年羊紹素榜進士，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>歷國子博士，后以郎官致仕。有詩三卷。于是宦達，俱素餐尸位，賣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>降恐后之徒，轂因撰前代忠臣臨老不變圖一卷，及《觀光集》一卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>并傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○殷文圭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    文圭，字表儒，池州青陽人也。乾寧五年禮部侍郎裴贄下進士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>初未第時，道中嘗逢一老叟，目文圭久之，謂人曰：“向者布衣，綠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>眉方口，神仙中人也。如學道，可以沖虛；不爾，垂大名于天下。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>未几，兵馬振動，大駕幸三峰，文圭攜梁王表荐及第。時楊令公行密</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>鎮淮陽，奄有宣、浙、揚、汴之間。榛梗既久，文圭辭親，間道至行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>在。無何，隨榜為吏部侍郎裴樞宣慰判官、記室參軍。至大梁，以身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>事叩梁王，王又上表荐之。文圭后飾非，遍投啟事公卿間，曰：“于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>菟獵食，非求尸璧之珍；爰居避風，不望洪鐘之樂。”俄為多言者所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>發，更由宋、汴馳過，梁王大怒，亟遣追捕，已不及矣。為詩有《登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>龍集》、《冥搜集》、《筆耕詞》、《冰鏤錄》、《從軍稿》等集，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳世。唐季，文體澆離，才調荒穢，稍稍作者，強名曰詩，南郭之竽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，苟存于從響，非復盛時之萬一也。如王周、劉兼、司馬札、蘇拯、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>許琳、李咸用等數人，雖有集相傳，皆氣卑格下，負魚目唐突之慚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>竊碔砆韞襲之濫，所謂家有弊帚，享之千金，不自見之患也。文圭稍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>入風度，間見奇崛，其殆庶几乎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○李建勛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    建勛，字致堯，廣陵人，仕南唐為宰相，后罷，出鎮臨川。未几</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，以司徒致仕，賜號“鐘山公”，年已八十，志尚散逸，多從仙侶參</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>究玄門。時宋齊丘有道氣，在洪州西山，建勛造謁致敬，欲授真果，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>題詩贈云：“春來漲水涼如活，曉出西山勢似行。玉洞有人經劫在，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>攜竿步步就長生。”歸高安別墅，一夕無病而逝。能文賦詩，琢煉頗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>工，調既平妥，終少驚人之句也。有《鐘山集》二十卷行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○褚載</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    載，字厚子，家貧，客梁、宋間，困甚，以詩投襄陽節度使邢君</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>牙云：“西風昨夜墜紅蘭，一宿郵亭事萬般。無地可耕歸不得，有思</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>堪報死何難。流年怕老看將老，百計求安未得安。一卷新詩滿懷淚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>頻來門館訴飢寒。”君牙憐之，贈絹十匹，荐于鄭滑節度使，不行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>乾寧五年，禮部侍郎裴贄知貢舉，君牙之荐之，遂擢第。文德中，劉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>子長出鎮浙西，行次江西，時陸威侍郎猶為郎吏，亦寓于此。載緘二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>軸投謁，誤以子長之卷畫贄于威，威覽之，連見數字觸家諱，威矍然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，載錯愕，白以大誤。尋謝以長箋，略曰：“曹興之圖畫雖精，終慚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>誤筆；殷浩之兢持太過，翻達空函。”威激賞而終不能引拔，后竟流</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>落而卒。集三卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○呂岩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    岩，字洞賓，京兆人，禮部侍郎呂渭之孫也。咸通初中第，兩調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>縣令。更值巢賊，浩然發棲隱之志，攜家歸終南，自放跡江湖。先是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有鐘離權，字云房，不知何代何許人，以喪亂避地太白，間入此閣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>石壁上得金誥玉菉，深造希夷之旨。常髽髻，衣槲葉，隱見于世。岩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>既篤志大道，游覽名山，至太華，遇云房，知為異人，拜以詩曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>先生去后應須老，乞與貧儒換骨丹。”云房許以法器，因為著《靈寶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>畢法十二科》，悉究性命之旨。坐廬山中數十年，金丹始就。逢苦竹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>真人，乃能驅役神鬼。時移世換，不復返也。與陳圖南音響相接，或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>訪其室中。嘗白襴角帶，賣墨于市，得者皆成黃金。往往遨游洞庭、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>瀟湘、湓浦間，自稱“回道士”，時傳已蟬蛻矣。有術佩劍，自笑曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>：“吾仙人，安用劍為所以斷嗔愛煩惱耳。“嘗題寺壁曰：“三千里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外無家客，七百年前云水身。”后書云：“唐室進士，今時神仙。足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>躡紫霧，卻歸洞天。”又宿湖州沈東老家，白酒滿瓮，瓷意拍浮，臨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去，以石榴皮畫壁間云：“西鄰已富懮不足，東老雖貧樂有余。白酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>釀來因好客，黃金散盡為收書。”又嘗負局奩于布，為賈尚書淬古鏡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，歸忽不見，留詩云：“袖里青蛇凌白日，洞中仙果艷長春。須知物</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>外餐霞客，不是塵中磨鏡人。”又醉飲岳陽樓，俯鑒洞庭，時八月，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>葉下水清，君山如黛螺，秋風浩蕩，遂按玉龍作一弄，清音遼亮，金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>石可裂。久之，度古柳別去，留詩云：“朝游南浦暮蒼梧，袖里青蛇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>膽氣粗。三入岳陽人不識，朗吟飛過洞庭湖。”后往來人間，乘虛上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下，竟莫能測。至今四百余年，所在留題，不可勝紀。凡遇之者，每</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去后始覺，悔無及矣。蓋其變化無窮，吟詠不已，姑此紀其大概云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    論曰：“晉嵇康論神仙非積學所能致，斯言信哉。原其本自天靈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，有異凡品，仙風道骨，迥凌云表。歷觀傳記所載，霧隱乎岩巔，霞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寓于塵外，崆峒、羨門以下，清流相望，由來尚矣。雖解化一事，似</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>或玄微，正非假房中黃白之小端，從而服食頤養，能盡其道者也。不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>損上藥，愈益下田，熊經鳥伸，納新吐敵，無七情以奪魂魄，無百慮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以煎肺肝，庶几指識玄戶，引身長年，然后一躍，頓喬、松之逸馭也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。今夫指青山首駕，臥白云振衣，紛長往于斯世，遣高風于無窮，及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>見其人，吾亦願從之游耳。韓湘控鶴于前，呂岩驂鸞于后，凡其題詠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>篇什，鏗鏘振作，皆天成云漢，不假安排，自非咀嚼冰玉，呼吸煙霏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，孰能至此。寧好事者為之。多見其不知量也。吳筠、張志和、施肩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>吾、劉商、陳陶、顧況等，高躅可數，皆頡頏于玄化中者歟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○盧延讓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    延讓，字子善，范陽人也。有卓絕之才。光化三年裴格榜進士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>朗陵雷滿荐辟之，滿敗，歸偽蜀，授水部員外郎，累遷給事中，卒官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>刑部侍郎。延讓師許下薛尚書為詩，詞意入僻，不競纖巧，且多健語</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，下士大筆之。初，吳融為侍御史，出官峽中，時延讓布衣，薄游荊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>渚，貧無卷軸，未遑贄謁。會融弟得延讓詩百余篇，融覽其警聯，如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>《宿東林》云：“兩三條電欲為雨，七八個星猶在天。”《旅舍言懷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“名紙毛生五門下，家僮骨立六街中。”《贈元上人》云：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>高僧解語牙無水，老鶴能飛骨有風。”《蜀道》云：“云間鬧鐸騾馱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>去，雪里殘骸虎拽來。”又云：“樹上諏咨批頰鳥，窗間逼駁扣頭虫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“等，大驚曰：“此去人遠絕，自無蹈襲，非尋常耳。此子后必垂名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。余昔在翰林召對，上曾舉其‘臂鷹健卒橫氈帽，騎馬佳人卷畫衫’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一聯，雖淺近，然自成一體名家，今則信然矣。”遂厚禮遇，贈給甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多。融雪中寄詩云：“永日應無食，終宵必有詩。”后奪科第。多融</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之力也。今詩一卷，傳世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○曹松</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    松，字夢征，舒州人也。學賈島為詩，深入幽境，然無枯淡之癖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。尤長啟事，不減山公。早未達，嘗避亂來棲洪都西山。初在建州依</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>李頻，頻卒后，往來一無所遇。光化四年，禮部侍郎杜德祥下，與王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>希羽、劉象、柯崇、鄭希顏同登第，年皆七十余矣，號為“五老榜”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。時值新平內難，朝廷以放進士為喜，特授校書郎而卒。松野性方直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，罕嘗俗事，故拙于進宦，構身林澤，寓情虛無，苦極于詩，然別有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一種風味，不淪乎怪也。集三卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○裴說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    說，工詩，得盛名。天祐三年禮部侍郎薛廷珪下狀元及第。初年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>窘迫亂離，奔走道路，有詩曰“避亂一身多”，見者悲之。后仕為補</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>闕，終禮部員外郎。為詩足奇思，非意表琢煉不舉筆，有島、洞之風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。弟諧，亦以詩名世。仕終桂嶺假官宰。今俱有集，相傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○貫休</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    休，字德隱，婺州蘭溪人，俗姓姜氏。風騷之外，尤精筆札。荊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>州成中令問以書法，休勃然曰：“此事須登壇可授，安得草草而言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”中令銜之，乃遞人黔中，因為《病鶴》詩以見志云：“見說氣清邪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不入，不知爾病自何來“初，昭宗以武肅錢鏐平董昌功，拜鎮東軍節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>度使，自稱吳越王。休時居靈隱，往投詩賀，中聯云：“滿堂花醉三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>千客，一劍霜寒十四州。”武肅大喜，然僭侈之心始張，遣諭令改為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“四十州”，乃可相見。休性躁急，答曰：“州亦難添，詩亦難改。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>余孤云野鶴，何天不可飛！”即日裹衣缽，拂袖而去。至蜀，以詩投</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>孟知祥云：“一瓶一缽垂垂老，萬水千山特特來。”知祥久慕，至是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>非常尊禮之。及王建僭位，一日游龍華寺，召休坐，令口誦近詩，時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>諸王貴戚皆侍，休意在箴戒，因讀《公子行》曰：錦衣鮮華手擎鶻，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>閑行氣貌多陵忽。稼穡艱難總不知，五帝三皇是何物。”建小忉，然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>敬事不少怠也。賜號“禪月大師”。后順寂，敕塔葬丈人山青城峰下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。有集三十卷，今傳。休一條直氣，海內無雙，意度高疏，學問叢脞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，天賦敏速之才，筆吐猛銳之氣，樂府古律，當時所宗。雖尚崛奇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>每得神助，余人走下風者多矣。昔謂龍象蹴蹋，非驢所堪，果僧中之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一豪也。后少其比者，前以方支道林不過矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○張瀛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    瀛，碧之子也。仕廣南劉氏，官至曹郎。嘗為詩贈琴棋僧云：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>我嘗聽師法一說，波上蓮花水中月。不垢不淨是色空，無法無空亦無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>滅。我嘗對師禪一觀，浪溢鰲頭蟾魄滿。河沙世界盡空空，一寸寒灰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>冷燈畔。我又聞師琴一撫，長松喚往秋山雨。弦中雅弄若鏗金，指下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寒泉流太古。我又看師棋一著，山頂坐沉紅日腳。阿誰稱是國手人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>羅浮道士賭卻鶴。輸卻藥葫蘆，斟下紅霞丹，束手不敢爭頭角。”同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>列見之曰：“非其父不生是子。”瀛為詩尚氣而不怒號，語新意卓，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人所不思者，輒能道之。綽綽然見乃父風也。有詩集，今傳于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○沈彬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    彬，字子文，筠州高安人。自幼苦學，屬末歲離亂，隨計不捷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>南游湖湘，隱云陽山數年，歸鄉里。時南唐李昇鎮金陵，旁羅俊逸，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>名儒宿老，必命郡縣起之。彬赴辟，知□欲取楊氏，因獻《畫山水詩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“須知筆力安排定，不怕山河整頓難。”□覽之大喜，授秘書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>郎。保大中，以尚書郎致仕歸，徙居宜春。初經版蕩，與韋莊、杜光</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>庭、貫休俱避難在蜀，多見酬酢。彬臨終，指葬處示家人窆，果掘得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>一空塚，有漆燈青熒，壙頭立一銅版，篆文曰：“佳城今已開，雖開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不葬埋。漆燈終未滅，留待沈彬來。”遂窀穸于此。有詩集一卷。傳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。彬第二子延瑞，性坦率，豪于觴詠，舉動異俗，盛夏附火，嚴冬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>單衣，或遇崇山野水，古洞幽壇，竟日不返，時人異之，呼為“沈道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>者”，士大夫多邀至門館。一日，邑宰戲問：“何日道成“廷瑞即留</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩曰：“何須問我道成時，紫府清都自有期。手握藥苗人不識，體涵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>仙骨俗爭知。”宰驚謝。后浪游四方，或傳仙去也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○唐求</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    求，隱君也，成都人。值三靈改卜，絕念鼎鐘，放曠疏逸，出處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>悠然，人多不識。方外物表，是所游心也。酷耽吟調，氣韻清新，每</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>動奇趣，工而不僻，皆達者之詞。所行覽不出二百里間，無秋豪世慮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之想。有所得，即將稿捻為丸，投大瓢中。或成聯片語，不拘短長，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>數日后足成之。后臥病，投瓢于錦江，望而祝曰：“茲瓢倘不淪沒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>得之者始知吾苦心耳。”瓢泛至新渠，有識者見曰：“此唐山人詩瓢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。”扁舟接之，得詩數十篇。求初未嘗示人，至是方競傳，今行于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>世。后不知所終，江南處士楊夔，亦工詩文，名稱杰出如求，今章句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>多傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○孫魴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    魴，唐末處士也，樂安人。與沈彬、李建勛同時，唱和亦多。魴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有《夜坐》詩，為世稱玩。建勛尤器待之，日與談宴，嘗匿魴于齋幕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，待沈彬來，乃問曰：“魴《夜坐》詩如何“彬曰：“田舍翁火爐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>頭之語，何足道哉！”魴從幕中出，誚彬曰：“何譏謗之甚“彬曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“‘畫多灰漸冷，坐久席成痕。’此非田舍翁爐上，誰有此況“一座</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>大筆。及《金山寺》詩云：“天多剩得月，地少不生塵。”當時謂騷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>情風韻，不減張祜云。有詩五卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○李中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    中，字有中，九江人也。唐末，嘗第進士，為新涂、淦陽、吉水</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>三縣令，仕終水部郎中。孟賓于賞其工吟，絕似方干、賈島，時復過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>之。如“暖風醫病草，甘雨洗荒村”，又“貧來賣書劍，病起憶江湖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>”，又“閑花半落處，幽鳥未來時”，又“千里夢隨殘月斷，一聲蟬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>送早秋來”，又“殘陽影里水東注，芳草煙中人獨行”，又“閑尋野</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>寺聽秋水，寄睡僧窗到夕陽”，又“香入肌膚花洞酒，冷浸魂夢石床</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>云”，又“西園雨過好花盡，南陌人稀芳草深“等句，驚人泣鬼之語</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>也。有《碧云集》，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○廖圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    圖，字贊禹，虔州虔化人。文學博贍，為時輩所服。湖南馬氏辟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>致幕下，奏授天策府學士。與同時劉昭禹、李宏皋、徐仲雅、蔡昆、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>韋鼎、釋虛中，俱以文藻知名，賡唱迭和。齊己時寓渚宮，相去圖千</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>里，而每詩筒往來不絕，警策極多，必見高致。集二卷，今行于世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>時有荊南從事鄭淮，亦工詩，與僧尚顏多所酬贈，詩亦傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○孟賓于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    賓于，字國儀，連州人。聰敏特異，有鄉曲之譽。垂髫時，書所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>作百篇，名《金鰲集》，獻之李若虛侍郎，若虛采獵佳句，記之尺書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，使賓于馳詣洛陽，致諸朝達，聲譽藹然，留寓久之。晉天福九年，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>禮部侍郎符蒙知貢，賓于帘下投詩云：“那堪雨后更聞蟬，溪隔重湖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>路七千。憶得故園楊柳岸，全家送上渡頭船。”蒙得詩，以為相見之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>晚，遂擢第，時已敗六舉矣。與詩人李昉同年情厚。后，賓于來仕江</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>南李主，調淦陽令，因犯法抵罪當死，會昉拜翰林學士，聞在縲紲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>以詩寄之曰：“初攜書劍別湘潭，金榜名標第十三。昔日聲塵喧洛下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，邇來詩價滿江南。長為邑令情終屈，縱處曹郎志未甘。莫學馮唐便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>休去，明君晚事未為慚。”后主偶見詩，遂釋之。遷水部郎中，又知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>丰城縣。興國中致仕，居玉笥山，年七十余卒。自號“群玉峰叟”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>有集今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○孟貫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    貫，閩中人。為性疏野，不以榮宦為意，喜篇章。周世宗幸廣陵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，貫時大有詩價，世宗亦聞之，因繕錄一卷獻上，首篇《書貽譚先生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>》云：“不伐有巢樹，多移無主花。”世宗不悅曰：“朕伐叛吊民，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>何得有巢、無主之說！”獻朕則可，他人則卿必不免。”不復終卷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>賜釋褐進士。虛名而已。不知其終。有詩集，今傳。孟子曰：“予之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>不遇魯侯，天也。”至唐開元，孟浩然流落帝心，和璧墮地。孟郊之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>出處梗概苦難，生平薄宦而死。今孟貫坐此詩窮，轉喉觸諱，非意相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>干，竟爾埋沒，與前賢俱亦相似，命也。孟氏之不遇，一何多耶！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○江為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    為，考城人，宋江淹之裔，少帝時，出為建陽吳興令，因家為郡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人焉。為唐末嘗舉進士，輒不第。工于詩，有“天形圍澤國，秋色露</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>人家”，“月寒花露重，江晚水煙微“等句，膾炙人口。少游白鹿寺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，有句：“吟登蕭寺旃檀閣，醉倚王家玳瑁筵。“后主南遷見之曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>“此人大是富貴家。”時劉洞、夏寶松就傳詩法，為益傲肆，自謂俯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>拾青紫。乃詣金陵求舉，屢黜于有司。怏怏不能已，欲束書亡越，會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>同謀者上變，按得其狀，伏罪。今建陽縣西靖安寺，即處士故居，后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>留題者甚眾。有集一卷，今傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>   ○熊皎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    皎，九華山人。唐清泰二年進士。劉景岩節度延安，辟為從事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>晉天福中，說景岩歸朝，以功擢右諫議，竟坐累黜為上津令。工古律</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詩，語意俱妙。嘗賦《早梅》云：“一夜開欲盡，百花猶未知。”甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>傳賞士林，且知其心遇。今有《屠龍集》、《南金集》合五卷傳世，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>學士陶谷序之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    ○陳摶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>    摶，字圖南，譙郡人。少有奇才經綸，《易•象》玄機，尤所精</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>究。高論駭俗，少食寡思。舉進士不第，時戈革滿地，遂隱名，辟谷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>煉氣，撰《指玄篇》，同道風偃。僖宗召之，封“清虛處士”，居華</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>山云台觀。每閉門獨臥，或兼旬不起。周世宗召入禁中，試之，扃戶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>月余始啟，摶方熟寐齁。覺即辭去，賦詩云：“十年蹤跡走紅塵，回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>首青山入夢頻。紫陌縱榮爭及睡，朱門雖貴不如貧。愁聞劍戟扶危主</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，悶聽笙歌聒醉人。攜取舊書歸舊隱，野花啼鳥一般春。”還山后，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>因乘驢游華陰市，見郵傳甚急，問知宋祖登基，摶抵掌長笑曰：“天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>下自此定矣。”至太宗征赴，戴華陽巾，草屨垂條，與萬乘分庭抗禮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>，賜號“希夷先生”。時居云台四十年，僅及百歲。帝贈詩云：“曾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>向前朝出白云，后來消息杳無聞。如今已肯隨征召，總把三峰乞與君</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>。”真宗復詔，不起，為謝表，略曰：“明時閑客，唐室書生。堯道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>昌而優容許由，漢世盛而善從商皓。況性同猿鶴，心若土灰，敗荷制</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>服，脫籜裁冠，體有青毛，足無草屨，苟臨軒陛，貽笑聖朝。數行丹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>詔，徒教彩鳳銜來；一片野心，已被白云留住。詠嘲風月之清，笑傲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>煙霞之表，遂性所樂，得意何言。”后鑿石室于蓮華峰下，一旦坐其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>中，羽化而去。有詩集，今傳。如洛陽潘閬逍遙、河南種放明逸、錢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>塘林逋君復、鉅鹿魏野仲先、青州李之才挺之、天水穆修伯長，皆從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p>學先生，一流高士，俱有詩名。大節詳見之《宋史》云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9a7b9adb6980ad1b/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-f09fcd twpub-9a7b9adb6980ad1b-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Tang Caizi Chuan, by Xin Wen-fang</p></div>"
        },
